naga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWty_MjaL5ghiNSm-Rjfmi3coWqCPIuK7LP1vqFCsze3zOuytUMzA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Easy to schedule online for a Sunday. Staff was super nice. No wait with an appointment. I took my 6 year old daughter in for tooth pain and turns out she needed an extraction.  Dr. K made her feel at ease and he was very caring and patient with her through the whole process. At the end of the visit my daughter asked if she could go back if another tooth hurt again. That says a lot! Thanks again Dr. K and staff!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2lsSC95cwA4RSWuVF_iaMLmSe2B85ymZECnMwrgkTPhrA23AUtAwJrpbG_FkcItWYNFndD7hf0TETXHozHe8foL-lK4T1Ui8ggAGOcZ1eNh--gfL9HWwCij7wnAc1fcd6HlJry8atGkiY=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-1"},{"Name":"John Grzemski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_nt5jK03aBlCFcocWr4umzvMe968MqiLkYvGW2wdZ0p_y3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in for an impromptu tooth extraction on a Saturday. I had a broken wisdom tooth and the most heinous pain I've ever experienced, which had kept me awake for 4 days. Within an hour, they had the tooth extracted and I was on my way like nothing ever happened. Not even any pain from the procedure as the sensation returned to my mouth.\nEverything went very smoothly. The staff was personable, professional, and VERY great at what they do. If you ever have a dental crisis, I highly recommend this group. They'll take great care of you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Virginia Nichole","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVRROjpZA-SUfhCQ-2EQfk9eq91VctC8PxC683OP4EdxOoKXqqj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kamara and his assistants where great. One of the best dental experiences I have had. His willingness to listen to me and find a solution was one of the things that made me the most happy as I have had dentist in the past wright me of and not listen. They made me feel welcomed and help keep me calm and even though we were there pretty late, Dr Kamara took his time and didn't rush. Overall great customer service and look forward to my next visit hopefully not while in pain 🙂.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"PK Chauhan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJUBaTsa4z1nrbY8_A3SNSFzRQbuT21H2-Po6MjYSPxlWbDmK4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lavanya is an excellent dentist and truly cares about her patients. I have seen her at both Chase Oaks Dentistry in Plano and Waterfront Dentistry in Frisco and my experience has been consistently great at both locations. She is very gentle, patient, and takes time to explain every step of the treatment, which makes you feel comfortable and confident. The clinics are clean, modern, and well organized, and the staff is friendly and professional. I highly recommend Dr. Lavanya to anyone looking for a skilled and trustworthy dentist in Plano or Frisco.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEq5SS0-SE9hOefZ30S7XOuVk0vXygd6_rKel1gk0uomSlr2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Harold Kamara saw me very last minute on a saturday, with some pressing issues and was very helpful in diagnosing and determining the proper treatment pathway. He was precise in his cleaning, helpful and made us feel comfortable and heard during the consultation and procedure. His dental assistant was also very patient and helpful as well as the receptionist Rosa. Prices were very reasonable, we left with the necessary script in hand and we were in and out quickly. Couldn't recommend them more, thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Susan Mccartney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcDLsnOX-ENxSHImyaglFKWPtWP3JyEMngKfYAJsE3qAtmYCimRg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was by far the best experience I've had with a Dental Office. Dr. Kamara and his staff were kind, compassionate and extremely accommodating! Dr. Kamara addressed all of my concerns and more importantly, my 17yr old daughters' concerns. He was gentle, patient and made it a priority to make sure my daughter left feeling confident with her smile. It was very apparent that he truly cares about his patients as a whole instead of just the dental aspect of it. If I could give a 10 Star Rating, I would definitely do so! The entire experience was exceedingly higher than any expectations I had. Thank you for all of your hard work and dedication, Dr. Kamara. I sincerely appreciate it more than you will ever know!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monika Veliz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ5l2Mm_Xqm7cG1ws7JsIwIimMeDxHsMlS6yqMB77t4cQ4Hkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved this place, came in on Saturday for a tooth extraction and everything went amazing. The front ladies are so nice they helped me alot. Dr. K is amazing he comes in and makes you feel really comfortable. I will definitely be back for my other procedures!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lashawnda Parksel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUruhLvoK8SqDqSBpW8KrJPuzi5c5WmT-NdX0z_ynSMxLcsnx8=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a really bad infection and needed a few extractions. Dr. Karmara was very thorough and explained everything from start to finish.  The receptionist and assistants were very friendly and helpful. They have various payment options with fair prices. I definitely recommend them for your dental work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
