end them? You bet! They're the benchmark!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0cpudOL701LhuQGSDtvAIfFi-bjHHGgRffRDUg_MT_W7Hvy4X-09ZW75SOz_vBVdtN01SK3RwwGsQ7k22qZsZ7omGtYS_qwwnMBjndZ7XrIm4tPq93MoUmfiD1IP1_Djk5jitBlwaLcwA=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-5"},{"Name":"Stephen Ingram","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKJNwdNWV4UdMim4zE7udOUGN-AA2w8EzxjgdkWN-r7RhZPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Lo and his staff are by far the best in the business. Dr Lo’s style is professional, yet approachable. He exhibits a genuine warmth and care for his patients that’s not only evident by his demeanor, but by the fact that he never recommends unnecessary procedures. My family and I have been a patient of his for years, and we highly recommend his practice!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Willett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVE_g4u2mWYDzxiUhyyQAYIGlU62GG1M5U8xnUqzIGhtvHu388=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going for five years since I moved here at the end of 2020 and couldn’t be happier!\n\nDr. Lo is amazing and somehow gives numbing shots where I can barely feel even a slight pinch and I’ve had two root canals, wisdom teeth removed (which took seriously 40 minutes start to finish) and multiple cracked teeth fixed with crowns!\n\nThe rest of the staff is amazing and very friendly as well!\n\nThey have a plan you can get from them that covers cleanings and gives discounts on their other services if you don’t have dental insurance like me.\n\nCan not recommend enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Emma Will","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKo9zkdDZZuXYyd9YJPT_vKySm576FiUEzwhfhYhUwQWFb-dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just wanted to shout out how amazing Dr. Pepper and his team were to me as well as the front desk people. I had a sudden and extremely painful toothache that needed to be addressed and they were able to get me in for an appointment the very next day first thing as well as called in a better medicine to manage my pain before hand.\n\nDuring my visit I had a root canal and crown procedure and Dr. Pepper was very kind and support through the whole process and made me feel as comfortable as one can with a bunch of tools in their mouth. I was left with some major soreness afterwards due to how my nerves are wired and them being near impossible to perfectly numb, but Dr. pepper and the rest of his team were extremely patient and kind to me and did everything in their power to help me through that last little bit and even ended up staying late to finish up.\n\nI really appreciate their expertise as well as their care for their patients and would highly recommend them to anyone","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tony Cacioppo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtcyNGQ9-2QNIG3XJASueejY_AFjDp4mDiQMgd6I5mF5K1E4qb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this practice for anyone looking for quality care. It was my first visit and from the time I walked in until I left, the staff was friendly. Attentive and professional. Dr. Matthew Pepper was equally as friendly and attentive and very genuine. He thoroughly explained long term treatment and options w/o any pressure. I will be back for all dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leslie Krebs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKm60VEW7t41NQWt-mozh7ZEdEH2rCG2adgeSZhmB1etfaHGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient of Dr. Lo for over 10 years. He is an excellent dentist and is always honest and caring. Just had an older crown come off and he was able to recement it, even though a crack was on part of the surface. He felt that I could still get some more time with this crown which is just a good example of his conservative approach to treatment. All the staff in this practice is friendly and caring. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabrielle Richer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL4SrV_wv147f9SruVc4KsCGuq-xS7OZssUdKvXyzuOMCFFTw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son had an ortho consultation today and  we loved this office ! The entire staff is so friendly and welcoming ! A special shout out to Dr.Silber for being so nice and very informative about everything and to Carlos, the treatment coordinator for making it such a smooth and easy visit ! I recommend this office to patients of all ages. Thank you Texas Dental","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barbara Charlton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5i0kqdOhwmCf5cL0SYcx69jFTy3o9o9iFpDjCTboSy9YFtbEk=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wilson Lo is a rockstar!\n\nAs a dentist's daughter, I worked for Dad as a teen. Dad set a seriously high benchmark.\n\nFor quality and thoroughness,  Dad would have approved and applauded Dr. Lo.\n\nDr. Lo exceeds all expectations for a high quality and compassionate dentist.\n\nGet an appointment with him if you need the real deal.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
