cJd7C8iDQYIPY-D-NssZc6KXWzw1RokzZVL5FjvMx3wqVDqfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every time that I've gone to Texas Choice Dental, my experience has been one of excellence! They are professional, kind and efficient. There's never been an overcrowded lobby, and I was called within 10 minutes of arriving. A courtesy toothbrush packet is provided each time I visit, which is every 6 months, and that prompts me to change my toothbrush, at that time. I was 20 minutes late, at my last appointment, and they were gracious enough to grant me the time I needed to get there, so that I didn't have to take off another day.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Klaudia Klaudia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjo6fXVWupIHp9HLd6Au7NErELxGmXaKeUnC1hTBwDlC8PoQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"No long waits! They took us in right away at our appointment time. My 11 year old daughter had teeth that were bothering her and they fixed those right away. She really liked it here and felt comfortable so we will be returning. The staff is nice, the place is clean and the instruments are modern making x-rays easy. I highly recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M Hunter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEIB-YaZhMjZ_Q2VFtLWHC52K7Hiy6G0iRG9mmzHsi8Eu0UA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is amazing from the time you walk in you feel welcomed.  I did not have to wait long to be seen and that was great. I went in for a cleaning and Dr. Kim was very gentle.  Selma (high five) your are amazing very professional.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Genesis Villalba","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8pCfjhTZJkaUSrKerj8lqCWt1HHG2PRbRy8YIy6YgHUanrw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience at my dentist’s office today! I came in with severe pain from a growing wisdom tooth and could barely handle it anymore. The team took me in right away and made sure I was comfortable. They sedated me quickly to get me out of pain, and I can’t express how grateful I am for their kindness and efficiency. A special thank you to Joanna and my doctor (whose name I unfortunately don’t remember) for their excellent care and compassion. I truly appreciate everything they did for me today — it’s been a long time since I’ve felt that kind of relief. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI550VVHEWNgm7TTMJN9vlp_vEEjHjX45h42R3BqnvLfIGJb-Qx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From.the moment I walked into this dentist office, I was met with kindness and care. They made me feel safe. Got my wisdom tooth extracted and it was a lot to take in but they made me comfortable. I will be bringing my daughter there next. Definitely recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheryl Kinder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ72_sk5BfxBro2-mjQAsNVmqbj-rFBJolB0dRiJe3qTYomfw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone was very friendly and provided excellent service. I had two separate visits to complete work on one side of my jaw. During the first visit, the doctor used a laser without injections or anesthesia, and the procedure was completely painless. At the second visit, the doctor used both a laser and anesthesia—again, the experience was painless.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jesse De La Torre","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKAVg7nkMGEMfflBeY2SdJSkh77S9VRvdB580vXhwhmok--Gg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kim and her staff are really nice and professional. I'm always satisfied with their services here. I drive 25 miles from my house, just to come to this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rochelle Purnell [HMS]","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW2Ub15mtK-BVPdetk8G-uYYwOhCTtTy9LZk4P_iV-pqQ7ky_a2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kim and  the entire team at Choice Dental from\nThe front office Nancy always making sure my appts. Are conveniently booked and paperwork insurance is in place. I don’t have to worry about billing.  She takes care of it all.  I love Dr. Kim; her chair side manner is very warm and comfortable to address even the most painful procedures.  The overall staff is Super!  My family Dental center will always be  Texas Choice Dental!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
