 very affordable price. Upon seeing his care for our child, I now see Dr. V for my dental needs. His office is outstanding and we are grateful for all of his efforts. Dr. V is not just a great dentist, he is a great person!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angy Garza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjbvYXEMw6c10VEQ-fHCOKhXA4daeHJ0tYoJ-lBgigxcO9CQrm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A Truly Kind and Caring Dental Team!\n\nWe recently switched to this dental office after leaving our previous dentist due to a lack of bedside manner, and the difference has been night and day. From the moment we walked in, the entire team was kind, patient, and incredibly accommodating. They truly take the time to listen and make sure every question or concern is addressed with care.\n\nI brought in my three young children (all five and under) on the same day, and I was so impressed by how wonderful everyone was with them - calm, gentle, and genuinely caring. What could have been a stressful visit turned into such a positive experience. We finally found a dental office that combines professionalism with true compassion, and we couldn’t be happier!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocICg-b9y7mqbl5DftKzAQg1mDsZSkCPmZvZXlN_oeUc7tWezw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is a great place for all your dental needs. The receptionist is helpful and welcoming and the text reminders for appointments make it easy to remember your scheduled appointments. They work with you to serve your needs and achieve your dental goals. I hadn’t been to a dentist regularly for several years and decided to get a fresh start here. They were able to get me on the right track and now I just have cleanings regularly. Highly recommend them to anyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"elizabeth leon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIcfxNn4oj838A7LWABpLsiQYDpr7FbivqOfdYYmBSDa6wV5bo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist place ever!!! Mrs Susan is always welcoming and awesome! Jose did an amazing job cleaning my teeth! Was also such a nice person and made me feel comfortable! Thank you guys so much! Wonderful team","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"julian ezra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDcXdByG-dTXS804ziWo0sy0UwGXrdX3mEHN-dkAfJ7PvnHg4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had to get a root canal and several fillings, and the entire experience was handled with exceptional professionalism by Dr. Vashisht. The procedure was smooth, detailed, and done with great care. I’m very satisfied with the treatment I received and highly recommend Dr. Vashisht. Also for those who are wondering delta dental insurance covers here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ms. M.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuLNAd_ZxRRLlfxKA_fmPzcfCSJbHAeVOndBi4K1CeEGd4LDtRwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The facility and staff are the bomb.com. Leslie was wonderful and her engagement ring is fabulous 🤩💕 Susan has this place jamn with 90s pop and everyone was super friendly. I'm totally coming back for my 6 month appointment. Thank you Dr. Varun. You guys rock.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S Singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2FILshQxhMgb2dfJ89Az29ziHgeFbgnQwwHbWn7xhF3EZMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"“Exceptional care—finally under one roof!”\nIf you're nervous about going to the dentist, this is the place to go. From the moment you walk in, it feels more like visiting friends than a clinic. I was growing frustrated with being referred out for every dental need, but Dr. V and his team handled my complicated treatment entirely in-house. Everyone here truly listens and makes you feel cared for. I’m so impressed, I’ll be bringing my whole family from now on!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arexas Tate","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVS1c0aqbM6RTD-Snm9rMqL5QUcgE15gQ94BIN2UYXTNvgHwbM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have two children and one of which has anxiety going to the dentist. Of course this child always wants to go second. The dentist made them feel very welcome. whenever it came time to see the dentist my child was calm as can be. had absolutely no problems. My child climbed in the chair, played with the dentist, interact with them with no problem and did exactly what was needed to be done with no issues. Needless to say, I will be returning.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
