0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://flexbook.me/texassmile?rwg_token=AFd1xnFv9qJxyeNmxJ5VCtfX4WnC91oG9UOR7aak3AtxAskmAUT1Odo1fflC2GJTF3TcYrF__VI7TIBpoS5Y0NaQad_L-zz1n0nzYI7r6FvfuLdEv1aXZLU%3D","source":"flexbook.me"}],"menu":{"link":"/url?q=https://familydentistfriscotx.com/family-dentistry/\u0026opi=79508299\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwi-raTclNCUAxXsEzQIHW0aDzgQqRkIHSgQ\u0026usg=AOvVaw1vmLDgxwcdsuEY6lciK2Sd","source":"familydentistfriscotx.com"},"owner":{"id":"104309771994082006685","name":"Texas Smile Co. (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104309771994082006685"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"13355 Dallas Pkwy Suite 400","city":"Frisco","postal_code":"75033","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"children","name":"Children","options":[{"name":"Nursing room","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"E.D. Snyder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVCXSv9fFLSDWcUVj_7uecYANJe4SoQk_mYjN0wlifgrLIEGL4=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best I’ve ever had. Okay, I’m in my sixties, so I’ve been to a few dentists over the years. I was recommended to Dr. Kyle at Texas Smile Co. by a family member—who was recommended by another family member! Sitting in a dentist’s chair is not my idea of a good afternoon, but his team makes it simple, stress-free, and pain-free. Seriously, I needed two crowns and didn’t feel a thing. These folks are wonderful—friendly, professional, and they truly make you feel valued and cared for. I even have family who commute from Dallas and Royse City just for their excellent care. I highly recommend them!  —Ed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dr. Johneisha Motley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeFJJzNBeswiMvwAFoYPF7Z06rOnlvnBeWzs2cTargXY0N9qW1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found this dentist office through my insurance but the reviews is what made me book an appointment. I’m here to say the reviews did not lie! Everyone was so friendly and welcoming. I don’t remember names too well, but the guy that cleaned and charted my teeth was so informative! You can really tell him and Dr. Kyle truly cares about the health of your teeth. I’m prone to cavities and no doctor has ever told me that there’s a toothpaste and mouthwash I can use to help the pH of my saliva prevent new cavity formations. Of course it’s a little costly, but I’d pay this over $5000 dental work in the future any time! Thanks so much Dr. Kyle and assistant no name 🤭. You all are amazing and I’m so happy I’ve finally found a dentist office that truly cares beyond the dollar sign.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shahid Khaliq","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXbyDikWqbFWZ5GgkayxixsNYATmy0Z7dPQCk7hcw2io0BrrQj-Ug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first visit here today and it was a wonderful experience! From the friendly lady at the front desk to the tech who took my X-rays, Kenneth, and Dr. Kyle, the entire team here was incredibly welcoming and professional. Everyone treated me like a friend and seemed to genuinely have my best interests at heart.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dentist, I cannot recommend this practice highly enough. It’s a true gem!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Will Smyth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIS2T-go8ibSo4GTQihOgIOQPSajdJdvNRLmEBp_ikt73PgqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the moment I reached out I’ve been impressed. An easy enrollment process and excellent patient service.\n\nKenneth, Dental Hygienist, was great and explained everything in detail. He never pressured me to purchase additional products/services because he’s not commissioned for sales. Extremely professional and knowledgeable. He loves his job and it shows!\n\nDr. Kyle was very personable and helpful. He never pressured me to purchase additional services but explained that I needed work but could do it on my time. I plan on retuning to complete a few things that need to be done in March. I also will be referring my wife and son for cleanings and checkups. Thank you for a really great experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jon warr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ9bKi2XSPkgF3s08FWsnF13PVywHwNmO3izJhIw7CCQTaGcQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kyle and the entire team at Smile Co. are exceptionally professional, welcoming, and attentive. I had only ever seen one dentist my whole life until he retired, so finding someone I could trust was very important to me. I’m truly glad I chose Dr. Kyle and his team. They’ve been outstanding with routine cleanings, and I recently had a crown done—the experience was smooth, thorough, and incredibly comfortable. Highly recommend Smile Co. for anyone seeking quality dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Garrett Herrmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLjP0o8auKEZQFSFPg0r2_DNdzm1qnJzK5ZLN-2vdBmJtBonw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The crew at Texas Smile Co. just does it right. They provide exceptional care and always take the additional time to educate on why they make the recommendations that they do. Because of this, I always feel like I’m making educated decisions on my oral health.\n\nI’ve seen Kenneth several times now and he’s always a bright spot in my day. You can tell that he truly cares about his patients.\n\nDr. Kyle always takes the time to connect on a more personal level that goes further than a surface level doctor/patient relationship.\n\nI’d definitely recommend Texas Smile Co. to anyone that is in the market for a new dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Corey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXN-gw5H4XrryhQHkwXtZXCh2DiFydESvKLoOSwVyfBhoi7WkY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I absolutely love this dental office! Every single staff member was welcoming and friendly. I didn’t feel like just another patient and rushed in and out and sold crazy treatment plans like you would experience at a big corporate dental office. Everyone took time to really get to know you, nobody was rushing around, they were absolutely transparent the whole time about what they were seeing and what the treatment plan would be and had open discussions regarding everything. They are very knowledgeable and passionate about what they are doing. The atmosphere is warm and comfortable and they make you feel like family from the very beginning. I’ve definitely found my new dental office and will be brining the rest of my family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"N G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKf2jFjTvbVwzjt1YyFCCuKTW98lO4AUUTU1E0DiTTZ0Ew0Tg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you're looking for a dentist, look no further than Texas Smile Co. This is a truly family-owned dental office, and you can feel the difference from the moment you walk in. The staff are incredibly warm and friendly, making you feel right at home.\n\nThe doctors and staff take the time to sit with you and thoroughly explain all your treatment options without any pressure to commit to a specific plan. I saw Dr. Kyle Poupart, and he prioritizes your health and comfort above all else. They genuinely want to help you make the best decision for your dental care.\n\nAlso, I had brought my mother here a few months ago for an emergency extraction, and Dr. Kyle saw her right away. She said it was the best dental experience she had ever had, and she had a speedy recovery.\n\nEven though their offices are just around the corner from me, I would drive an hour for the quality care my family has received here! I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
