ns","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jessica G.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIyx_AlmG7FhJ6oiQ8Z6nVFMHpaNQIXU8xcFiZ0BZ_nJJGDlg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Where do I begin! In my past, I had experienced the fear and trauma of white knuckling through a dental procedure where I was not completely numbed. Seeing dentist after dentist thinking this type of treatment would get better, or maybe I was the problem. I dreaded every appointment.\nUntil now!! Until my search brought me to Natural Dentistry of North Texas!\nDr. Randhawa and her AMAZING staff (please forgive me as i don't remember a name). They were so kind and so patient with me. They definitely handled me with care and encouraged me through my fears. My dental technician was so reassuring and so encouraging, forgive me i dont remember your name, but thank you.\nThis place is really like family! They offer  the type of treatment anyone and everyone deserves!! I was able to complete my treatment pain free yall! NO PAIN!! Do you hear me!! NONE! For those who know, know. I will be back every 6 mths for dental care with Dr. Randhawa.\nI got it right yall and you can too! This place is the real deal and worth every penny!\nI am so grateful! 🥹 THANK YOU SO MUCH!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Troy Boscia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOK37RVdmr6bLLbXeIwvZCeQmyI2euvWMlSwPVrOVaAUhS4gNThw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough great things about Natural Dentistry off Town East. I recently had to get a crown replaced along with a couple of old fillings, and from start to finish, the experience was outstanding.\n\nFrom the moment I was brought back, the dental assistant was incredibly kind and sweet—she made me feel completely at ease. Her professionalism and gentle care truly stood out, especially when it came to fitting my bite guard perfectly after the crown work.\n\nDr. Randhawa was absolutely phenomenal. Even with multiple procedures spread over two visits, she remained patient, took the time to explain everything, and gave me clear options to consider. It’s rare to find a provider who blends clinical expertise with such a compassionate approach.\n\nThe front office staff? Just as amazing—welcoming, helpful, and genuinely kind every time I walked in.\n\nI’m moving soon and will sincerely miss this entire team. Thank you all for making what could’ve been a stressful process feel comfortable and cared for. You’ve set the bar high!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Ni2xefigyunBzAl-UvZu_oSVqG_feAD5Hqdh4cyMofFXvuijheR4mOIN7XMkCGKX-uygbOX4a_9ROTXFunTBArPlA4HCpuZQFySb1HjrtvSMGxtNuquUKBgx4-1qG3hBlWXbf=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-21"},{"Name":"Garrett King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJXWNZRY2G1hJwgGlGs9XJfOMYX3H7bz1lYA4-ae3nZK2ucfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have used other dentist in the past but was referred here by a coworker. I had a lot of work that needed to be done. After a few years of chipping away at it im finally done and I couldn't be more happy. Before I could barely eat and now I can eat whatever I want with no pain. Natural might be more expensive than others but the doctor is very good at her job. I have one crown I got from another dentist and I can defiantly tell the difference in quality, fit and finish are way lesser quality. The crowns I got here fill like my actual teeth. I would highly recommend this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebecca Hernandez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJv3SwunMLKE2o5JhyXojbX6qAiBKC5uvorQYmFHd7AlfSIKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Angela is very friendly , always has a smile and goes above and beyond to help me with any issues. I would definitely recommend coming to Natural Dentistry. All staff and the doctor are amazing","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jim McCullin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGANLkZSc9IP_FfZzr3sRuFRtpUQijPLwx4g1vUWteEDCKPw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Randhawa and the entire clinical and administrative staff are top notch. You won't likely find a more competent and polished (pun intended) dental practice in our area. My wife and I have come to Natural Dentistry for everything from simple cleanings to implant crown placements. We've never been disappointed. Skip the chain dental clinics and opt instead for the real professionals. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vanessa Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_0oYEABJqtodNl59Nz2vDpGHONFLf37CDUy_sbkN726liuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been coming here for years, and i don't think I’ll ever change my dentist. Love the entire team here, they are all fantastic. Thank you guys for always making it a great experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKC01kpeBpYJRkgKnbFivTuqjaEJ6PT90f0ExkzCQzp3jdZjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Literally the most amazing dental professionals I have ever met 🥹\n\nThey made me feel so supported throughout the entire process especially when battling anxiety from past dental experiences in other places . 10/10 would recommend!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mitzi Booth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJMKM52o928qyM7Td89wemYfv8aeOvefDb2jmCD7O_y-PYUGA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very impressed with my first visit \u0026 cleaning. Extremely friendly \u0026 welcoming staff. Really liked Dr. Randhawa too. Im happy to have found a natural dentistry practice near me","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
