":"Ashlee Carlyle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVp8XkJzo7pMZbZfJU4QZmpIT-IEgwsOcOiEpnapHTj7vZYPBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Goldman is always a pleasure! She’s very knowledgeable and interactive with me and my child each visit. My son has complex medical needs and she was the only pediatric dentist who would accept him back when he use to have a trach and was on a ventilator. The entire staff is always respectful, kind, and professional; I highly recommend this dental office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melody M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKl_Kv8LrftqF78xuh-BEtjAhjuuQRstXuOr1Ce1s8XKRoIUVegA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! I've never experienced such care and professionalism as I have with Dr. Goldman! Your kids will feel comfortable, knowledgeable and safe when in this office! Thank you staff!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3ytmpm4xItrZMu0jIKInui1ycZc4-d4mLuM1D1D6s4dWVrxUH_vmtnCdS6wWtgE-LGDF00m3RABDtX0CduJq2cNidH1f7tAAn32qIWbSvAd2LLUUxizPdIXx9pLe75HCQT0Wosgw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0s_fE0c5u61iqePvve5F_thpiuVb8wZ0UU_kJMkScI3TPVrlaerisPeWNxefYQykEzl6d3GVdjT3mzbuREkot0WginnXxAiaLUHkA62sAjP_sK1utLFj2pvIw0mb0-virkrJP9=k-no"],"When":"2023-4-13"},{"Name":"Josphine Njeri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzUSl_7uX3_EbQ9KSoE8kiYoCaKgQ6Jz-cBmbtI55pzVwHE1fk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great customer service. From Ms Melinda and other front office staff to the dental chair, they make your visit feel so comfortable and welcome. Dr Goldman is an amazing dentist who knows how to work with kids. My kids are well taken care of here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terry E.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_NRKngc5gAdKkJ4cUfo_0fL7eYMYqL1EaOj28cjOBoyFZ4Os=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our family loves this office! From Melinda at the front desk to Dr. Goldman they’re all so welcoming and warm. Everything is so clear and concise during and after every appt. The way Dr. Goldman works with the kiddos to keep them feeling safe and assured is a gift. I highly recommend Redbud Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTmOV38J_u-6axXc7ey4O2RvlpPaH_7-ifQYZyB2hm3b2mas0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have nothing but praise for Dr. Goldman!!! She is amazing, very thorough. She takes her time to explain everything in detail and is wonderful with both of my kids.\nI truly appreciate her professionalism, kindness, patience, and warm friendly nature!\nDr. Goldman, Melinda, the assistants are all amazing. Great Team. Highly  recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elizabeth Roberts Kaddoura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW236-_WMYbzi7A0-81elfsz3MRzJHPLclISvzJ6rHt4L6LWyq1=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. G and staff were amazing as always. She has the calmest and most reassuring voice. The staff is always so kind and friendly. It’s a very relaxing environment for kids, not over stimulating or noisy, just calm and I love going there with them. iPad check-ins are super easy and staff was constantly wiping and cleaning everything that is high touch. Employees are still masking which I appreciate in cold, flu, virus season! Thanks for being the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheilla Nathan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWPXkWPUpC3gvZ9ZmZNeLcj82NKceCx6s5OGmx0xLZ4vm5Mc2f5VQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been bringing my children here now for well over 6 years (maybe more) and I couldn't be happier. They were referred to Dr. Goldman by their previous dentist and she is wonderful. No matter where we move to, I will always make the drive to McKinney to bring my children here.  I like that she takes time to greet everyone and learn their names. She is kind and gentle and never hesitates to answer my many questions when it comes to their dental care. Her staff is amazing and I love visiting. Wouldn't change a thing!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
