asseter and the team at Heart of Texas Smiles are absolutely amazing. She makes you feel completely at ease, even when you’re showing up in pajamas — she just wrapped me in a blanket and got to work. I even had a root canal today, and I still walked out smiling (that says everything you need to know!). Professional, kind, and truly caring — I can’t recommend them enough.\n\nDr. Lasseter is not only an amazing dentist, but also someone who makes you feel genuinely cared for every step of the way. (And yes, I still love her even after she gave me a root canal today — that’s how good she is! 😅🦷)\n\nFrom the warm staff to the state-of-the-art office, Heart of Texas Smiles truly lives up to its name. Highly recommend them to anyone looking for a dental home that’s both professional and personal.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Orzeilu2sva0OgkTMwjmeBxn8nGCZo85TjQ1Qo3bDbgdAKCjgYP7FlhpkZyFLZv_jN7TuBD6dGhTzw0ry1mRaoI2gWzf0DK4X7Es19n_xVlai34x_OEKu0_iGFFgs2_OGE7HtmFkuW4c=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-2"},{"Name":"Alejandra Gonzalez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJcYj5_tweJER8yweNZ5omXFBLSgiqH4FY9H90m1tgTB8eT2A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New pt here, first off I really really liked Paula and Dr Kuma! I felt very comfortable with both. All my questions were answered very clearly. Paula was great she made me feel comfortable throughout the whole visit and had a good conversations.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Van Raalte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIbXuFWnKPfJtKqDPbyVxWCb2QuFA9lJyn-gafP5bQTcC28w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love every single person here!!  The care is fantastic.  They make going to the dentist a pleasant experience.  Jennifer S has been my hygienist and friend for over 10 years.  She is a rockstar.  Our whole family is blessed with their care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Banks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleuse