astic during my teeth cleaning. She made sure I was feeling comfortable and not in pain, she made good conversation, which  I enjoyed, and she just made the overall experience enjoyable. Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
