Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had a deep cleaning at this dental office by Dr Linh Nguyen and I am extremely pleased with the quality of care and results. The procedure was surprisingly painless. Dr Linh was remarkably thorough, ensuring all that plaque, tarter and bacteria were removed, especially in the difficult spots below the gum line and between teeth. Post-cleaning, my mouth feels incredibly clean and healthy! I highly recommend Dr Linh for anyone needing a deep cleaning; his expertise and commitment to patient comfort are truly outstanding!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bailey le","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6Y1Z0H3oe3O4P9q0vtNioJaZVLDrxsNE4dwGDN3XpclFDsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From my initial consultation, Dr Linh and his team thoroughly explained the entire process of getting orthodontic braces, ensuring I understood each step. His expertise and attention to detail was evident as he crafted a personalized treatment plan tailored to my specific needs. What impressed me most was Dr. Linh and his team’s commitment to patient comfort; they always took the time to address any concerns and made sure I was at ease during every visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracey Lindsay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU1lnAQzMBPFTErKUB_ZOALPMMwIilgQIOrs0jLXlGC-0TVNOAx=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Dr. Linh for a few years and he is so amazing. He is very personable and gentle. I hate going to the dentist but he makes you feel so comfortable and relaxed. The staff is great as well. They make you feel very welcome. Thank you Dr. Linh and staff!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ogechi Ugwulebo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfR1jlQCaniUNnjsQqgHn03gr1Ps_xICAvqzGalUyyR8eHQTKr=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"My daughter just had her cleaning appointment done today and had a very bad experience. According to her, the hygienist (female Asian or Hispanic) that first attended to her before the dentist came in was very rude and unprofessional. She walked into the room and didn’t even acknowledge my daughter or look her direction but went straight to the computer and was talking as she was typing. My daughter said that she wasn’t sure if the lady was talking to her or someone else. Then she came over and started cleaning without turning on the light above her face or putting her in the bib to avoid splashing. Also, the x-ray machine wasn’t functioning properly and she had to sit in the machine with her chin and face for almost 15 minutes while they tried to figure it out. However, she did mention that she was relieved when the Dentist later came into the room to finish the last part of her teeth cleaning, Overall, a very unpleasant experience. This is very disappointing. We may have to find a new dental clinic.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
