o"],"When":"2022-2-1"},{"Name":"Celeste Ibarra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJyA3rfC7BZTIbVGFSOcwZIfUef6sAyQueGxdBezGzRF7dcKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Martinez is absolutely fantastic! They made me feel incredibly comfortable during my entire visit, clearly explaining every step of the procedure and ensuring I had no pain. The staff is friendly and welcoming, and the office is clean and modern. I highly recommend them to anyone looking for a caring and skilled dentist. He also see's pediatrics which is a plus when you are trying to get all your family appts in one day at the same time. He has been taking care of my 3 yr old son since he was 6 months old, always very patient.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUtu7LON9bNz58wxBi5S2J2izqSVo5JINCyku5T30J1NPvewQoI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always have the best, efficient and friendliest experience every time I come here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Keily Midence","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-28TZXhKhQOl_JtgFcNmt_g686JjUG47fehPn0L2bTFNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great dentist and staff! Dr. Martinez is extremely knowledgeable, kind, personable. He will spend time with you to make sure, you're well taken care of. The wait is never long and they respect your time. I highly recommend this office to anyone that is looking for a great dentist. Everyone there it's always professional,friendly, courteous.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Theresa C.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJwnEFrmmhizO2ARzTHBOJkaT3VotjjiKXG9z_xBoiSK4vpow=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Place!\nThis is a very personable, clean, sanitary and technologically advanced dentist office, a really great place for your dental needs. The best dental care I have ever experienced!  Everyone is friendly and caring and the dentist is very knowledgeable and takes time to find out about your allergies, your general health and any meds you may be taking.  He is very thorough and actually listens to any concerns you may have. He then followed through and solved my problems that I couldn't get any other dentist to solve.  Also most dental offices you visit for a cleaning will have the dental assistant do this procedure, but Dr. Martinez is hands on and does it himself and does a very excellent job. I felt no pain or discomfort as with other dental offices. But most of all he doesn't pad your bill with a lot of unnecessary procedures. I would highly recommend Big Texas Dental and Dr.Juan Martinez,DDS.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marie Louise","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLkLuZaQg3LDrj2QiN1vmGm65uJm3Z4SuFrxg8UFsCoFxDfAg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great! The staff and Doctor is welcoming and polite. The Doctor is gentle and professional,  explaining the problem with a n affordable plan. I found the work done quickly.   Good tv right in front of you in the chair. Will most definitely return again and again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Priscilla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSwhOJsjiM23t78BcHyZFZOn6MB4vX1KPB5qf0sMUWIf-4cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best experience I’ve ever had, the staff and the Doctor were amazing and explained everything. The facility was clean and wait time was minimal. They truly care about each patient and made coming to the dentist a great experience for my children. Will definitely recommend to everyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"gaby tovar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWpirOZaZgQsMyS---81tekutRg7grcU3FBcLuuj2Xc1dihtdVL=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I was calling all day for 2 days because my husband needed an appointment ASAP and nobody ever answered the phone. I sent an email and I didn’t get a response either. We finally went in person at 4PM and they were already closing. I asked if they still closed at 6PM and the front desk said yes but sometimes the doctor leaves whenever he wants?? It says “emergency walk-ins welcome” on their doors and yet they told me the earliest appointment they could give my husband isn’t until May 9th.. it’s April 25th today. Won’t be returning.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
