true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Katie Rawson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJnmQAf16rgmGBnpdx6ZLwG-heBTYtKx1J_dcgPe1Xwz5S_YA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Bove was a literal savior for me. I had been on a high dose of ibuprofen for 5 months from a previous dentist that worked on me and I was miserable. He not only addressed the issue but then immediately handled it during my first visit. I would recommend him to anyone. My dad is the one who recommended him to me because he helped him out in a time of need.\nAbsolutely fantastic office as a whole. Will definitely be coming back to them for all future dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Dupree","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJPW5TnbGkz06hW1i-G-lXKDn9Zdqd3ZL-xxrxc9lMPjPb3Nw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is coming from someone who is deathly afraid of going to the dentist.  Dr. Bove and his staff are AMAZING.  In just two weeks I have had multiple fillings and my wisdom teeth pulled.  This would have NEVER happened prior to meeting this doctor and his staff.  I can't wait to complete the rest of my dental work!  I absolutely recommend you trying them out.  You won't be dissapointed!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Caelin Gutierrez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfkEV60IrPrlPVbe77X9xLJTrOKSO6JRf5SF18wjIlm80l-ZxR8g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was admittedly very hesitant to go to a dentist again after a horrible experience at another location I had gone to my entire life. It was an emergency, though, and I called hoping for some understanding and hopefully a quick appointment. The woman on the phone was incredibly kind and comforting, and offered an appointment the very next morning.\n\nGoing in, I was somewhat nervous, but the pain wasn't going to go away so I bit the bullet. Upon first meeting Dr. Bove, I was immediately struck with how understanding he was. I wasn't chastised for my poor dental hygiene or dismissed, and we talked through possible solutions. I ended up removing the tooth due to struggling to reach it, and he was happy to answer my questions before and during the procedure. Also, I got to see a long piece of the tooth that was removed when I asked and that was pretty cool. The woman responsible for billing explained each item when I asked, and didn't try and upsell me; in fact, I asked for less aesthetic focused additions and she didn't seem annoyed at all.\n\nAll in all, I cannot recommend this enough. I'm currently home the day of the procedure, and I genuinely didn't know that it could be such a positive experience. I won't be going anywhere else for the foreseeable future.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Molina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLRKzqpfhwCMeyAcgq1CR3dZ20nkdIJYjU2xWfhPvGJZUC66g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Dr. Bove because I was having some extreme pain in the left side of my mouth. Dr. Bove found out I didn't have a cracked tooth as initially thought. I actually had a sinus infection that was causing tooth pain. Ms. Ashley was great as well. Very kind and patient. I will be back to get some work done I need. Thank you Bayview Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alyxandrea Geiger","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXJzGMXFrpVnQSivzCGUoWE2re8fCcAf5ZyUJ3BJAmMWfBmZGs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m not one to write an instant review. I wait for several visits and procedure before I share my opinion. I really want to get to know my provider. Now, 2 years after starting with Dr Bove I am\nhere to tell you, I chose Dr Bove based on the reviews given and they are right on! He is such a great dentist. I have previously had veneers, implants, root canals and crowns from other dentists in my 64 years and wish that I had had Dr Bove as my dentist for all me work. He is very conscientious, thorough, makes sure it’s done right with consideration for your limitations whether financial, emotional, or physical.\n\nOh, I’ve had other good dentists, but also other very bad dentists as I’ve followed my husbands military career for 30 years. I especially  don’t trust the ones that want you to give them a good review at your first visit.\n\nIn these last two years I have had Dr. Bove replace a very bad crown my previous dentist kept saying was fine and could never get to fit right. Dr Bove explained what was wrong with the crown and replaced it with a far superior and beautiful looking crown for less than the previous dentist charged me.\n\nHe has extracted a fractured tooth and taken care of 3 other routine dental issues over our 2 year relationship. Everything he has done has been superior quality, bites perfected and looks excellent.\n\nHe won’t bilk you for unnecessary work and he will offer his honest opinion about your dental health and needs.\n\nI have had a plethora of dental issues since I was young and try to take very good care of my teeth so a great dentist is very important to me. Dr. Bove knows I am willing to put care and money into keeping my teeth but never ever takes advantage of that. He lets me know what must be done vs what higher level options I have for aesthetics only. He work with and for me and I love that about him.\n\nI have my teeth cleaned 4 times a year by Marcus (my choice, I love having my teeth cleaned). He is wonderful and keeps track of my mouth health so well. I appreciate him so much as he is so thorough, gentle and a really nice guy. I always look forward to seeing him.\n\nThe front staff is warm and wonderful. Do they ever have a bad day? You wouldn’t ever know because they treat you like you wish everyone would. You feel uplifted and glad to be there as soon as you are greeted.\n\nI couldn’t ask for a better dentist and I am please to add my experienced 5 star review and say all the great reviews here are well deserved by Dr. Bove and his staff.\n\nWe drive a bit to see him but I would drive over an hour for this kind of excellent care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Otis Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVxbHEbf-k7vpyt7DZzcmbOiyOyW5tkj27btoLUu-XLrC-yvKs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dental office is outstanding from appearance to the staff. When making my appointment I was allowed/given the opportunity to complete my paperwork before my scheduled appointment.\n\nThe receptionist were great and very helpful from my phone call to me showing up. The dental assistants are outstanding as well and make you feel welcomed and appreciated as being there patient. The new state of the art technology has me feeling like being in the computer world of technology with being able to see everything going on and being able to ask questions about my teeth from being able to see what work is needed.\n\nBayview even take referrals and will give you a discount as well as the person you referred. I like this dentist office and location and glad to be a new patient of there’s.\n\nCoach O.\nOtis Brown","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ace chapman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXKJPTVRDryjZ6AhSwXFbg8sd2T4IUZHz289caSLFDdgab2pNACXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got my teeth cleaned here today, i purchased a cleaning for myself as a birthday gift to myself.\ni am SO happy. i had build up on my teeth that made them look gross honestly i didn’t know what to expect, i figured maybe they could get my teeth cleaned up some but they got it ALL removed.\nmy heart is so happy, they were so amazing to me, gave me so much information.\nthe ladies in the office were sweet.\nmy hygienist was caring.\n\u0026 they have top of the line equipment with cameras for teeth, 3D scanning \u0026 of course x-rays.\n10/10 would recommend.\nwhen leaving i received a pamphlet about their non insurance plans \u0026 i think they are GREAT options.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0bovUxz5jTvmYmQ5krrqxOSGSxNGbrFKpifGOeum0Jt4o8fTmDhLg0cXTkp6TvCr-b9_7sWAeB8kp2X0V5f1XgoeHKeq2E7TeXYMIuVy_MoCYstGoD0AcMpl1AeRUEjOA7_zib9g=k-no"],"When":"2022-10-11"},{"Name":"Stephanie Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX-cK1bJZNSLV2qaNzuuRwJfNisPOuz3TRgFTfbvmsfyWKhbp3K=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New favorite place! I’m a clef lip baby so I’ve always had people in my face/mouth due having work done and always got anxiety from bad experiences, sister comes here and recommended and felt welcomed, was asked how I was doing every 10 or so mins when getting teeth clean ( last dentist office NEVER asked) Dr \u0026 staff  explained everything properly, just overall nice and awesome experience! Felt anxious going in \u0026 left feeling happy and looking forward to coming here again❤️","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
