o-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Dr. Ungar to inquire about getting braces. In my situation, he could have easily gone ahead and scheduled treatmentmost places probably would have but he didn't. Instead, he was completely upfront and told me straight that braces weren't the right option for me right now. He explained everything clearly and honestly, without trying to push anything that would waste my time or money.\n\nIt's incredibly rare these days to find a doctor who prioritizes what's truly best for the patient over just making a sale. Dr. Ungar shot me straight, and I really respect that level of integrity. His straightforward approach made me feel valued and respected as a patient.\n\nIf you're looking for an orthodontist who's skilled, experienced, and most importantly genuinely honest, I highly recommend Dr. Ungar. Thank you for the great consultation!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Toby Haynes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOSqGXZbhWIvYX-zgKrs2ntGHy7gKT3oOL42lUiRGJDgZmnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Texas dental arts was an extremely pleasant office. But the office was very nice and my appointment started when it was supposed to. The technician was good and explained everything to me clearly. Really love this dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJEg11BzOLlYPmefKs6hXn16RSf4cokNbp2-Zcdy0H1J6XMTA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Texas Dental Arts! Dr. Unger is very professional and knowledgeable. He was even able to assist with a dental issue I was having over the weekend and it was very appreciated. The front office staff is also very sweet and friendly. I always have a great visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathy Cyphers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKZs7NSH571dLuqIkMmrHsogj-TdgbW1X4gG8k6YP3y-0lm8w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"