tal Arts is wonderful. Dr. Unger and his staff are professional and gental. I’ve been coming here for years. Highly recommended this dental office. Their in office dental plan is helpful as well. I won’t go anywhere else. Dr Unger is conservative, but thorough with his treatment plans. Great doctor and staf!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
