 Manager, Kirstie! She always has a smile on her face and is incredibly helpful. She’s definitely a huge plus to the team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Ray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRSbFkPIZilvj0nl59U1bTvYMLTSpyhiCPgznoRR_bqQmA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I could give this place 10 stars I would! I called them after I an emergency with my tooth and they got me in same day literally 15 mins after I called and they said come on in. Doctor and all staff are super friendly and very organized. I really have to thank the lady that worked me in I think her name is Claudia and she is very sweet and explained everything perfectly. This will be my dentist forever now.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yvette Michael-Elgin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIqi7QxRaoNz_9rYtzdvoP5hR6lZuDrXIqrpPGF7OQylJ8F4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t trust quickly.They were very kind, nice. They kept me informed about what was going on and the things that was being done. Doctors solid  and nice their nurses very informative and kind, clean work environment. They we're efficient, Direct and caring. Thank you for being so helpful and caring. I was able to feel safe, connected and able to trust them with my care and concerns. I give them 5 stars. Thank you for all you do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna de Socarraz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ0PgvJ9S-x17DoelxU3skXXuT7OWiKdkciai3vkWLwbww8JA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a very informative and pleasant visit today with Dr. Taylor. The staff were very friendly and efficient. The facility is nice and has a calming atmosphere..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Derrick Torrente","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJxEf4AM6NWaJUir4OyJT70XU4CItEgC6m_0xD2tzfunVaFlg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"You all are amazing.  Very nice staff! . I came in for my appointment. The doctor immediately addressed my concerns and setup a plan. I was able to have 2 fillings and a crown done that same day. Very great experience 10 out of 10. I look forward to my next visit. Thank you all for the great work you all do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jo Ireland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI60DV3KGgqtvTtil67q-SfZoRrEWY0LMwkDahyuw9rhQW_XQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every person in this office is so nice and knowledgable.\nEvery.  Single. One.\n\nFrom the scheduler,  to the front desk,  to the insurance person, to the hygienist and the doctors, they are uber-professional. The practice is way ahead of the curve on technology and it's so impressive. Both Dr. Wilkinson's are kind, sensitive to a person's apprehension and are perfectionists when it comes to service and product quality. And it helps to know that there is never a long wait from your appointment time.\n\nIf that doesn't convince you, you should know that I fly in from out of state to dentist appointments here! You can't go wrong at Forest Trail Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Imelda Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwaGEDgivTp98YNZ84THPBx_qQ0DmOT2SENzvVLjJZvcNRIHs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The office flowed so well. Great team and great vibes in the office. Taylor was thorough and did an amazing job on my cleaning. Stayed for same day treatment and they addressed all my concerns and needs. Thanks for a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
