menities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Lisa Truitt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJnIksWHZfrftrdGYXJKWcPmElVgBHSSBFNZYhy4U5DswJRPjT=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the staff at Temple Dental Trails!!  I had a  dental emergency prior to leaving town. They were able to get me in when I called after 12 noon, on a Friday! Dr Craig and the staff were able to see me and rectify the issue. They are young and positive high-energy.  Five star staff and service every time!!  ❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cort Spellman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJNq8bHMu7RLhh5yT8yKmscngf__freR5yPm63tCOypPC2vzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I switched to Temple Dental Trails so our little one could go to the same dentist as us. I’m glad we did -- it’s been a pleasant dentistry experience! Jessica (hygienist) has been very helpful and the ceiling-mounted TVs are pretty nice when you’re in the dentist chairs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Courtney Diggs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-_cZVCRyqJKJDlcckPio0UTFlUasSpGaRHfMEWq83qWR0Jw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Newton has changed my life for the better by giving me a beautiful new smile. Her bedside manner is amazing and she was almost as excited for the final product as I was! The dental assistants have all been so sweet as well, specially Ashley, Melissa, and Lindsey. I felt so comforted by their presence even when I was nervous. Dr. Newton is honest and knows what she’s doing and has really been so attentive throughout this long process of mine. So blessed to have found Temple Dental Trails!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Scalf","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDZgaqKWdULLJ72_rSROUbMKlQ3eFLYiekbz6Hpu4bg-hNRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We are very happy with the care we receive here. 😊 Always professional, organized, clean, and details are well thought out. We’ve been patients with regular cleanings for years now, and needed my first filling with them yesterday. It was fast, painless, and feels great today. Thanks y’all!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bria Land","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKdZhvw0jjOJLyP1_jDc8fxr02ZoZT5vwBCUzQF-zZ6lQLZLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff here was absolutely amazing ! From my first call ( and I called several times just asking crazy questions 🤣 ) and every time Angela was so warm and nice and informative and so sweet ! When I was welcomed in, the office was beautiful and clean and again I received a warm greeting . When I went back I was welcomed in by Ashley who made sure to make me feel good and comfortable and even gave me a compliment to make me smile . Then when Dr.Newton came in she blew me completely away she was soooo kind sooo helpful and extremely informative about everything . She explained everything to me top to bottom and she went above and beyond! She educated me through the entire process . I was blown away by the service here. I had an emergency and they helped me SAME DAY ! They now have me as a consistent client and I can’t wait to see all the beautiful staff again!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Autumn Brewer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQf7tNczyE9896mOCWCAy1B_Z6sqU1fu20Mtktq_UhAdoPNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was a new patient yesterday after changing my insurance. From the front desk to the back to the house, staff was all incredible. They were punctual, knowledgeable, and genuinely seemed to want the best for their patients. I was not wanting to go because I knew I hadn’t been in a while, and they made me feel so comfortable and gave me some pointers to get back on track. Always making sure I was comfortable. Happy to have found this place to keep my health on track.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharon Timothy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUEPJyR6v1kqJ4VsKp-Kq_6ZjpVNBa8Q1n6nYYCcviyzyC6mvwY5w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first visit to the dental office. Upon entering the office my allergies to the numerous plug ins really made it impossible to sit in the waiting room. It’s very unfortunate companies use these strong chemical base products due to so many who have sensitivity to these things. I had to wait in my car until it was time to be called back, I did make the front desk person aware of this.\nOn the better side of my visit, the staff was very nice, the office was very clean and up to date on the newest procedures. The dental hygienist did a fantastic job and walked me through each step and explained everything she was doing. It was a painless cleaning. The dentist who came in to check everything out was friendly and her suggestion on my dental treatment were on spot.\nI would suggest friends and family to give this place a try.\nIf you are highly allergic to strong scents you might need to wait in the car until you are called back. I have hopes my concerns about this will be taken in to account and they can remove these plug ins, they really are not necessary in providing good care in fact it to some it may work against them.\nI did give a five star due to the fact I did get great service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Sawyer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_EfJwE40UQHKUpMLshLQXCOzZIDZpF0rYI0FV1NQvNjoGR5YMig=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m the person that puts off going to the dentist because of previous dental trauma. The team was wonderful and kind from check in through checking out. They made sure I was comfortable and I had input on my treatment plan. I look forward to working with them on my treatment plan.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
