 cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Alma Alvarez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULREqdyc5VrKEKp7zaCYJLP-0OlakoXkUYyuIyCYHux0aWllc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had the best experience here! Since my first visit. Everyone is friendly and welcoming. I just had composite bonding for cosmetic reasons and I love my results. Thank you for all you do!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rebekah Mayne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKIS2fFcMm9uZRny2S1FsbPHyLhbcLnwnxbiQW5Dm6f5pCdwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So thankful for Dr Callier and his staff. Their office brought me so much peace and I couldn’t be more grateful for the experience I had.  They truly care about people. Would and will recommend them to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Casey Coats","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVifH0E5IsBnPDG38V-kafz9sQaitbFAzrHBp5EecMBQhbhlBWr=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Callier and the team at North Texas Family \u0026 Cosmetic Dentistry took such great care of my son who needed a tooth pulled today. They got us in for a same day appointment, and they were all so warm and friendly. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dylan Matthews","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVsLIs99TYsgPtitQdd4ontwSlOLFJ55cB_ZSLiFUiM_A4uNL-k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I got my teeth cleaned, and it was the best experience. The people were friendly. They were very professional and especially the front office. Tammy signed me in and my goodness she made me feel so welcomed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chad Swoveland (Macbeth91)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkvYTyX7-7p8IW8qLzl0q3nXI0T51iL8VnesIIEj62J6S55YdS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This will be an easy review. Office staff was completely over the top courteous and professional! Right away you can tell that they want you to feel relaxed and comfortable.\n\nDental hygienist provide excellent care and are detailed in their work.\n\nDr. Callier is the definition of the standard of how every dentist should operate. Meaning if you look up dentist in the dictionary you should see Dr. Callier as the reference.\n\nOverall could not recommend this practice enough. 10/10","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie DeLand","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVUPwmIcr-AumzxwGhE31rIIZj5FpXL6YY36ZWrbm5DEo2iD_HABg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been seeing Dr. Collier for over a year now. He takes great care of my teeth and checks to see how I am doing after something more major. I would recommend them to anyone looking for great dental health and care. Everyone in the office from the front office to the assistants and hygienist are very polite and caring.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdYswGjGvfM1QIzL4MzAnBMkxW5_VzlzIQmqdgLL7nn1ylFlA5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Callier and his staff are very professional, knowledgeable and personable. They know me when I walk in the door and provide very friendly, caring service. They explain and encourage proper care of teeth. I had some comprehensive work done and they were concerned about my comfort and results with every step taken. They worked with my insurance favorably and effortlessly for me. I'm glad I left a chain outfit because I receive comprehensive personal care here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donna Padgett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0EwaCLf9OtXx7jWcRWRf-0IzA9wW6hlzCVJRsx8XPyRgt0Bk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is the best office staff ever, and you’ll not find a better doctor than Dr.   Callier!  They go above and beyond to make you feel comfortable and confident about your smile. After all your teeth are one of the first thing people see when you speak. They’re all amazing and you’re like family to them for they care so much! ❤️\nWay to go North Texas Family and Cosmetic Dentistry!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
