],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"106353346738867923820","name":"One Dental Texas Cypress (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106353346738867923820"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Cypress","street":"7014 Fry Rd SUITE 108","city":"Cypress","postal_code":"77433","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Andrew Cabrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURR38y104UdKfPKOtrJ2roE8Q2gTpqIM0eFy2-OdMY48vHD0OR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down, best ever dental clinic. Dr. Trung Trinh is an expert when it comes to planning the treatment based on a variety of factors. I really do appreciate this dental clinic. It's truly been a huge blessing on my part getting my professionally fitted dental implant. Highly recommended on my list.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Norah Heizenberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6IVx53Jvi0o_lGuizUx24CaIlE6jDd9aU18Iazk3A106plmQ_hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist I’ve ever had. Nice staff. No long waiting time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Huang","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBKJRzaxvfQIBEOiCHUxxTa0z-ZAt0Dl9AJY-6IEBKcB5rYg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"In brief summary, this clinic falsely claimed I had 8 cavities when I only had 1. I would not recommend this place based on my experience, as it seems they were more interested in making money than providing honest dental care.\n\nI visited this dental clinic two years ago for a routine check-up, the dentist claimed that I had 8 cavities. What raised my suspicion was that he explained to me where the cavities were based on pictures taken, not X-rays. After that, they proceed to show me the pricing, but I decided not to proceed with any treatments due to my doubts.\n\nHalf a year later, I went back to NY and saw another dentist for a second opinion. the NY dentist found only one cavity, which I had it treated. A year after that, I moved and visited a different dentist, who confirmed that I had no other cavities.\n\nAlso, that 1 cavity that I had was not any of the 8 he mentioned. So either, I got cavity after the visit or this clinic can't identify cavities accurately.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chad Harrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJwHKUzcShEr6aDMhTSxPs5Y5PKszgt0PwtyLYJodiONnGkwNs=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have dreaded going to the dentist and have not been in years due to horrible past experiences. Dr. Tran and the whole team have truly changed my life and gave me reasons to smile again 😊.  I highly recommend One Dental Texas, as this is the best dentist ever. They are very prompt and truly care and appreciate their patients. I now look forward to my next appointment. ✅️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mechelle Bodwin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPFxvtJMdBF2kxWdSPexoNbTXa7R50evzdDKgqwJ76MCVsDGBhyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"💕Hands down this is the most friendliest and best dental place around! I was seen by Dr. Joshua Tran and assisted by Amy Nguyen and they are soooooo incredibly nice!  I had to get 2 cavities and a deep cleaning and I was so very nervous but Dr. Tran was so very gentle and patient with me. He didn't hurt me and talked me through the whole process. I recovered nicely and can't wait to see him again when I have to.\n\nAlso, Amy walked me thought the entire financial process of putting braces on my older child and she was so knowledgeable and friendly and calming about the entire procedure. I never felt more comfortable than I did here and I will be sure to recommend all of my friends and family members to come here for their dental needs.\n\nAlso, they have VERY FLEXIBLE HOURS which is so important when you have kids in school that are involved in extra curricular activities, so they are available on Saturdays and Sundays which is sooooooooo convenient!!!\n\nI will be sure to tell my friends and family members about this dentist office for sure!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Monique Jonquitud","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUwOd3S20TkfyjZrO0zUm0OFpMBlXITQhylLnFQSEgiwpWsIwY8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Yes I prefer this dentist they go above and beyond??","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paul Bergeron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJR0V8D-BNfnjYmvk944TFC1iq5yfbyAWJ4XTK0pBbp-7A8qg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"New Patient when in to talk ! Took me in got X-rays, consultation on my dental problem , showed and explained the problems I had , explained the procedures to fix the problems, and how much the cost  My question was how soon could he start !! To my surprise he started right then !!  Medium Deep cleaning , 3 cavities filled, preparation for crown including core build up and impressions all in one sitting ! All for a price that made smile! Amy and Dr T are such pleasurable people it was so nice just talking to them ! Amy and Dr T worked on me with the consideration as to my comfort and explanation of what they where doing as they progressed in my dental work ! True professionals! And then explained the care and restrictions  I had to do until the crown was finished! And as soon as the  crown returns they will call me to come in ! The best experience I have had in all of my visits to different dentist through the years !!👍 Lots of parking nice and quit office great people couldn’t have asked for a better experience! I am one very satisfied customer!😁","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Ivy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUd9uZDVa66Zb59zKvrcHtbiVIdU1rjDiYJSpMCA1uKNIiokfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was having problems with a sore tooth on a Sunday.  Amy found me an appointment on the same day and I could not be happier with the care and professionalism of her and Dr. T.  They gave me a full exam, explained my issue and the required treatment to repair the cavity which was done during the visit.  Dr T is a kind and skilled dentist who made the experience as pleasant as possible.  He also laid out a complete dental plan for me to affordably do some other work I want to get done.  Excellent professional service and very fair pricing. I highly recommend 1 Dental!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
