ought I should come to a dentist here in Austin!\nVery professional, thorough, compassionate and o felt like home. Coming to the dentist is not my favorite but this place made me feel taken cared of from scheduling, checking in, dental hygienist thanks to my hygienist and the Dr Nguyen!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3H3ivxbE4hSzfbo0ej4e4S5UpbqmD2ZfOJZLYPKlQIQSyMgfj5ZaqMnXcW_UEHA0v7KZnTSji0CF1vgZ8ORy33aVbiJI3V1nA2we30CVaIrli1Cj5B7PqHU7PrJdlqksCJMzmdTVY9IjM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn35ff5Fr__W5AFsV5pusgYuYwQPaZkjQlztaoD2HSCn275B-fMiijaY7_fiheZXjNSdxP4HdLox8u2ISQxdh_Japr1BbjmQr6ZKe5EIoinQNCMX9h7rvyQG9g9qChR3Snk-kcYdKSigzFNW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2NEfcQEke94yoPib6gGizl11nJQWqyBI8eWF3267tdjKTttXLWewzK7QHbTG3Scef7jrPwrSsEdoHV1amTaSz-goQsg1vlG59ZL1u3pFcRN0PP-c8Tb0reF_GQvWzx6aocJsTrsOExaDo=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0SyLFUvs8gsTG8k3szOql7zpxDBwXHXnbH-ed2-8vs3gSz9bXdvpRQ6k49QxFDcM9SWHaTrNLnTsaHXWPJkOwtjAQQt7Vc7ExEOrhh0t-jTihkpoKO3RzNRVjoErmPd9oF60XvsNCEFjL6=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-10"},{"Name":"Tim Alumkal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsn2WnMlTBh-LZlS4pmYt8Jk2i_RzsrRRPaR6qKC0IIvKIbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an issue with an older crown and they found an appointment time to address the issue. Lauren and Dr Minnie were kind, professional and efficient! I’ve never had a bad experience here. Everyone is like family and genuinely cares! I know I’m in great hands with routine dental needs to specialized care! Keep up the great work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheyenne Crouse","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXv9iYCYcE8B-oanOYKAqRrTn8aurNnSB7Q4jN7VLCnF3L9EQA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The office is always clean and very welcoming. The staff is kind and very caring. Dr. Sean performed my filling and he was gentle and quick with preforming the work. I recommend coming to this dentistry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Sieloff","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgfQJmx30wUEZNsxuEMfh_8CSzTaVdpFd36-orUl-Kb1hUHsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent. Careful. Precise.  Explains procedures.  The hygienists are the best. The entire practice is top notch.  I had to work through 3 other dentists before happily finding Dr Sean, it was a good search.  One other quality point - after a crown he CALLED ME to check on how things were going.  That’s a first","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Huong Theresa Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBvf6bBPYDdPBKePxdHFnmCDoZHAlvRFzqucDBhFU7fy1PRfOxHA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been going here for a decade ! Always a pleasant experience. Dr. Minnie is very sweet, personable, patient, gentle, and thorough - everything you'd want when seeing a dentist ! She's the best one I've ever had, and over the years I have felt more educated about my own teeth and how to care for them better. The entire staff  is amazing, from Ken /Lindsey at front desk to all the dental techs /hygienists I've had (Ellen, Paige, and others) - everyone has been so nice and friendly. Never felt rushed or pressured at all. A truly wonderful clinic. You leave feeling like they really care about their patients as well as each other.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yvng Lex","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU2UM67TciyMJpwky4_mJly1oPrzSZTnVbuOVVZyrzVRIx5nN8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Honestly, my experience was beyond amazing. I came in with excruciating pain. They immediately check me out and let me know that I needed an extraction. The dentist went out of his way to move my appointment up to the next day because my pain was so bad. He pulled the tooth out in less than 20 minutes. I had no pain during the operation. I still have no pain a day later I’m not swollen and they sent me home with good postop care. I was so intimidated before I got my tooth pulled now I’m super ready to get the other three out. I love Tech Ridge 🦷 dental. They genuinely made me feel safe and comfortable 💯🖤","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Nwswa2QnhRwCYxkz56lVGkcthF_yzzziik7Xrg0nVtjZzpwz6e_1NzlUZb61Uag_PdwU0P1sOr0kgacR5FXMSqU_KJsh9333t9IP6vx-qbup9t8IThd0IuPmXXyULmjXrzM9y46NKsD49=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1-pRXzlP1vbhqwGspSbNAVQkSlLW-qYaBbSjPI2MpVv2JflhGaNKkfC_odYz6T1Fn2TDgwLz1yqWvxO96smbqS4TcQCRBNuxbhGspHgYGD6hWJFk913a5_EcUGwKc9tx8PBhqIgdO_sPAw=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-6"},{"Name":"Karen s","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImrc1hH7TAk2XXQpaiOyCKOFRTxfyTOiblEI2jmwV5HVSy-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The dentists and staff at Tech Ridge Dental are amazing. I can't say enough good things about them. Dr. Minnie, Dr. Sean, Lindsay, Ken, Ellen, Dulce and all their awesome staff go above and beyond each and every visit. Tech Ridge Dental has been my family's dentist for over a decade, and we love coming here. They are very professional, knowledgeable, friendly, and prompt, and they are a team that enjoys working and being together and it shines through. Before discovering Tech Ridge Dental, I was so nervous about going to the dentist, but they have changed that for me. They have created something really special here, and I am so overjoyed that we found them all those years ago.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIEdrmoBsGP0bNoqmsYM4iRU1h5Gh8sNj9UNZ3c_RkOp91obA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently had to have two root canals followed by temporary crowns and then permanent crowns. The root canals were performed elsewhere, but I went to Tech Ridge Dental for the temporary and permanent crowns. They did an excellent job, answered any questions I had, and the atmosphere was