 orthodontic service is exceptional. The waiting room is also really cozy.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0XUQa1zbBwrWlwzla8piN4_CCyidDCab0jth_wjgfBa0MZRhku_ZDW6qu-Ddl77vnaT2qpHQ6_XGodsBUhDviOw4ocXtSmGaYwQMN6JkwDkJjuVOZGXUEA8Yu37QEbsE0R0Qdi=k-no"],"When":"2025-4-11"},{"Name":"Cassie","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYDUspEZSK_GrIfgbdRD0fR3zbXeYuqz6X405cPFh3ldTyg-QWzg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is very friendly, they really work with you as far as scheduling all of my kids at the same time, which makes it super easy to be seen. They offer care credit too.  They care about your mouth and they really help coach you on how to get your mouth health back.  They also make sure you are comfortable, pain wise, and are very Gentle.  The Doctors and Dental assistants and Hygienists, and staff All are AMAZING.  I have been bringing my kids here since they were little,They are teens now.  They do take medicaid as well and now they have an Orthodontist who comes to do consultations here and does the work here as well.  Its a great place.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3kEc7TA3D0aGC5eKncJkOPgubB0gMICKAwHxQXNtOVEPqTx84KdOZz4xft4UuuWJQMGAvVylZqaSHdsMxhXyhOKmrDobwW6fxqYOfdlYcgoP5fYln7EaJvvS9MBrUNuquLWSIyrg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0zTX8_MW_ddK8MG4v1_KcQ7P1zjIciEtCz2cLzxyrADTPCcABbL68D2WLtH5wMy-bd7JQjKrF3hLlJfWFJcq4hJbRZiaohvniBoV9pspDin9sGdMHCdOy15HQZNHz7yc1vHuT7=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2kQdwhaXyKutjG3P2SAG3v2A47-6iWuTkOVgmahTjX0VAwFn0a8T9rlO5uSdDBpq_JRhAdGlkHGoCcAqf5ODt7UuW0lRw7_TOSCj8tq--nea4fvnb0WQmzfOdvJ9fbZMYcjDEw=k-no"],"When":"2021-9-16"},{"Name":"Christy Fox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU10HIm2cLmknoNEEMqHGrhogZOz0xTrPyJ0-NbLpxaZrk8qUrnEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Tran and all her staff were amazing. She gives the best Dental shot I’ve ever received","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiara Rivers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJSt-bGhNYDMURijlosIUnYgBVwScLVRf_DyPINyCiV_i4nNA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My father(Walter) had an appointment today with this facility and called me while still at his appointment so thrilled with the service he received. They were so nice and kind to him and made him feel good about his smile and feel hopeful about his future smile. So grateful he ran across good people and good service. Highly recommend! Thank you for your kindness to my father!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mandi McArthur","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpkTiiwFQT0ssLAmQa9xeWwugaxRhMQexrDA20c4rVc_iQ8iAB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love Texas Dentistry in Kaufman! They are always on time and fit all 3 of my kids in at the same time frame. The dentist and staff are very friendly and considerate. They work so well with kids. They know what they are doing, have great technology, and build great rapport with all of us.  I am so thankful to raise my kids coming here and to get to go here myself!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crystal Briette","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVVKa2uMPvNT-IzwTgXQmH2npxs9qjffFoVnaqCBdC7om1yiMo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Edit to my previous review. They just called to “Release” my son’s appointment because they did not like my previous review. Sorry but not very professional.\n\nThe dentist and staff are nice but their scheduling and pricing is not great. They constantly call to reschedule. The first few rescheduled appointments were just to go in 30 minutes earlier but just now they tried to get me to come over a week earlier because my son is currently scheduled on spring break and apparently they can’t do that appointment time anymore. So why schedule me if they can’t do that day? The lady on the phone didn’t know. She said she could not answer that. Not only that but my last appointment I was fully paid to cover this appointment and all of a sudden I have to pay an additional almost $100.  Lady in the phone said my insurance didn’t cover what they said it would cover and I now have to pay again. Weird to me because they had already looked into my insurance previously and we had already discussed coverage. I paid what was not covered at the first appointment and this appointment was supposedly covered (1st appointment was to make the crown. This next appointment is to put it in).","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melinda Estrada","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIa-977TRqxzHNOQ9UD6maj6J8F-31whyDZJVrO1jsWRhosSz2y=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When I tell you this place is the best please believe me😭 I’ve had really bad experiences at dentist offices and I kept away for awhile until a tooth was bothering and I knew I had to make an appointment. I used to go to Jefferson in dallas bc I worked over there. They are the ones that scared me. So I decided to make an appointment here and they made everything so easy for me. They listened to me and didn’t show any judgment towards me. They made me feel safe. ❤️","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
