enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Nic Vita","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWrPYVCUGQfIltPz9PQl2b6XA3nyq7yR8ex-ywa0XwoVWpejzn5eg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best dentist experience I've ever had in my life by far here. I used dread going to the dentist for over ten years after a horrific experience with someone else and after coming here one time i feel completely comfortable and don't even think about it anymore. Dr John is the best there -kind, explains things very well and is very attentive and makes things go smoothly. Sandra  was amazing as well,  also the best experience I've had getting my teeth deep cleaned which usually  sucks but somehow this was pleasant as well. I could never go anywhere else again, even if i moved i think i would still travel here just so i know I'm getting the best i can get !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Peggy Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIm2AlaDpQzKB9VyfEnM3zNw8miYI6Yjunmx9NaK4Bv9yXGEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It is truly my pleasure to write this review for Eagle Dental! If I could give them 10 stars I would! Dr. John, Sandra and their entire team are the BEST! Our family has been seeing Dr. John for over 10 years, and the genuine care they show is second to none. Not only are they extremely knowledgable, but the way they communicate is very much appreciated as well. I give Eagle Dental my highest recommendation -- if you're looking for a dentist anywhere in the Fort Bend area, look no further than Dr. John and her amazing team at Eagle Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raji John","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILxtTVxOkcdjHxB4MIsMYt8g1VFGe9o8R_kFZcn2gFlH5rJQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. John is an excellent doctor. She was very caring and responsive. Her work was awesome. Staff was great.I love to recommend the eagle dental was the best place to go for your dental needs .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"NKS","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhxsSAbsasKYNFDveW-grIoe0DtqgIftBAi3h6SzeqWKv6gA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Don't think twice about making an appointment - call them now!\n\nIt has been a long road to find a good biological dentist. I have been to 4 in the last couple of years, so I know what I'm talking about. In fact, I'm usually hesitant to write reviews even though I rely heavily on reviews when I seek out a new business. This is why I decided I must do one for Dr. John at Eagle Dental Texas.\n\nDr. John is exactly what every dentist needs to be - honest and considerate. Additionally, her staff is equally amazing, from the front desk to the dental assistants and hygienists, too. I rarely find a doctor and extended team that are equally great, but they have somehow managed that. After 3 visits and 2 different kids taken as patients, I've interacted with 90% of the staff now and really have nothing negative to say about any of them.\n\nThe only pro-tip I recommend is if you don't get in touch with a human on your first attempt, it's better to call a little later instead of leaving a message.\n\nWhy are you still reading reviews? Call them NOW!\n:)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alita McAdory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdBS71PKucC0Nw_SWjl_kWEN7X7vsG2focw3rhRIxOCl1Im8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr John and Dr. Rodriguez are both amazing providers and outstanding people, who I consider as friends. The holistic\napproach they use for providing dental care is cutting edge and refreshing.  I appreciate the care they take to ensure that my individual needs are being met with the natural products and philosophy. Great job to everyone at Eagle Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Just Here","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKqKL-D4pucZ_H4eIrBt56AzXtb1BdbVYv1VLFBPNSwfJwBCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The hygienist, Sandra is THE BEST! I’ve been a patient here for many years, and with reason. Dr. Rodriguez and staff are professional, personable, the office is comforting, and CLEAN. I recommend this dental practice to anyone and everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Toni Gauthier","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIADWRZCBziijrny7QoYionnTJjeNQvOMhrOByHbH-50F0Etw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My Dentist Dr. John is awesome!  She is friendly, very  knowledgeable, caring about my teeth, pain and me as a person. She even calls me the same night after sitting in her chair to make sure I am okay. Everyone at Eagle Dental is friendly, kind, considerate people who take an interest in their patients. They are all knowledgeable people who are willing to listen and help all the patients in their care. I am very happy to be a patient.😃","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cleveland Sterling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-S3QnuSfEehF-mlOhZDax-L67c1Izcc8FVeIAm2Glz8rpN9o=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the new location!! Everyone was very friendly and welcoming. My doctor and associates were very detailed about explaining the process and what was the steps needed for recovery.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
