:"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true},{"name":"Paid parking lot","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Makani Plunkett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6h4l6mlDFGOSyE1Pwn0tCuD9MyYrksVMYrjbfzN8sCg4u-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Bullock is the best dentist in town. He is very knowledgeable and isn’t judgmental. He also isn’t boring and shares with his patients. He understands when you have to unexpectedly bring your kids and the entire staff helps. He makes going to the dentist easy!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christie Garanzuay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrv_2iYalmlcvDz4bG4Li260lMQuskT18EAsWhLUYAEXgtiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience! Dr. Bullock is kind, thorough, and explains everything clearly. Taylor, the hygienist, was gentle and friendly. Brittany, the dental assistant, made the whole visit easy and comfortable. Tonya at the front desk was so welcoming and helpful. Awesome team—I definitely recommend this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jared Demartini","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaEaQiPiuze-b_rlfaEVy7WdDD5ClkllDDTWMepx3L6aeCbw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Kinsley, Taylor, and Brittany were all so helpful taking care of me and keeping me at ease! Dr Bullock fixed my crown quickly and perfectly. They even talked some Pokémon card news with me. Would strongly recommend if you want affordable, personable, and expert care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ken Fowler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIqoO92qWyzOCUBXq2dspjz0Xltt4_hV2lm078lxq98qF51Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Bullock and his staff are amazing! As a new patient, I was scheduled in a timely fashion. You can tell Dr. Bullock and his staff work extremely well together. They listened to all my concerns and developed a plan. I had 6 crowns done in one sitting. No pain at all. I’m so glad I found Chimney Rock! Thank you so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hannah Ariola","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEo3gOz8TQlJcJU5afZwbHNfdV7tfU81PyClxhm6g-siou-Gs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First visit to Chimney Rock Family Dentistry and it was a great experience. Dr. Bullock and the team got me scheduled quickly and took care of everything I needed without the usual dental runaround. Amberlee was welcoming, knowledgeable, and answered all my questions with patience.\n\nThe dental hygienist did an incredibly thorough cleaning and made the whole visit comfortable. Teeth feel so fresh and so clean clean!\n\nHighly recommend this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sharone d thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUctZg5XpOcAkgzaPJR_Le9vHlfi69yQWjS7T7QCkxtQksnqDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Chimney Rock truly makes the dental experience pleasant. The staff is amazing, and Dr. Bullock is exceptionally gentle and kind. He takes the time to explain the entire process both before and during each procedure, which is incredibly reassuring. I experience significant anxiety when it comes to dental visits, but Chimney Rock has made it far less intimidating for me. They even offer you a blanket if you’re cold. I am so grateful for this office and highly recommend them for all your dental needs—they are truly the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jason \u0026 Amanda May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNZ317ZsKOoLbRRAsV91PmE_WW_Mg9cbQlCu2sDY7Lv3WOhXsR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 !\nThe staff is so friendly, the office is clean, and every chair is in its own room so you aren’t right next to someone else getting a cleaning or work done which is a big plus for me. Highly recommend for the competency/ friendliness of the staff from the front office to hygienist and Dr. Bullock. All are great and take their time answering any questions or concerns I’ve had. Very happy to have found this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Boone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUlMxC3APZU_TqDIn0Wy0EnpyVcv6K1a1G_66VBPCHUrijf3ESw0w=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Chimney Rock Family Dental with Dr. Bullock and his team. Taylor cleaned my teeth and always does a great job. From the warm welcome to the thorough, gentle treatment, everyone made me feel comfortable and well-cared for. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
