/ALV-UjWfQ4G1HCXjBJc0bnNcw3Borf0aXXhKDLgJmpCBtDuOjzXXcd1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I would give this place 20 stars if I could. I hate I didn’t find this place sooner . The staff is absolutely amazing!! \u0026 the Dr Turner was AMAZING as well.  He was Very knowledgeable and Kind. you can tell he truly cares for his patients . His associate Dentist or the 2nd dentist.\nHe was so kind and down to earth as well. I was like woah everyone is so nice and kind , not just doing their job but going above and beyond.\nI’m always honest on my reviews so trust me when I say definitely give them place a try . You most definitely won’t regret it and won’t want to go to another dentist office!!\nGod bless .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debra Mayes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXuYRAJiSgUZ0Xh5HoUOvQKcNDcKrlmZK3FA72CH55Bos-WwW6U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Dr. Senior Turner he will go out of he’s way to help people I can tell he’s very Compassionate in helping others and the work he does I fully trust he’s Opinion.  Because I have been Traumatized by these our Dentists And its very hard for me to trust people when there doing work on your face Dr. Turner tells you what he can and can’t do not others Dentists in Abilene Tx they don’t he’s very friendly and Detailed  And organizedI I  love that he looks at you with no judgment eyes like other dentists but staff needs  improvement or pointers  when It comes to billing write recipes for work done  or itemize work done and tell them about there balance because trust is at jeopardy especially in business not to argue with patients if you can’t show it on paper what was done and balance then take responsibility for that do be friendly and bring patients and explain work done if we don’t understand and then let us know about patients balance please don’t hide that from patients because the older we are the more we the patients need to be shown because we have to budget and have to make our money Stretch out with a lot of things out and  be friendly like doctor Tunner it will help he’s business  I wish  I had found you when I first had problems if I had more money to fix my the rest of my teeth he would be my first choice Thank You Dr. Turner for helping me and going out of your way we need more Dentist like you 🙏🏽❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bryan “Boaty” Boatright","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXs1Lf5v8EUGtJwewPOg-j6R1TKVUZ7HfK4z6KYtllhZAq29PkL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Turner is the best dentist I have ever been a patient of in my entire life. Dr. Garrett comes in second. But if I was standing in front of either I would flip flop my rating of both of these great Dentists. I am a big baby when it comes to needles and applying local anesthetic and Dr. Turner always makes it a painless process. When it comes to cost, I am out of network and I pay mostly out of pocket, so what I am saying is that the procedures I have had are far less than what I have paid out of network. Great team of dental assistants and front desk team. Thank you for your care and jokes. I feel comfortable after 5 minutes in the chair.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike Thornton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJs3fFH4yX_6QwxKo-8NVjLL7FrSGfkaMzopEFy04o6NqTR6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Stan Turner doesn’t mess around. He is very thorough. When he does a filling, it feels natural. I’ve been other places where you can feel the filling. He is very passionate about his job and getting the job done correctly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Plenty Organics","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-ujIE45daDbRfT_6BwOZ-vRppNx-bScv7GoBk_9r6juvHBCw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is one of the best offices I have ever been too. All of the staff members are very knowledgeable, technology is advanced, and the office provided me with much needed advice about hygiene and care. Their standard of care is impeccable and I am very grateful their office accommodates both adults and children. You cannot go wrong with choosing Dr. Garrett/ Dr. Turner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"harluy art","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL-UeRQNDcCYeL7sizzSXwEDG4PfQg4N1-Js1pjkIs7Dhau=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was seen by Stan Turner for a root canal and he is the most caring dental professional I’ve ever been seen by!! Him and his staff are amazing and I will definitely be a loyal patient to Turner dental. Thank yall so much for your kindness and providing the bestest of the best care💜💜","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Strom-Kieschnick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBNQ1JCMqV0gHhrnCa_ArdAHm9DCN-Fvc2DwkOJrBt5M0rnWmEEQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Stan Turner is always so thorough and helpful with our whole family for over 10 years. I love the bird feeder \u0026 water features out most the exam windows to help calm the environment 🐦.\nI have an allergy to sedation and he did research and a consult to make sure he could provide me the best care and he was amazing throughout my treatment.  Today was Halloween Eve and the office was dressed up, pretty cool!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patsi Young","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJGDft-MGBxmyGPULEd1-znzLHDhj8Ls-Nt0_SY7ZKzMrfPFg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Garrett and his team are wonderful.  The office itself is beautiful.  No pain, no anxiety,  makes you want to go to the dentist. Thank you all very much.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
