ents","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Carla Harper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW7Jvx16H_u2M9enth0z1aqvgj97lonr89FIimSEhnjh9viBYNn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really don't like dentists and because I haven't been in so long my teeth are horrible. But Dr Oakey and his staff put me at such ease and helped me to understand why my teeth are as bad as they are, it was actually a pleasant visit to the dentist! I'm going to leave some \"before\" pictures here and will post some \"after\" pictures. They take their time with you and they explain everything to you, nothing is going to be coming out of left field or an ambush. That's another fantastic thing about this dental office, you don't feel rushed to get in, pay your money and now get out.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3eyvAB5RaUFpR5ac6LNdvCXOAmGvKCUjmUK0Dm9RnLwXQIocLaIn1hGem7ZMXLD0ydK_sFRifUarYd3u4JXwHThsi8-Igzeo8guGbj8ui4MW-1jHIoJbKtqhdp7N3ZTxIHeamG_GKykzpK=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0y83dh0iiLcCEhoJY_L0EPlOy6Uv1pJcxEPh1spkXWcS6dN-7kgoqcDPbO8JDD2uNpChJQAZjGpw2yudj1mCLKuoIQc5i0SiC96G5OB8SaX-EZgzfTWnkDlsQ8vaYTq66twX38mBt_Ywdd=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0k8C3QjeLcqbGFvxlDhv9N9s7lhvDQ1q9ZmMlg8TbN8QX3AsMzqsH4wMMvDvvmLBzw5ogOWjv_Vl-8Er7sfmvHhecr1UJCbydvmpEYJIx3Nn8_1BhK7CZFNYippTSeAdP2WvHHdNMxBIVK=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-17"},{"Name":"Dana Brewer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUi8AtJzQHASGL5VIatK-Ka6cpXmWrZV6K5Oqwx4FCnS_bAxg3ujA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently moved to Whitney and needed a new dentist. My husband hadn't been to the dentist in years - they were absolutely wonderful with him. Then our youngest son had a toothache - they got him in right away. I have been dealing with some trauma from a previous dentist but with how wonderful Lake Whitney Dental was with my family - I made an appt for a cleaning and check up. It was an absolutely amazing experience. Lauren my hygienist was terrific \u0026 my time with the dentist was as well. I am beyond pleased with the whole experience. I would highly recommend them to everyone. Their kindness, quality care and prices just blew me away. So blessed to have found them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marina Webb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWegxoHpsDVeA5jM8b24udtlWokc_VI8Hr-xJPde7ooQX1-6AUs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Oakey did an excellent job with my tooth implant and crown. In just 10 minutes, he placed both the implant and the crown, making sure the entire procedure was painless and comfortable. His friendly attitude, smiles, and jokes made the experience even easier. I also appreciated the complimentary tooth chip polishing.\n\nOver the course of three visits, the dental assistants who worked on my implant were outstanding as well—very attentive, supportive, and professional. Overall, I am very happy with the care I received and highly satisfied with the experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rich McVeigh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ4pAhW2bT3Ey98o5JHJ6U4KJEH3yJnpEpX1WDGt3ESUrMqgg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Oakey and his staff are excellent. I have/had a huge fear of Dentists since being strapped down by one as a child. During covid I had a tooth issue that I couldn't live with. He saw me, took his time, and worked out a plan to get my mouth back to healthy while acknowledging my fears. I will never go to another dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elena Fouch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI0dvhxuf-i34CijwlP0DVHIL-BqUYTSMBMMd3c-YpRKLbfrQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Oakey was very friendly and professional, I appreciate the fact that his office got me in very quick in spite of being very busy. I had a front tooth chipped Sunday night and Tuesday morning I was seen and a crown was placed on that tooth. Dr.Oakey uses advanced technologies where the crowns are made and fitted in office without the need to wear temps and come back for replacements. The staff was wonderful as well. The procedure was quick and efficient, highly recommended this office and this particular doctor.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bobi Buske","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI-MXVT_LAhG_kD6anuyu7CYwLARoTifToVX6_eA8LhTxPMug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so happy that I found Dr. Oakey at Lake Whitney Dental.  He cares about his patients and works hard to make all procedures as painless as possible.  The entire staff are kind and efficient.  Dr. Oakey has all the state of the art equipment which made X-rays (which I normally dread) a breeze.\n\nDr. Oakey is very capable and can take care of all your dental needs from teeth cleaning, crowns to implants.  No need to leave Whitney for any of your dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Wilson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIWPzy4xyWn9LD6-nTEbm5zZcKT4KKHYQajUF42cvjvA2ieXQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"What a fabulous practice.  The feeling of family upon arrival was above expectation.   The prompt attention of all their staff was superlative.   The attention paid to me by the dental hygienist was friendly and proficient.   Dr. Oakey was professional and showed his personal interest in my case.  I will be back and I have already urged my wife and daughter to experience this feeling.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nancy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0BMEys-tpxkumtXuDqG_LQ4-NBtDCqgSyWVRpsFeeuqNRMJYtBA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had our 1st dental visits for my 1 year old and it went great. LWD was able to do a through exam without being intrusive or pushing his limits and I feel next time we’ll be able to do X-rays and our little one will cooperate better now that he knows what to expect. My two older kids and myself are long time and returning patients of LWD and glad we were able to get on the schedule so quick after moving back to town.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0-eSYX-ClZf3H9atwe72Y9oUEvtTk1PMkIj5_z2BbHGeUfVTKiQ11G43pMyYECx92aDaaMN2lrtOrJzkZEYA12N-Q-gOUs-AR8F7mDDJ2igakhprnHKXNk8VtaVjDYRweC7Ki-BaqJ5IYC=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-17"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
