ustin Dental Company (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112042288526053752669"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Steiner Ranch","street":"3810 N Quinlan Park Rd Suite 140","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78732","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Bruce Deschamps","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJYqziySdxxGF15RXOhr-xEXMzWMKZi98Tk3pwB1TUXplesDw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another great visit. Exceptional upbeat staff with professional protocols during the appointment. I always leave feeling I got great dental care at a fair price from a staff that really knows what they’re doing. I’m happy I found Austin Dental Company.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0rIOBLIl8RZxsfIdFqjiZtoU5M6rx9a7NYHS84tWyu6mjYdBSTk5o5EJ9Nm7JgjUcEC1TRV7lwBSOIalPSp848Q6glJQIWq_simK4MT4lKIvwP0mgyKpz0pdme1zenTwMWGCPU-IEp-6o=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-9"},{"Name":"Jeanette Ogle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKOG9VaZMUBQoPjA5k4nfmr1fOHYL6Ek1O30M4YsZ0msoWDAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience as a brand new patient could not have gone better. Summer was probably the most amazing hygienist I’ve ever had … with her constant smile, her gentle but thorough treatment , her sensitivity to my anxiety of trying a new dental office, and her overall sweetness . Dr. Mink was equally great with her engaging bedside manner . She took the time to get to know me personally . She made me feel welcome . The front office staff was another highlight with their patience and kind demeanor . I left with a happy heart that I found the most perfect dental group .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michele Ott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQASAaSWAtHCeKW4JJ-8JLqrFJ8zO_FOi497dU9nK0lRTKZNzW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Austin Dental Company for a few years now and couldn’t be happier! I have been through it all in the dental world—crowns, implants, etc and I would not go anywhere else!  Dr. Mink does incredible work and also has the best bedside manner! All of the dental hygienists are fabulous! I really love Lenny. She has the most upbeat, positive attitude (which really helps with my anxiety—I hate going to the dentist!) and she goes above and beyond to help me feel comfortable with my super sensitive teeth. You won’t regret going here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judy Fox","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV0LNb-DgHHQrJK3oLUUQTILi-lI5qMZF4B2qyAyH8bcvPV0aDDBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Experience. Moved to Austin last year and was skeptical about finding a Dental office that would come close to the outstanding experience I had for over 10yrs at Harbor Dental in Fort Collins. I was pleasantly surprised, completely wowed by the professionalism, compassionate and exceptional care that I received. From the courteous Front office Staff, to Xavier who took me on a tour of the practice and did my X-rays, to my Dental Hygienist ~Ariana,  and Dr. Mink. Everything was top notch! such a pleasant experience, in a comfortable, clean, modern and inviting office. Can’t thank you all enough!! Will definitely be a family affair- appointments for my family members have already been scheduled. THANKS SO MUCH TO ALL OF YOU!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Clark","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWix_BHFag1LvAXWKF0t2kWoId58VdJaQuDun51AsTXNnyCM3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I haven’t been to the dentist in several years due to moving every few months - now my husband and I have planted roots in Austin and saw amazing reviews for this office.\n\n10/10!!! I wish u could give 10 stars. I felt so welcomed, and they were very thorough with the cleaning and explained everything in detail.\n\nSo thankful I found Austin Dental Company!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"anisa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbLhWBdyodhrKW3ZnoglBcUXU3ktDj1xpMfHUG1cqJbHB3Te8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience as always! The staff were super friendly, and the office was clean. I love coming to see Dr. Mink and Ariana they always do a great job! Love watching shows during my cleanings and visits. Definitely recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexa Cortez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKEBJ7P2cRx515YSLguq1ctil1Dx0G5gB8MwYJtcLT9OvbFOA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Austin Dental Company is absolutely amazing! Called for an emergency chipped tooth and they were able to get me in asap. Dr. Mink is the best and made sure I was comfortable and happy with my smile at the end. I couldn’t recommend this place more!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lisa Berg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUdLZJNzm0j1s3jhrfcPP7qsowf69wqe0SKd8595uNo6xQnj1K5lA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Always friendly, welcoming, understanding of my dental anxiety and never make me feel pressured to buy things I do not need. I highly recommend Austin Dental Company. My family and I love them.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
