rue},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Donald McKenty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV3MfGQnSCOplqV6FU8b75NdyO7iR_Nq7bq2ScEsPSh_bAmEck6=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Omg, great place with great ladies! First appointment for cleaning and exrays. Painless, even though it's been three years. Second appointment to fill two cavities, crown. Painless. Wonderful people work here. Enjoy!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jennifer pierce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJA3V0UzH6ZPNfzJZJAeePebTcKE0s7qvVI3p_J1k6YGenO5g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff are exceptional especially Lexie, manager, she explained the procedure in detail and the cost and the ways to make it work!! I have sent several coworkers their way!!  The dental staff were amazing and talked me through every step, feeling completely comfortable the whole time!!  I will always come back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"chase newton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL_u73gl6u6djPr9NpOGctqdJwf0e3oBjOP6UMjkzwEn42Ktg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone here is always so friendly! I use to go to Mint dentistry and always had terrible experiences and seemed to pay a lot of extra money every visit. Every time I come here they are straight forward with pricing and very open on scheduling! The doctors are very knowledgable and the hygienists do great jobs at the cleanings!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Taijeron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIs3EscCQUuNfiLbS84EPgkwLRKmcXDFSKU5on4NwMlW7_MDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I really wanted to go to this location. The staff and the nurses are really amazing but I wouldn’t see Dr. Daniel again. Went in for a root canal on 06-21-24 and literally had my mouth open for almost 2hrs (2:14p-4-12p) while she was back and forth between me and other patients. The numbness wore off and even though the nurse recommended giving me more (TWICE) she said no. I left there crying with an incomplete root canal and had to go to a specialist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alien geek","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVqjINkc0ho_GGil71wSq45yGBUeaq91dtrvDxEvvPX1NpLATRI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm a single mother and don't make very much money and Kelli has done sooo much for me. She has helped me with finances ways to work around my work schedule and work pay with the most important issues that I've been dealing with for a while now. I've been to so many different dentists that haven't treated my issues with heart and care but Kelli and her staff have. They treat me like I matter and am a person not just a customer. I finally have hope for my future smile again. I will continue to make extra drive for this office because of the care I KNOW I'll receive.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Horns Of Heaven","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVIauGjcpil72ksEXFexesrtWKQejczxjWF8uwdDyskVaxET3HD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Two thumbs up! The service is good from the front desk, to the x-rays, to the cleaning, to the final check out. I must say there is a wonderful woman here named Shay who did my X-rays and it actually felt therapeutic. She made it extremely comfortable for me. She knew what she was doing! Highly recommended! Everyone here is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beatrice Akatukunda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKSxnsgfkhVGvoBekVIskOqExW5gmOqgtzuJm_dAt7jFOBZTSHU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the very best experience here. 10/10. Everyone was so kind, reassuring and accommodating. I’ll for sure be coming back for all my dental appointments to come!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"An N Tran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKycdRArHYDfRuarCNy7qh-GSWTRH-wRmbfZNiBWVmFw8mftQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in for exam and cleaning, ended up having to get a deeper cleaning. Dr. Kuar is super attentive and really nice. Did my deep cleaning and was really receptive to my needs (needing more numbing, explaining treatment, etc). The front desk was also really nice. Miss Kelly and Miss Marissa are really personable and when explaining treatment and the price that comes with it, they were super thorough and transparent about everything. Overall, great clinic, I highly recommend to anybody in the North Ft. Worth and Denton area. I'll definitely be returning for subsequent dental issues.\n- An","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
