99\u0026sa=U\u0026ved=0ahUKEwi81I7ilNCUAxVMFjQIHVyUB4wQqRkIHSgQ\u0026usg=AOvVaw1bpQ1qoaMPzBJg0i1nneIz","source":"killeenmoderndentistry.com"},"owner":{"id":"101412146284226267083","name":"Killeen Modern Dentistry (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101412146284226267083"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"507 W Stan Schlueter Loop Ste 400","city":"Killeen","postal_code":"76542","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"AJ N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXcy8J9xBR4mXNug6cod0F2UB2R6N0A6C0R9pM0a_vjG5AqH8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My “singing hygienist” Jesenika was absolutely amazing! I was nervous, but she made me feel like I was with a friend. From the moment I stepped in to the moment I left—even walking me to the front—she ensured I was at ease. She answered every question and made sure I didn’t leave with any doubts. She’s the best at what she does and doesn’t settle for less than her best! My dentist Dr. Bell was fantastic too—needles aren’t my thing, but he knew the right thing to do and say to put me at ease. The office staff was also, the office itself is a comfortable laid back environnement. I’m not a fan of the dentist, but this office and staff gave me a phenomenal experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Takes Kare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIGWAEI8H44fVS7dqWg3mUxEMIAGxNLOoJKFcMJU_y-dDnidbU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have had a great experience with the staff so far. They have communicated my treatment plans and billing in a manner that was not confusing and filled with jargon.  Dr. Musunuri  was awesome with my initial appointment. She listened to my concerns and came up with a plan that worked for me.  I have also had an appointment with Dr. Bell and he was extremely personable and understanding of my concerns. All of the assistants were awesome. I look forward to going to the dentist, especially since I stayed away for so long due to bad experiences with other offices.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Barbara Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLe3MimT3gYhjC4N2RqcMLh14VvXZtePJ2eih7OCvwHbvRU4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"To whom it may concern my sister and I each had a dental procedure that was absolutely professional as we both have ever experienced.. Our doctor and dental hygienist mis. Jeseoika  both showed professionalism courtesy kindness patience an excellent workmanship that is next to none. If you're considering any dental work major or minor they are more than worth your time.\n\nThank you many times over Killeen Modern Dentistry.\n\nB. And A. Dunn and","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Desiree Allman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYJAThweA32aytDcjktV4MDFSWdFmgm5Wdno5PXOlxJItj4FrB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the best experience today with Dr. Bell and his team. I scheduled an emergency visit as a new patient who was in pain all weekend. The treatment coordinators were so helpful and professional. Dr. Bell was able to extract my third molar (wisdom tooth) the same day. As a dental assistant who’s never had to get any dental work done, Dr. Bell and his assistant did an amazing job coaching me through my extraction. The numbness lasted an appropriate amount of time after the procedure and with the help of ibuprofen I wasnt in any pain at all when the numbness wore off. I will be a returning patient. Thank you so much Dr.Bell and the rest of the Killeen Modern Dentistry team!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fulmer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWOKD7ZLV9MDJ2-04zBpzWaI9tzSmyowdxsB6AhaLtKGKVkCRZp=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Been a patient here for years, will continue to be as the entire staff consistently embodies professionalism and levity in their character and demeanor. In my experience the vibe has always been positive, reflected in a focused, celebratory approach that I perceive as sheer enjoyment of their work, which may becoming further rareified. Along with master periodontist Jessenika Perry, the great Dr. Huang has been my dentist for some time and I was just introduced to Dr. Bell, who will be soon replacing the relocating Dr. Huang, and after my exam with Dr. Bell today, I have nothing but continued confidence in choosing that the abundant future of my teeth remain in the hands and eyes of the expert beings at Killeen Modern Dentistry. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nancy faria","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVlHRH8Wyc6M14lziDuLgcpJRK6EYpKgcO6JdeMZMC5O6DdXSTf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Another great experience at Killeen Modern Dentistry. I had a tooth extraction performed by Dr. Matthew Kelly and his team.\nThe previous appointment to get this set up was with Dr. Andy Huang, his staff was able to get me in quickly for a lose crown that turned out needing the extraction.\nDr. Huang is a great person and dentist, he has built up trust over the past 3 years, as I am very tense due to a bad experience years prior with another provider, another state.\nThanks for the great experience during a not so pleasant time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Paul Campbell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhSOBmNnYQsiYhV2zhZoZ9CEpCvx9D79KttKM7-E7ja7PINg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I took my girlfriend for an emergency dental visit for an infection this past Saturday.  She was in a significant amount of pain.   They said they'd prescribe antibiotics and pain meds. We went to pick up the prescriptions... only antibiotics were called in!  We called the emergency line... keep in mind this was a Saturday afternoon... Spoke with the emergency line attendant and explained the situation.  NO RESPONSE FROM THE DENTIST!!! MY GIRL SUFFERED FOR 48 HOURS! She could barely eat cream of wheat with a mashed banana!  Monday morning they sent a prescription for ibuprofen. She went in on Tuesday for the extraction. When she asked for something stronger than ibuprofen, the look they gave her was appalling and then the dentist said they'd have to look at her ENTIRE prescription history! Did they? Probably not, because they haven't called to say anything! If they had, they'd find that the last time she got a prescription for pain meds was 15 years ago when she fell off the roof!  My Girl is a decorated Killeen firefighter.  Respected throughout this community!  She recently attended the opening of the newly built fire station 4 and training facility. She uncoupled the ceremonial fire hose, which I'm sure you can find images online. This woman is a hero!  She is not a drug seeker.   The treatment she received by this practice was appalling! I personally felt so helpless watching her go through this!  The dentist didn't even offer an apology to her for not calling in a prescription on Saturday.  DO NOT GO TO THIS DENTIST!!! My Girl deserved better treatment than this!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1oPhqsThKR5jkczhWlFzpBVezFBWdDEFPsBJmud0EI_9OPbGkQ39OYtqHnt3imM8emLTZ8PXofvA7ZWoZcsZHmXSU-F_zmWM8joDGuPXQdRUeoI3tj2oktU9RSsoAlGuwRYFBIWDtCbeIi=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-9"},{"Name":"Josephine Pinkston","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVKDJUBKCrSt597qkmAlk-Yyh2WDTHRaDzmICcBsx2MQPiMwVw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience was amazing. I will definitely continue to use modern dentistry in the future. The team works so well together and they made sure I was comfortable and pain free for the duration of my surgery. Thank you all for a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
