ite parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Clara Yoon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJEu_lZX8oIzvwfTO9Ooh4dv9D5GnzCkcJPk7FJLH7mIIpcVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I am very disappointed with the lack of transparency at this clinic. I was aware that my child would be getting only a bitewing X-ray, and I agreed to that. However, they went ahead and performed additional preventive-care X-rays without informing me that these extra images would cost significantly more.\n\nAfterward, they told me, “We already told you we were doing X-rays, so there should be no problem.” This is not acceptable. Saying “X-rays” in general does not give parents a clear understanding of what types of X-rays will be done or how much they will cost.\n\nIf a procedure is billable and more expensive, the clinic must explain exactly what they plan to do and the cost before doing it. This did not happen, and now I am stuck with unexpected charges.\n\nParents deserve honest communication and upfront pricing. This experience has really damaged my trust in this clinic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"TIARA BROWN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJKgZXNjc5shcJ2KRQ_tSTPCRB0Pb6zyukPPBhNxP0rOZND7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is our first experience with dentist for our littles. The front ladies, both are very nice to let us make appointment on the time (yes. We are lucky!). The office is really nice and clean. They look pretty busy too. Then go to the process with Dr. Ahmed. He explained all of our (first parents experience) questions and patiently make it details for us and all of our options for next actions. We will comeback! Thank you","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda May","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgmFIIBxYHTCtrp3UgbEFdmtrbPCocpkyeAwhyf6c2oOQ2_-s_=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We have been using Dr Warcup and his staff at North Texas Smiles for 10 years. We absolutely love every single one of them and enjoy every visit! They’ve seen 2 of my kids through braces with phenomenal end results and my 3rd is about to get his on! We drive 45min to get here because we love them so much!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Blair Burnette Rivera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLquENL2apJu00PqAaCATMU0Ystl3qHCWdSgmc2Nq78oDhdAQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and Dr. Warcup were very informative for my little guy’s tongue and lip tie revisions. I especially appreciated the fact that he was given numbing injections as some places just do topical and others nothing at all…subscribing to the old school belief that babies do not feel pain! My baby was comfortable during his procedure and that comforted my mama heart greatly!\nThanks for all y’all do! See you at his one week follow up.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn30Z9Oh4xNL2OO82N8fjpgZjLQK5zRpV4BExwyJUNP8cqtKIKmPCCgvNZvqvaM4J_oyBmW6hK8pZTd3Z3s6v3rLM2WQkfyzdbus9IPebFCDWEoD0pazWTtCbESWplWvojkf_ywL9w=k-no"],"When":"2023-12-20"},{"Name":"Chelsea Webb","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocII8DWTSMCDhwSW-_RlHYmcMFM1Trdlqf3IfGUl9ecF9PCegA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Warcup is by far the best dentist! We had a traumatic experience with my oldest when he was 2 years old. He made sure he was comfortable and every visit after that they take special time for him to get warmed up. Then today we took our one year old for his Lip tie fix and it was a breeze! Very fast and he handled him so well!! Thank you Dr Warcup and staff!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alexandria O'Reilly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkgnyfutboNbouVdcGQfB8-PuVwYrK0eprqIEtat3ZFo1vRIGR=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Our newborn’s tongue tie revision with Dr. Warcup was incredibly smooth and as painless as oral surgery can be. He combines top-tier expertise with a kind, thoughtful approach that immediately puts parents at ease. What really sets him apart is the time he takes to explain the procedure in detail—laying out the pros and cons clearly, with zero pressure and a lot of compassion. He’s professional and somehow manages to make a stressful situation feel manageable (even a little lighthearted at times). We left our appointment feeling informed, supported, and, completely confident our sweet baby was in the best hands!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"bethn03","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfruXg8M7d74L_1J_Pxb5Fk3drjPg2568NI84KJIZ2Ffzh3CQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We had a tongue and lip tie revision done here.  Exceptional care received, Dr. Warcup was very informative without being pushy and only does what is absolutely best for you and baby.  His team was great and super supportive of a nervous momma of a newborn.  They fit us in quickly knowing I was in pain due to poor latch.  He has follow up appointments included in the total price to ensure baby is healing correctly to reduce risk of reattachment.  Exceptional experience and would recommend him and his team again and again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Montes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXxoXNRDfgD9n49D5eu5k1mTDFrbEzXxuOTFg4G9S2Ygx15tjYsQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We visited for a consultation on our daughters lip and tounge tie. Dr. Warcup was extremely kind and very informative. He took lots of notes when we shared our experience, and asked us follow questions to better understand what we were asking of him. We walked away feeling confident and supported in our decision. 10 out of 10 would recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
