just wasn't enough. I'm grateful for the helpful tips she shared.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anson Booker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwvcCj29MJM-a5QH47vTcHJNLsnrFInwwr8zHBBxY_aIonXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️⭐️\nI had a dental cleaning today, and the staff was absolutely amazing and professional. We’ve been going to Heights Dental for many years, and it seems like they’re always stepping up their game in both care and professionalism. Truly a great experience every time!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLlnrSjkKTi8D5NupSMHOFpKR_xh7W-pIUPnsyGldhXpKdDXA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I would like to share my experience in this dental clinic. Dr. Shruta Lakhani helped me when I first came to this clinic but I must say that she is a tough and a bit rude doctor. I am grateful to her for her help, but I did not dare to undergo any more procedures with her.\nI also had my teeth cleaned at this clinic by the dental hygienist, Dawn. She divided the teeth cleaning into two sessions so that my insurance would cover the cost. Thanks to the clinic for ensuring that the client pays as little as possible, or nothing at all, for the procedures with the help of insurance.\nI didn’t like the way they performed the dental cleaning at this clinic because I noticed that it was not done thoroughly. The plaque and tartar were not completely removed from my teeth. They cleaned the left side once, and then a month and a half later, they cleaned the right side. Both times the hygienist did not do a full quality cleaning of my teeth, although now I understand why she advised me to do a cleaning every three months. Apparently, this is how they attract clients to come and have teeth cleaned. This is the first time I have ever had a bad dental cleaning, and I had to pay an extra $100 out of pocket in addition to what my insurance covered. In Europe, I have never seen teeth cleaning done like it is here, and they do not recommend cleaning teeth more than twice a year. That's why I was alarmed by the advice to have my teeth cleaned every three months. Additionally, during my last cleaning, they introduced some kind of infection into my gums, and afterward, I had to treat my gums. This confirms that I will not return to this clinic.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2pRH3FqC9ARhTK_YY3eoGRQqFDNrJNxX4gZ-HH7GeERAOSav8RCp9BOnckIy_hcCoAXQ28kB6HuCStzFMu-PoXIJ-7xokNBxbW0DGdsXJ3r__eQNTHO1dV6wpEppKv_EAFd1qx=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1_oRdpD_vU5gh45uxbx1F1eNBpYFy5mtHxTuVluK93mzqzK0rJ6WpB4qjhLQ_Z9TF3PcgdrWYyx9U1ik1IBE7m91pW29F1ShCBrKEOsVSaq72daDaYe3iEsX1OaMKs04VilK0s4A=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1uX4JS0eA1E5-Rm9IkoO790nrSyZU_dwkUxyKiZq93phg8bB_cvaw5q5LapWg3F4tErcPat6UA68w1i9L6F0lkyuujL1KtdvfRq0jFLITRpTB6Nbys7cgMuTGgbw-YJvHO2Etl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2Bfc3CPiCMPyx1stXeQNlDGoskM2vZsjKiQIfjwNqCtL2uwwysNCcYi1ESEne6yFj0Fu5VUwgYv0FAHGlW_yDrW10D9-5yCDKbJY9ftT9TLgkOji3vpih04Bm7uNu-xLowIPSYtg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn29AhrnhsRUyC3VYAcGzoYprAoTOQ_Xg2jZnVE19EUVNMS5mWfS9SHgmY84XySfxiY1ZuIqpJeDQkB1l1ugoDTXANmMlYRbd8EyjM00k-93kgtoJgnPSSDN2X1mAHWbUxBctuuU=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2mVxXv2vUNETApHypoywvR_lGz1Rh9DHf-qmmjCR168QWH6onXmpFOnIEb6_UtMoalJtoySc_pULRWgUHaJP5Dm75M0Xlju_LlqLboX-7XzZoVgl5ZjdwwTh7xtY8YRVFuJ-58cw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2qGVgxytCO3RIldSHCQUM3gdAXs0z9J4Or9aodXLD5AeM5HTQoR-7dQnl7exGuHYYCyK59k4xaBTTeKSpQTTBRDeMQ34ncH0wD347t8jNBb63CGEWP8s62KQK2qF6oycNx_T-w=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1JjS__3WZyAn55-UQsePjZL2CnwvZ-7TPALzDRZhdTBNuLPLTgyPl0I-mLGboh4RwY1cJapdKBP-iI7aS4jbxNktgHswHETqpj_n39n2K_cdIbVwc1qgBKXm0bBYAhVUyu8hGvRw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3xesgzebI