"Monika F","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1Peu2b6omjTY3IcopZUbeO08M3s-vbD044EDHlxjtJYhpbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to Texas Tiny Teeth to get second opinion on a dental plan that my daughter received from another pediatric dentist. Dr. Abi took the time to review the other dentist’s plan, view the X-rays, give my daughter an oral exam, and gave me her professional opinion. She was helpful and explained everything as she was doing it. The office staff and dental hygienist were equally as kind and helpful as Dr. Abi was! I would definitely recommend Dr. Abi if you are in need of a pediatric dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"valeria garza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIc0JrwfFPNogdp8Xek4SoCeL9r7ep7AHxSSaCN4mobaMFGqQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Raquel and Dr Abi were so great!! I was able to get in so fast. My daughter is not great with strangers but they made her feel safe. The staff was welcoming and helpful with insurance along with paperwork. I did not have to worry about booking next appointment or waiting, they had it all set up for me as soon as I was done with the visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elexis M Berry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUpYxRGg0YeaVkPD1Mh0_-rlEIDEbVawrNf92SDhdpw1JDReTmY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I wish I could give 10+ stars! The office is so welcoming , upon walking in we were instantly greeted with multiple smiles from the front desk 💕 Jocelyne was incredibly patient with my daughter, and Dr. Abi was very informative while still getting us in and out. I was worried my 1-year-old might have a rough appointment, but they made her feel so comfortable that she immediately gravitated toward them. Such an amazing experience 💕","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crystal Shannon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIt1WLWfgTmtWHVYf17ERycEfEo5V0E2F8-LN2r9HT8L6QK_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recommend Dr. Pan! He is a fantastic and skilled pediatric orthodontist. His assistant Ava is wonderful with kids so patient and kind. They made what could be a stressful experience easy and even fun for my daughter. The office is clean, modern, and runs on time. A+ experience all around!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Van Ness","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpZQd1bTsXubd05VTIo6xZF2pFhBTcFR1tJ1qV8Pd3d4mcl0d7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Who knew going to the dentist could be so fun for a kid!? My son and I love this place. Dr. Abi takes such great care of her patients and all the staff are so gentle and kind","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"R","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdxmpT6HYeXQuzz2awjYWwAXoYwPgfsc_qX954FzWdDNzVzw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Abi is awesome our triplets love her. She's so understanding and knows how to handle the kids. She is always kind, accommodating and knowledgeable. She's easy to talk too. She's always able to answer the many questions we have as first time parents. The kids love going!!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jane Ware","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtFOsqN5_XcsIyKnSoU--jp3lLwQOt9BkgmESvp1yRR7I26_s=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We brought our 3 year old in for her first exam and cleaning and couldn’t be happier! Staff was warm ,welcoming and quickly put us at ease. They gave her lots of stickers and treats and had Disney movies playing that made the appt a breeze. Dr. Abby and Anna were wonderful with our daughter and we were out of there super fast! Highly recommend!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1_BieHxI7T6kt8gKVP5QW7SEJVc19kwV72VLSs6j8ZJUXA79W5oAVFFFvsPd4I8sRZQAca_rq-h4GRvFytvaLdLRnw-Os5hK4414MpnPYGp--atjJoKYzRO-HsCDezQRxKBxU=k-no","https://lh3.googleuserco