team. Organized and reasonable for any emergency. Wait time for a walk-in is good. Referred by my dental insurance options. Had a quick clean and polish. Had some overthinking before my evaluation turned out fine. Thank you!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dave Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKRQSouRBxvdRoRoj7SePHhSjhN0TFF5TKWUk4h362QUb6iCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing staff and dentist!  Nicer environment, office space over the previous location on Hickory St. Dental assistants, hygienists are amazing, caring, gentle and very thorough, as well as professional. Sorry I didn't get their names. Israel, the front desk manager is on top of everything that keeps the operation running from Q\u0026A to scheduling, billing and overall customer service. Anything my wife \u0026 I have ever needed, Israel has been able to accommodate. On my last visit I had two fillings and a deep clean, 99% pain free. My fault for not maintaining \u0026 flossing. Thank you all again! My wife \u0026 I have referred several people to this office. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynnda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXcMxnUpCoq5h5uQchzONaow6jygKpNxCFHN581JPcuFcc3z3oE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is my first visit to Abilene Dental Care. I had to change dentists because of insurance challenges.  I was very pleased with the level of care my teeth received. They use an interesting water pick type of machine to clean tartar. It was fast, relatively painless, and seemed to work really really well. The staff was kind and efficient. I will definitely be keeping them as my dentist as long as my insurance lets me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffany Johnson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoz4aH3YYynt43l-0CWBHsLBl61RJIgh_x_gJI3HuXSrSDQZjF3g=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best experience ever! The Dr was friendly and understanding. I was not rushed in and out. Treated as a person, not just another $. Injection was seemless and treatment even better! Thankful I found this office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eating good","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI4zHVySdoj0IxUXzB3WiWWGkc1lTvEnBsHvxHBbsh8CebhrA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The gentleman that saw me I don’t remember his name. He was a traveling dentist. But was a day and night’s difference from the week before when I went to Jefferson Dental in Dallas, which was a horrible experience the difference, of course was me getting a couple teeth, pulled to something very minor but overall love the staff. Israel helped me a lot by getting me in the same day. I continue to plan on still doing business with them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeromy Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX14eDlMDT6tfwy_AA_ZynbRM31YZUC9TUsDZSrBoedpSkZUUBz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jessica is the absolute best hygienest. awesome. Brains, beauty, and wonderful sense of humor. Wait until you see the hair: eat your heart out Tina Turner.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connie hooper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo-9P2mSDQ7DW72mzFZ-NUt5cYSeIVOQGj564wJS0UeRZVuE_T=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very patient oriented. Israel is fabulous with customer/patient communication. The tech and Dr are as well. I called for an appointment that I needed quickly, and got one next day. Great, friendly environment","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Glenda LaVelle Brown","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXOJNHruSF5bP55EiaTAJ57vlSKz3YVXs2FlXfv8Fx1ee-qiiCt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was the best experience I have ever had with dentist. Everyone was very caring and passionate to my condition. Found me a solution and help me not only with fixing my teeth, but emotion