on availability. Reality Bites was also clean, well equipped, and full of nice, competent dentists and hygienists. I highly recommend, especially if you want to schedule your appointments without missing work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Troy B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVXpHEVzhJgTefSrbwbXWpOJ4DE913rcBv7cHWedQ1elgKyNeo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This dental office is by far the most friendly, professional, kind and understanding place I have ever been to. They were able to get me appointment same day last minute and took care of me. I was in tremendous amount of pain and left with no pain. I couldn’t thank them enough I will be returning for my cleaning soon!\n\nThank you all!\n-Troy B","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"alireza esfahanian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocITUYS02sRy4YuJgMZzacfHBoRMfHTfxZz00NhqPetTl6Q4Fg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’d like to express my sincere appreciation to Dr. Katerina Nechay for the outstanding work she did in creating my denture. She is an exceptionally intelligent, skilled, and knowledgeable dentist.\nI’m also very grateful to the entire staff at the clinic — everyone is polite, professional, and incredibly kind. Thank you all for your excellent care and warm service\nAliReza  Esfahanian","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Amor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJLYP9nbyffnRZIATRhLV54ctW172ZPwME-uxUDV5bqvKzf6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"The staff is very  nice. However, recently I had an exam and cleaning scheduled. I got a text saying I could come in earlier which I did. Then they told me they did not have time for my  cleaning and I would need to schedule Another time to\nget cleaning done. This was at 12:05,  my appt was at 12:00. 5 min. Are you serious? That’s terrible customer service!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"funstation rg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVcu8C1VGVLv_9XxpjEo4l-g7Vrk58zEcajZQwmDjcbGQ9jg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My dental cleaning went well. The hygienist explained each step from beginning to end and left my teeth clean and smooth. The dentist also accommodated a tooth filling procedure the same day. The procedure was painless and precise. The staff was attentive and made me feel comfortable the entire visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ronald Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTGmtGvVy-PgGipmLOZh_85ZBinCbDyDulhRT5vqhc7IiLbVQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff, elite servicing, Trish was amazing. Will be back for upcoming appointments in the future. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
