aPwohck9dHbMlxNWtsTQaYugn8s3klIRSb3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came to Seven Lakes dental due to a not so great experience at a previous office. I am very picky about Dentists and hygienist as I’ve also worked in the dental field almost half of my life. Tina and Dr. White were really truly great! Very professional and made you feel comfortable and like you were part of the family. Also a shout out to the front desk! I was having not so great of a day and they were just super friendly and welcoming. I’m so glad my friend recommended them to me!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lynne Galliart","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWgObaZcVfkKq8NS8CkPEBNt7Nj7UFSq1NwpwR_MxwhtS96Zjc=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This visit was to have my new crown seated. Once again, everything went smoothly. Dr White is great with the needle, didn’t feel a thing. The crown came in perfect needing no adjustment. So glad I found this office, if you’re looking for a new Dentist, I highly recommend Dr White and team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patricia Elliott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVItaSiP_WVPmk5-1Wokt-7vJ-P0dVwT8Teqp86ajp1I3UZ5jxI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Seven Lakes Dental performed major dental work for me as a new patient. Everyone from the administrative staff to the dental assistant was extremely professional, friendly qnd helpful. Each procedure was thoroughly explained to me in advance by Dr. Shedlosky\nand her assistant. I felt very confident that I was in good hands and I received very good dental care.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Bergmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLY90NKB_K5GlMhYIvBb03CmCG42iFxDgp8p03XmuCHXAO82w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a good size piece of enamel break off the front surface of one of my front teeth.  Dr. Crum had it perfectly repaired in short order. Cannot 