an happy to drive the 18 miles away to have it fixed. When I got to Boerne the staff was just as nice as the Spring Branch location. They did the root canal and I didn't feel any pain at all not even when the doctor injected the shots to numb my gums because he put numbing jel on before he did the injections. The Bourne Doctor who did the root canal was the best !! I'm 69 years old and that was the first time having dental work done that I didn't feel any pain. Thank you Comal Hills Dentistry !!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jewels Kublank (Jewles)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFzX8QjkFYwQi0C2X5l76t2qfCNA8i4jOpgwf-_oqWQAukWKxt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Comal Hills staff was so helpful and so friendly and kind. Very very clean, very thorough. Highly recommend. Jewels","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christiane Govan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWQQApapYrjkQvb1ZnfCdw99jOl9LU6aMqiX_Ca42qnp6XS4sQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so glad I was referred by a friend to Comal Hills Dental. The office space is beautiful and the staff is competent and friendly.\nHygienists are very professional and do an excellent job.  I truly feel like I am in good hands!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Petra Goodman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7bjK9q44mZBy0GlM2vOiv9oymR-XTFVs9_eTthQyMPdoHlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first visit to Comal Hills Dental was excellent. The dental hygienist (Sorry, I can't remember her name.) was great. She kept me informed of everything and was so much fun to just chat with. In addition, all of the staff was very helpful. Everyone made me feel welcomed.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
