""},{"Name":"detroit texas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJy7SWVwK7p8DKX7XnPzp_4D6U3WsdVVBRMJMbuuZb5mRCh3A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m not a great patient have very high anxiety and low tolerance for pain every effort was made to make me comfortable I recommend dr Rodriguez and Miguel I was a difficult patient and I know it but they got me through it (Lisa pitts)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sam Landy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUJIyEg3Xp3G6YLwzDc2ZvaeRe9_rDlD1BoueFJHWUSQCebbY0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"“Loop Dental is by far the most unprofessional dental office I have ever encountered. The staff is not only disrespectful but also dismissive of patients’ concerns, creating a hostile and uncomfortable environment. They consistently fail to follow HIPAA standards, as private and sensitive patient information can easily be overheard in the waiting area. Beyond these serious privacy issues, the lack of empathy and genuine care for patients is shocking. Simple questions or requests are often met with impatience or rudeness, making what should be a routine appointment extremely stressful. It is deeply concerning that a healthcare provider would operate in this manner, showing so little regard for patient well-being and comfort. I would strongly caution anyone considering this practice to think twice, as my experience has been both disappointing and disheartening.”","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marcus Maple","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW6_HtlTDlBwnnw66-W5ihXqBR6luG6D6d29qIx1Wvu_GSCKOk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this clinic for a few years now and I always receive exceptional service. They send out appointment reminders in a timely manner and after any procedure I would receive a courtesy call to see how I am doing. I recommend them to anyone looking for a dentist area.  Dr. Rodriguez and his crew are the best in Killeen!!!!!!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kuaika Iokia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUe8BoivArcc9jblryG5yj_qII2adbp4bD3IUorr6nDd7ueawQoFg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Rodriguez  has been phenomenal and has done amazing work for me. All his work has been top notch.\nHe's done everything from extractions, to crowns, to partials for me. Thanks to him and his amazing staff for fixing my smile.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rufus Walker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVyk8UAMtOzJD2-RCU7hrrLCclVxHZOQrEH8I-KvNYH9UzOSCv1AQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I really love this office. Been going for about 7 years now. The receptionists in front have always been amazingly nice and helpful. The wait time usually isn't too bad either. Dr. Rodriguez is great, professional, and does amazing work. The best part, they actually care and remember you! I am sometimes surprised by just how much the staff remembers from just a little conversation we had last time I was in.\n\nOverall, I love this office and my family loves it here as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lorraine Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ25tNySTztruDXBn5sDvSKl3oKoPQCcdbvQ4cJiD4pAMqRWIA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went yesterday as my second time for my check up/cleaning and like the first time all I can say this team is awesome, Mr. Tony explained to me everything that I needed to know about the health of my teeth in a very charismatic and polite way. In summary I can say I’m more than satisfied to choose them as my dentists. The staff is polite,charismatic and very professional! I definitely recommend them.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jay Hugs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI90A-BzTn3U7VlzIVCuaknEey1kn0Rb1x6EC_6dDLbbxljuQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm not 