d training on their part.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Jackson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJQTc-CqhS1RKCphJcDCQLgSg0fA8x3KcrDbBFi4XFfaW90oQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Trybunko and staff were professional, kind and helpful with my dental needs. Being a new patient recently, all went as smooth as possible. I needed a follow-up visit after a molar extraction and they got me in their clinic the same day! Thanks again for all you do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Briggs","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1HaHJHsNWAK2sp7ph1ICZvh52WlHANjkACm8hYMOP2lgpaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I drive 30 miles to come to this dentist. She’s awesome and if you have to get a shot, you won’t fill it. She tries her best to keep the price down as well.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shannon Hampu","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZG5uv3Ids6sQe6NymPL1FoaZHCJGSefPkOLBKNRu2l42v7g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"All staff is skilled in their area of service and our smiles are their primary concern. While I was in the chair, I was informed if each next action to be performed. Their patience is apparently endless. My care during and after the procedure was addressed at all times. Gentle, professional, caring!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leannette Kemp","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUGA-w9_nH0tYk31zM8GWerxpluvhkgzk0hFofO8TNpIx5cR_jD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is always super kind and it's great place to take my kids when they need their bi-annual check up. Never had a bad experience and we have a super patient dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Ellison","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKhUEAUElifATEANNv_xPHsFBHqkLZRx5YQ23EK11d7ekvG_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Extremely pleased and highly recommend! Staff 