]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Marwa Ahmed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLg4b-g4Qo_QIhwf8PcUlPyV6UORBFKtmc-P05NnjdeyFUzEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at this dental office. From the moment I walked in, the staff was welcoming, friendly, and professional. The front desk made scheduling easy, and I didn’t have to wait long before being seen.\n\nDr Omar Yousuf took the time to explain everything clearly and made sure I was comfortable throughout the visit. The office was very clean and well organized, which really helped put me at ease. I truly appreciated how gentle and caring the entire team was.\n\nI highly recommend this dental office to anyone looking for excellent care and a friendly environment. I’m very happy with my experience and will definitely be coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amy A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLYnvbGEfRbkOLPymMb0oeLSsGYU7HXEwsgOEDiccaS04Rbhw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the moment I first called the office to the completion of my procedure, the entire team was kind, caring, and professional. Dawn was so sweet and helpful setting up my appointment.I had extractions and implants done.Dr Yousuf and Haley made sure I felt comfortable and informed throughout the whole process. Dr. Yousuf’s skills are truly unmatched. The level of care, precision, and attention to detail made a big difference in my experience. I’m very grateful for the excellent treatment and highly recommend this office to anyone needing dental work. I’d give 10 stars if I could!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dr. Esteria Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd4k70bCWjggvEP3uwVuYTTyuUjsoPJ_HsrBptc82v0AuDq6w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐ Texas Dental Specialist - Affordable Dental Implants in Texas\nIf you’re searching for affordable dental implants in Texas with a team that truly cares, Texas Dental Specialist is the place to go! The process of getting implants is simple, stress-free, and expertly handled by their experienced implant dentists. From consultation to completion, everything is streamlined for your comfort and convenience.\nWhat makes this office stand out is the personalized care. The staff knows your name the moment you walk in, creating a warm and welcoming environment that feels like family. They combine state-of-the-art technology with genuine hospitality, making every visit a positive experience.\nFor anyone looking for top-rated implant dentistry in Texas, this is the best dentist on this side of Heaven! Highly recommended for quality, professionalism, and a personal touch.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judy Kuiken","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLdfAnXiCQKQP97DHw2cAnr4Zw9jaoTB4IezL3RKFLyHCjK_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was in Texas visiting my daughter and her family from out of town to enjoy a  formal celebration for my granddaughter.  I was devastated when I had a major dental emergency and found myself without one of my front teeth.\nMy daughter was familiar with Texas Dental Specialists and called to see if there was someway they could help with this emergency.\nSuper hero Dr. Omar Yousuf and his staff had me in their office within 1 hour of the telephone call and was able to do a 3D printing of a front tooth to save my day!!!\nI am grateful to Dr. Yousuf for the high technology and innovative solutions they can offer.\nThey truly were my Super Hero! !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mike G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWN16-JCujh8HT-4vHbS-4TL1maGsJk9-gsOMrwI3xeMSpSb3c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to see Texas Dental Specialists about full-arch replacement.  My original motive was not appearance improvement, rather long-term cost and time efficiency.  My teeth were not really jacked up all that badly (did not have my first cavity ever until age 52) but gum erosion was causing crowns to need to be re-done, plus extraction of a couple teeth.   When my dentist informed I needed an oral surgeon to pull a tooth, endodontist to do a screw, and then dentist does the crown top, I hated the thought of three appointments again, three procedures, and realized pretty quickly that just two such situations would pay for a full arch.   With Dr. Yousuf I feel I was able to remove the stress of worrying about further erosion (for the rest of my life) in a one day “one stop shop” endeavor.  I view it as prepaying dental expenses for the rest of my life.  Dr. Yousuf and all of his staff (Ashley, Towanda, Haley, Stephanie, Dawn) have all been awesome and helpful.   And now, I really like the look too.  😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"megha singh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzA1MGHqK7EMsWjeXHzdTGFbNexvQpsWhXFjil6prislOVhHo=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have been visiting this dentistry since 6 years, Dr. Yousuf and his team has great beside manners, today my cleaning was with Miss Olga, she is very professional and polite. Highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaivon mortazavi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJn3DHF5QFRbX-1ly2y_9WtrLCSEq-yRmfvHjgnp_12VojTnA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have always been met by a professional, courteous team from walking in and registering to initial exam and cleaning or treatment by Dr. yousuf.  Staff is always prompt and I never wait more than a minute or two to walk back.  Dr. Omar has invested in many of the latest equipment and has done a great job with modernizing the office esthetics and service capabilities of this office since acquiring the business a few years ago. He is a very competent dentist as are his entire team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Precious Love","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-