State Board of Dental Examiners! Secondly I have been coming to Texas Dentistry probably almost 15 years or pretty close to it. The past few years there have been a couple of mishaps that have made me want to part ways such as my daughter’s mouth being cut during a service and that’s just one incident (I still have the photos to prove it). However, when you have an established relationship sometimes it alters your decision making. Needless to say I have continued to come and the last of my children who is now 9 was recently seen and recommended to the orthodontist for braces. Let me just say I absolutely hate the orthodontic side! I went over there and instantly felt anxiety because I don’t like how open everything is! It’s very congested in there and every single time that we have gone which has been just a few there has been someone different in there and almost everyone seems so very young but a couple people. I’m sorry and mean no offense but I just don’t want my child in a dental office where the people are rotating in and out and I have every right to this choice. Moving along after the initial appointment we had a second appointment for more radiographs then the following week we had an appointment to determine whether or not my child’s teeth could be removed or if we would need to go to a specialist. By this appointment time not only am I anxious but my son is too. He’s getting nervous and saying mom let’s just go. On top of us anxiously waiting our tech comes in and presents me with a paper saying I would have to pay $45. I don’t recall being told at all that I would have to pay anything else outside of the $2100 that I was already expected to pay out of pocket. I then request to go over to the orthodontic side so that I could get clarity on why I was paying anything else at that moment and requested to speak to the office manager. He/she NEVER came. I left my information by end of day and some guy returned my call and let’s say the call ended with me being dissatisfied and him NOT being helpful at all. I opted out of having treatment with this office because I’m finding somewhere else to take my child. He then tells me my deposit is non refundable and I stated that if he didn’t make sure it was refunded I was going over his head because first off we’re not getting serviced here! He assured me that he would contact upper management and get back to me. IT BEEN TWO DAYS AND I HAVE YET TO HEAR FROM ANYONE! If I could give zero stars that’s exactly what I would have done.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"lesli mejia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXyklb4TcuSPFwvdd3K9ef2G0ED43HqHxVcEJHrtiBih-2V-sLI=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an exceptional experience with Dr. Tran and Sara during my recent procedure. From the moment I arrived, their professionalism and warmth put me at ease! Together, they created a smooth and reassuring experience, which I truly appreciated.\nLove It!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Caitlyn B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUAvShPbYWAbQIABLS30qVJqhRjdM9B4Olt5Temq97NBLYBOeoJEg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to this location in mesquite for almost 6 years and  have loved every single visit! All three of my children come here to keep their teeth beautiful and healthy, and I would honestly never take them anywhere else! My oldest has always been anxious when it comes to any kind of doctor appointments and since the staff have always been so patient and kind, my son looks forward to his dental visits! We get top notch care, I never wait long before my appointments, and most importantly my kids enter and leave that place smiling! I will always recommend the mesquite location!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharonda McClellan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLq4PL5iAfC1prxlzewAtp1qmDm9r-iykVqlLYpHIa3xEU1jg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"We had an appointment today at 8:30 a.m. no one came to the door no one answer the phone no one is here. I even drove around to the back. No cars. Nothing.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3t1Pz0UO9WOjporu7-fZijUXvL4GsxtMcJ7wMpOouomUwsaV34Bbx-87eUojIKqaK5H9GGBmSxcKttbcalK8IA8LwSiqn1f2QniBP-A5e-yxCDq2msXFcsNRunuYvzP2Qadge3BNvESJk=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-3"},{"Name":"Mavelli Parra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3P8eGbO127IETKbRyb14UcEKwZm9f57JHglyosnEOlbCUuhpN=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great! I would definitely recommend for anyone with kids. I've been going to the Mesquite location for years. I took my daughter last week and they treated her very nice and calmly. All the staff are nice and welcoming.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kela Willis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUsyhF73j_YOzu65MsuaBu1SjH6Hywc2WKb3oJG5qbTDH1OZH1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good place to take your kids !! The staff is very knowledgeable and friendly!!   The facility is  nice and clean. We didn’t have to wait long to be called into a room, and the receptionist  asked my kids what they wanted to watch on TV/Netflix  while we waited.  The dental hygienist staff is awesome!! She was quick and effective with x-rays. During the cleanings she made sure that my kids were comfortable. Dr Thanh Tran is very nice,  sufficient  and considerate.  She calmed my son and really reassured him  that it’s OK when he was feeling uncomfortable. Dr Tran made sure that she informed me on everything that I needed to know.  At the end of the visit one of the staff members made my kids a balloon animal !!  I thought that was so nice !!  Good place! Good Staff! Great  Doctors!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adriana Lupercio","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqkKq6XdW8IvM1iGM_fhDOkitp9k_6zkqRfTHu3HzPTa8F7CyU=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr.Linley( spelling?) and Dr. Lee are the absolutely best. I have a child with Autism with the strength of Hercules and they both do such a wonderful job with him. They are very patient and although it gets tough with him they are thorough and very caring and understanding. The staff are so sweet and compassionate always try to make sure we are in and out as smooth as possible and are very helpful in getting my child in his papoose as fast and as safe as possible! We have been coming here for years and will continue to do so.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joe “FaydeRumble5” A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIJjVQWytqtG0tY399t4ftNaEzi3otXWeoFbcHTAPDcYqgutQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I typically hate dentist because of all the noise and poking that they do but here they helped relax my mind and made my cleaning and visit very pleasant and smooth. The front desk is a great very informative and helpful. 10 out 10 recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
