vous about dental appointments makes you feel so comfortable. So happy I tried this office and will definitely tell family and friends to check them out","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Judie Olivares","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXeBnL5PLFpZSNf11FPgMQN7QzWQnxGQVnvnQnE8p5D99rN6sCEWQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an outstanding experience at this dental office! From the moment we walked in, the staff was warm, welcoming, and incredibly professional. The dentists and hygienists are thorough, gentle, and clearly experts at what they do—they took the time to explain everything and made sure my daughter felt comfortable throughout her visit.\n\nWhat really impressed me as well was their billing department. They are efficient, organized, and truly go above and beyond to make the process smooth and stress-free. They explained my insurance coverage clearly, answered all my questions, and handled everything with transparency and care. It’s rare to find a dental office where both the clinical team and the billing staff operate with such exceptional professionalism.\n\nHighly recommend this office to anyone looking for quality dental care and a team that genuinely puts patients first!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Perry Fulcher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLIkftA65m2HpkE6GiACmSQwhRBIXsxIcZKJBGdi5LXsK3ReQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"At first contact with the front desk reception team there is always a warm pleasant greeting (and a touch-free temperature check). The facility is immaculately clean and comfortable for patients with the latest in dental technology available (advanced imaging systems just one example). Everyone in the office greets me whether or not they are directly attending my dental care that day. There is continuity in staff members who assist Dr Tello in my personal care. Bobbie is a great technician who prepares everything so well that there really is minimal extra effort by Dr Tello when she comes into the room. Dr Tello’s personal interaction is full of TLC, surpassed only by her knowledge and technical skills. Even the checkout process where I get the bill is relatively painless, because the billing process is so organized and her staff from beginning to end are so well trained and helpful that there is little question about insurance coverage or copayments. This practice sets a high standard for others to meet.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kiyeen Kiyeen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJT6nEdFwk_I-SqgFcv1i17NAjx7q8Kf2JTd_tcluy2f7eZwhc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Like most dentist offices they dont really teach you how to take care of your teeth, what products to use, how the teeth demineralize and mineralize. I had to go research Dr Ellie Phillips on youtube to learn how.. All they care about is if your paying with cash debit or credit.. I left there with the same oral health  knowledge I came in there with which was nothing. My review was not made in error I was a patient at this office just a few weeks ago.. No I will never come back to discuss anything.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Braianna Mccrory","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJr_bAunkyjSVOciiK6E0xyi3iJ0wSUzUhmqQD-Yx9PN5AXiA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tello Smiles is the place to go. Dr. Tello and their team provided me with amazing service. High tech office, w/knowledgeable staff. They addressed my concerns, and I felt at ease when leaving. The billing department goes above and beyond to verify our benefits and informs us of any costs out of pocket. I would highly recommend them to friends \u0026 family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DeeDee Elizondo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQMZBLwduKUQfShdOQ56FXOzowxD5CB-ow9rbQsq8AmeduFQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The whole team is amazing, and Dr. Tello is a fantastic dentist providing generational care \u0026 building a legacy of trust and familiarity that becomes part of the community's heritage. Hands down, the best!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yulianna Medina","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFHnISvJG8diuO4gjnGf-SlNDOTbQtO7A9_nG2p_4NAZ9pETAt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Tello Smiles never fails to amaze me. The staff is very sweet, from the second you walk through the door from the moment you walk out. They were able to answer every question I had clearly which I really appreciated.10/10 recommend :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracy Orr","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWf4IbY-0is6P221fSNIPbbtqOZ61XuKZ3TMxc8YxQBN28vcm5kCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my 6-month check-up and cleaning today. The Staff is always very courteous, friendly and knowledgeable. They make me feel like a valuable customer. I can actually say I like going to the Dentist!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
