commend..\nLeo Bernal","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lourdes Escalante","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIloBwLHwoL3jsbvajEB_QqrAEMaRToR_dWq36Qy1HJmGHE2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today was my first ever visit to this dental office and wow they left me with a very great first impression. I haven’t been to the dentist in moreover five years I have been postponing it and quite frankly I haven’t had good experiences with the dentist in the past but Dr Patterson was great he was very welcoming, attentive and informative. Overall the whole staff was very friendly and nice from the front desk, the assistant to the hygienist. Highly recommend this office","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKe7biwfrM_aMAFzSAXek47lVTOlHC46t65XOakikLM9PA1-A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been using Texas City Family Denistry for many years, and Casey is my hygienist  and she is very gentle and so very sweet. The whole staff is amazing, starting with reception as you walk in the door. I have never been a fan of going to the dentist but Dr Martenson makes it as pain free as he can. He is a very cool dude. If you r looking for a family dentist , this would be your place.\nKaren Williams","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn197M--nXz4BOGhplpBGG4_t0fi1VrErW4HM9eVT25ePVSI8rcy80zAInfWq05ouaHAj0fjR7MztGMv1M41Tolst3ja1Qhg8QTAI0ZLFCwwXjICC6l_eTuPbr8zOGm5Paut41Pb=k-no"],"When":"2024-4-2"},{"Name":"Nabila Faisal","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYoEv-_X5WPmhQ7cBAEYfejuaN2J68pvL3zXDLijMf9brMGPHPZg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience with Dr. Martinsen. I have lots of cavities from the past, always hasitated to go to dentists..He expertly handled my crown and front tooth filling, ensuring my comfort throughout. Additionally, he fixed my previous fillings from els