ou can truly trust, but I’ve found it here!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kat","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUgy0ePw4JLE3VNwL8ikrGsDUo1Gg-8aQgqDh5456oelFzNbAC1tw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We recently had to find a new dentist because of insurance change, they are very welcoming and have clear communication of treatment plan and price. the price was fair for the work and they explained our insurance benefits clearly. They are a great team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Bufkin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQF1PjshaJe3Wy0Ecs4Wf9Y3VsdNyjoiilzRQXfQ01VLTiUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service. Visit was for a cleaning and 6 month check up. Fortunately I have really good strong teeth. From X-rays to cleaning, polishing, and fluoride treatment (and arriving exactly on time-not late) I was in and out within 30 minutes. I was barely seated in the waiting area and my name was called.  Love this clinic. I have been using them for 4 years and I’m never disappointed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda Nelson (Nana5)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXz1IV_eX4cD7WmApnKXtiqvh31dQcXyCrxicG-ZoV3Surz2LMR=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very satisfied with Portland Dental. Dr. Malhotra is friendly, professional, and good at what he does. His dental techs are friendly and skilled at what they do. The office staff is so efficient and helpful. Though going to the dentist may never be something I enjoy, I am so grateful that Dr. Malhotra opened his practice in Portland.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Blatnik","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVhyaY8P1tnqF6y7qk8PPdXfrCgqVJKo6TVXPiU8jMFYh-L9aWX=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very happy with the care my six year old daughter received here. She has never had X-rays because she's so scared usually screams cries and kicks. And not one tear came out of her eye at her visit here, only jokes and laughs. Definitely going back. Thank you all for taking such good care of my baby girl.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1ypANpYCDxC5whAfSCQOscPjc0cPDui-5GOB7LewWRGtut3vYe-TIeMnF3_IXJFC-dM-Fe03v0Kt1G8P2RyfL39Yszx8yR-Ffj9j4oCP4Pa4IIWypfJI1-Xbg5Yx0B8xzgqv7szw=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1L-lCYiJRK6tCtTvSwoW_A3rluwYtaVb8wY56_B-4jUm7zDwtpXlh9l0GGR6ym-xbCAaQ6orvjfbzDMUVVwZobrXN_N_3HBvUEXSGykUVf9GIF85HM2vXSh5so3TBagbaTrjg=k-no"],"When":"2025-1-4"},{"Name":"Jose Juarez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKCrbJ31-4XrpcuP8HhePVQyn_Mk2gZFFMMjrzBTCPR7E7oVA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Really good experience here! Dr. Hani was great and made everything easy to understand. His assistant Jamie was super nice, knowledgeable, and did an excellent job with my cleaning. Clean office and very professional staff whole team was friendly and the office was spotless !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"May Sanders","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRZuZEpksIB4WDkRSshflgsmPEWfrdQuQp-Z1S_-05pnBAziuM=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the dentist he is very gentle compared to others I have seen. Staff were friendly. Got seen on the same day but it was over a 2 hour wait. I was given a quote over the phone and when I got there it was going to cost alot more. They didn't send me away. They did everything to help me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Crystal Breon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjURd0AF3x50EiTxgsOengZrcKKvCvGRTc2-33llYWQMMJJwpdQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The integrity of the staff saying they took my husband and I insurance and then getting a bill in the mail because they were not in network with us is shady. Please make sure you see if you are covered before calling here because they will lie \u0026 say yo