-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I called this office as a new patient and was able to be seen the same day. My visit was perfect from the initial phone call with Miss Laura to Mrs. Carol in the back to Dr. Sikes And also to the lady who checked me out, I cannot remember her name, but the customer service was top-tier and I just love everything about this office. This will definitely be my new dentist. I was educated on things that I have not been educated on in my 40 years of life when it comes to my oral health.  I couldn’t have asked for a better visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"April Daniel","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVN9qgjfED5Pva4efDNrKh4-H6F351Dy-rdN7iZLZAPl2LIJuqe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent staff, excellent service, and very professional all the way around making you feel right at home.  Maddie took care of my cleaning and x-rays today, it was painless and a very pleasant experience.  I highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gregory Michael Masood","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKFOQ2d-eUwpo_bVjItzIrq2sO5mTOlghiiR1_3r49AjP6CNg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The kindest, sincerity, professionalism and personal care received from all of the staff is above and beyond one’s expectations.  Interaction with all of the lovely ladies on the team, from the moment you enter at the reception desk and then throughout your dental needs process is met by such genuine and very personable employees. The level of care, consideration for your particular needs and application of the latest dental practices offers exceptional patient services. Knowing that such a reputable dental practice staffed as it exists, will immediately give reassurance and remove apprehensions for one to put off receiving the corrective services for improving and maintaining you dental health. Sincerely submitted, GMM.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharon Wagner