sercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3qvL15BmpEKIYULp6-IAl8fUh93h7l0_SJ6Y7T0hv7h11zYhT3UmsqZvScaAldHg4jee76wEwskwBQykajXaVFUtsPrCE1Epz1n2O-Mgx014HKHUH7q2m5DqjBkM8wL2ocMzsViNwnx8rR=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Jt3SutNtvDFBNq_bW_qi_b9l3ev4AymEDJTPg0AAdUxSDsnUX5c-a34IhBfx_RxodLqHsGrBQhjO0PkOcOVITW2mLduFBLk4NOKrUbeR7BsmQ8PKa58gf7Nb7Ic9bUxa0sE4IYWTFPyQB=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-6"},{"Name":"TheFamilyof3 Arhontidis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUOdOXnveuRLz7SBjldM7gWHNtjXr5sH5L77SlQm8sK6qa51Ijz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can’t say enough good things about Smile Texas. Dr. Dooley took such great care of me, and I’m very grateful for the additional help and support from Dr. Haws. From start to finish, the entire staff was genuinely warm, kind, and professional, making me feel comfortable and confident throughout my treatment. The final result exceeded my expectations, and I’m so happy I chose Smile Texas. I highly recommend them to anyone looking for exceptional dental care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2FOoFLx2sLDI3yPC1uLNLX-r7NV2c1yvF0SG2QgIRNW2RKedDqCZGaT4u8Mtwaz_hO-tHiaL_yKLMpL5nC2vzxPQbUxHe65yYO2zJhGMuKq9DCBx3JmnHWVvOrTrqZUuiNQuGdHdr_fc9E=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-15"},{"Name":"Carrie Nelson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocII6IsZSEsXbsNWMrvd9LHyO2egaZs9paG7R-uTN0huatopDQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's difficult to put into words what a change this has made in my life in just a month.\n\nIf you have less-than-perfect teeth, smiling isn't something you do automatically, or without reservation - you find ways to smile without showing your teeth.  SmileTexas changed that for me.  Without realizing it, I was smiling more, and I felt lighter, brighter and happier.  Nothing else in my life had changed, but I felt better about myself, how the world would see me.\n\nThe process is everything I could have hoped for as everyone at SmileTexas has been amazing.  Exceptional!  The entire crew is friendly, engaging, and very supportive!  From the initial consultation to the extraction I needed, then the temporaries and finally, the finished veneers, the procedures are explained.  During the actual process, they make sure you're comfortable and not in any pain.  They also follow-up in the days after to ensure that there aren't any issues or pain.  Caring for your mouth and new teeth is part of their care.\n\nThis is a big step, and a not-insignificant expense, but it's worth it.  Especially with Dr. Davis and the SmileTexas crew.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miles McPherren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIC96DHkZWJv5RE0jVE4INGA9r7ZKlo8QGvRK-Ub4xWlqjFfA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Couldn’t be happier with my experience at Smile Texas. The team was professional, welcoming, and truly takes pride in their work. They walked me through everything with care and made the whole process smooth and comfortable.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0hlV-jMHFTuy9eSSe9k7A8aHUffRMW_-wXZQ_rPtuXPaUg_BceEc6SIuyJKvdqWTyY5u7ohhJPwZUlS4qmKlCDxuVmm-LboJXyuiGJocENGrgDBgok9S-4talSLMrpkyKPGsNF_vkM03PW=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1W9qkoWhjY1CYZZ5Qx52b9w5_CJAHJMtVySltqKsWGuOEIwgxF6K6sbflz_41dAtbHHwJeImk5O_FoZw4FO0lp9LOY5A2y71px-NR1WbY0xd0Xh1wv0Lg8WZJv8XqSBDDVIIAoHP5_dSdR=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-4"},{"Name":"Amber Bryant","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-mNRmqd3P-ncZMUOP5AKjMDgS5gEPDjIPdSSYpGjM9L8N3g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly highly recommend Smile Texas! The staff is wonderful and so caring. I had tons of questions about the process but they were answered effortlessly and seamlessly by staff.\nDr. Davis did my smile makeover, he’s very knowledgeable and kind; so professional and really pays attention to details and care about his patients.\nI have anxiety when it comes to anything related to the dentist due to previous bad experiences and they handled that so well, I felt at ease and very comfortable.\nBefore I would hesitate to show my teeth due to an old crown in the front of my smile that made me self conscious.\nNow I can be confident and smile knowing that I have I nice beautiful smile now!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Makahla Ross","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTJ_za9WMu1qRUb20Y8HZUBDDAjeXZ4006nEky6x1dTRldWFdg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had the absolute BEST experience at Smile Texas!!! I have always been a little bit fearful of going to the dentist, but after visiting Smile Texas- I didn’t want to leave. Every single staff member and Dr. was overwhelmingly amazing. They all were so kind and made you feel comfortable, making the entire smile makeover so easy! Dr. Dooley is absolutely incredible- and I couldn’t be happier with my smile transformation!!!! My wedding is in two short weeks- and I get to walk down the aisle with not only the man of my dreams- but the smile of my dreams!!! Thank you so much to everyone at Smile Texas and Dr. Dooley!!! I walked away with an incredible smile- and many friends amongst the staff! Thank you all so much! Love you guys!!! - Makahla","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
