 you and turned to leave. She asked if I wanted to make an appt for the 19th. I let her know that I'll schedule an appt with a dentist that tells the truth up front. Will never do business with them again (already had X-rays done for the procedure) and will certainly not recommend them to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI5JGN8YnIGjJ5hEmUSCPUpye7b8VMnlkzFYM2GubfE38v6pg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love the ortho team and the new doctor, as he also explains everything step by step and makes sure I understand how to take care of my braces. I don't remember the three dental assistants that always get me but big thank you for being gentle and helping me pick out my color bands and the new doctor for helping me correct my smile. Also thank you to the friendly front desk lady that sits closest to the entry in when being taken to the back! On the left, She always remembers me and greats me super friendly.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Egypt Butler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTtecVXHL7lPzkRR04Fajq7enkl3SBwBm_sg0zk7vNkLfpKWxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend them!  I had a dental emergency and needed to be seen right away. The staff got me in and were very attentive to all my needs. I came in pain and left feeling so much better. Thank you again to all the Famila Dental Team you all are much appreciated!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Muhle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVPtfzt8_pTC7JCHG1esfg8MsJD0lIBMpk_knS_Dj8xX_PfBo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"It was frightening and  a Spirits I have never had before ever with a dentist, never\\n Had a dentist, tap my teeth with a metal, asking me if it hurt and I never had a dentist. Bring me goggles to put on my face.  And they do that to a person that doesn't trust Dentist and scared of dentist I would never bring my child to there.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1BWY5U3n4OAHyYe90jLACM87L_1LN3QX_7cgAcYj2WbSaywjM0_WMaxJeDOmrz3r9VWITp-JHWVL3Hb6jyHeqFu7MiK-5kivo4V5rtYgq38ldr7fuJ3dAmqjRs5cnQLbX1-crl0t9y36np=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-8"},{"Name":"Amanda Podowski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxaij6MGJNwXrHgGB8O9iwecQEV_XqVZBFrhCgZcp3y-XzN_7Upg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My kids really did enjoy there visit today even though it was a long wait... But well worth it when we found out what was wrong with both of them during there check ups... The Nurses and the Dr was absolutely wonderful... Made them feel welcomed and most of all very comfortable! Will see y'all again soon! Thanks for everything and truly helping my teens! 🤍🤍🦷🦷🪥🪥😁😁","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3Q-bF2EDHiurx1YB85vtc2j07HYSue7cRYZu7K_0Kl9o0PB4L-lzidwiZ104iy8TSptaRcxo4rRsfMk2mSU4TZ9SKwEsALOAr6IbB_F4ASnZqoJoX_Y6jUUPhLOgtPESy9wY-Atg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3AXS7a55cluMXR9HaPp0o5Sxr0rDsR6CqFXhFE8j0rP2PKGW-0YeT39hZr9PKA9vA2dTUQxw9BOznTJ8dSeb5e6bWHPYpZQUQqWWYWiWvtlFTnqUdWta9sOb7lwhUN5nfBuNfP=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-27"},{"Name":"Rentia Mathis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXX6EcgfjBgriIDkxj_EQfiTLEYoBoCewjq7bpIvh14DeuD5iAbwQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The dentist was amazing and as sweet as they come. I am very pleased with everything here. Dental assistant and the one who polished my teeth he is so amazing and polite. All the recipients were all so knowledgeable and helpful very good service.I would refer anyone to here. Thank you all","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daniel Ceron","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXGE8N90I7mE5uqhr8SOR6SsK5eCgR2Qpn1ayYfglH2E6OyN9cg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Misleading Practices and Coercive Billing\n\nI strongly caution against using this office. I scheduled and pre-paid $98.00 for an exam and general cleaning on November 4, 2025.\n\nAfter the exam was complete, and while I was prepped and lying in the dental chair, the doctor informed me that the necessary cleaning (scaling for minor buildup) was not covered by the original fee. I was presented with a surprise upcharge of $330.00 and was told they could not proceed with any cleaning, even the one I had pre-paid for, until I got up and paid the full amount immediately.\n\nThis is a classic bait-and-switch. The office used the mandatory $60 exam fee simply to ambush me with an exorbitant, unbudgeted charge. I left the office having paid $60 for a useless exam and received zero treatment.\n\nBe aware of their pre-payment and diagnosis tactics. Highly unprofessional and financially misleading.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
