:"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Maggie Martinez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPBU0rx293I8vJ6Rz2i5HL0z-DvRVgXZVkHHvwNhaXZ2GTX2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the BEST dental experience I’ve ever had. From the moment I walk in, my dentist and her entire team make me feel genuinely cared for. They don’t just make me feel safe and comfortable—they truly pamper me. Every detail is thoughtful, every interaction is kind, and they go above and beyond to make sure I’m relaxed and at ease.\nIt’s rare to say this about a dental office, but I actually look forward to my visits. I feel taken care of, listened to, and treated like a VIP every single time. If you’re looking for a dentist who combines exceptional skill with warmth, compassion, and an amazing team, this is the place. I couldn’t recommend them more highly!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Cooke","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXi2eZDv6JbRVQraq2HF1Q_IAsbV-ZlC3T8LfqMJfsPjW6ICOhN-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone was soo nice and helpful here. They make you so comfortable and are very gentle and informative on everything they're doing. I've booked my next appointment and can't wait to get back and get started on working towards having a healthy and beautiful smile again. They are very up front with your treatment plan moving forward so you always know what's happening next. I'm soo glad I chose The Houston Dentists and I feel like I'm in the BEST hands and care with my treatment moving forward. I'm soo EXCITED!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Krissy krissy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIfOOpk8Nd7zG0LaIHHENIuGakJhSNpn_xJ37TlLqp0ryCggw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They say first impressions are everything and boy did Houston Dentists deliver!!! You are immediately greeted by the receptionist and offered coffee, beverages, and snacks. Next is a tour of the facilities where you see the well decorated, clean rooms, and state of the art high tech equipment for X-rays and what appeared to be hospital grade sterilization! Then, I was presented with a brochure with a beautifully boxed gift! The dental assistant and dentist were absolutely knowledgeable, professional, and went out of their way to ensure I was completely comfortable at all times! Me being thoroughly impressed is an understatement! Best decision ever!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chima Mbadugha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWxL63oXl5-0_NDOisquOSEXTTpJmCq0tgpf5OyJLFjzTKXHcoM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been searching for a new dentist for a while, and after reading various reviews, I decided to give The Houston Dentist a try. I can immediately say that from the moment I stepped off the elevator and into the space, I knew I made the right choice.\n\nThe office goes above and beyond to make the experience as easy as possible. They’ve genuinely achieved a \"spa-like\" feel—offering everything from headphones and TVs to weighted blankets. They clearly prioritize patient comfort, and it makes a huge difference.\n\nThe staff is truly phenomenal. I want to give a huge shout-out to Dana. She is a big reason why I decided to come back and move forward with my procedures. Her energy and the way she connects with patients is amazing; we were laughing the entire time I was there. I told her I was going to write this review because she is a major reason why I feel this is the place I want to be for my dental care.\n\nThe rest of the team is equally impressive:\n\nDr. Coury is really great and a pleasure to work with. I’m actually excited to have her put my permanent crown in.\n\nSeida was excellent and made the process of getting my temporary crown seamless during my second visit.\n\nJuanita and Elizabeth at the front desk were both wonderful, and even Sherita (whom I just met today) gave me a great greeting the moment I walked in.\n\nJob well done to the whole team—I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beth Kreuzer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZDGwUN--v_2-l2W9pLULknUeAbxezCQf0_mcia8RZNjesGA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience with Oral Surgeon Dr. Foust, his employees and all the staff at Dr. Fraser’s office was impeccable. The removal of my wisdom teeth was flawless and so professionally done. I cannot express enough how the whole procedure was quick and painless. Incredibly grateful! Kudos to all who made this procedure professional and I highly recommend. 5 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Taylea Ferguson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXiataZ_1Oo73_rTvjhOl8iCiUcOTVWQhogH7S_Frdp4cyK-0RA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"everyone that works here is lovely and always makes sure you’re comfortable. you get to watch tv, they give u a blanket, and you can get a hand mask with warmers (free) all during your appointment. they make going to the dentist enjoyable!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Penny Pfeffer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKKdqh-WnN8gZebo53by8Y4CigftcvRa_XJjxikFyLq90btMg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Before I decided to go to Houston Dentists for the safe removal of the amalgam fillings from my teeth and have them replaced.with other fillings, I did a very thorough searching for truly the best ones in the Houston dental industry.  I'm blessed that I made this decision..  This team of dentists and staff are hard to match in their skills, professionalism and compassion, not to mention that they are a bevy of beautiful ladies.\nThank you so much Houston Dentists .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Juana Pineda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-P5r9rSbW-X_VrEC9tY6xEPajfCxlN5XM6bw-wsYIIqOocu6T=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow!\n\nI was not expecting the attention to detail and care that I received today. The Houston Dentists truly crate about their patients. You can tell by the time they take to get to know you and introduce themselves. I am beyond impressed.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
