uly great with children. Even though my daughter was fussy, he managed to keep her calm and successfully remove the tooth. I’m very thankful for the care and professionalism we received.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"YaelG","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrMbX0nFzYTsV4nZkVvBpJ4TPZZE1n4t3vj6l8BkA0QJxT4g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We all want to avoid dentists, but this attitude changed for me after I found Dr. Yoon. He is by far the best dentist I have ever had. His gifted hands combined with genuine care for his patients and an obvious strive for excellent treatment put him high above others.\n\nI am leaving the country and, as I told him, I wish I could take him with me… If you need a dentist, don’t even think twice, go there!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Prince Imo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxZ0PT7DTfSeFZurrmt9pXcAumLcvKYpycYiQtGenA_mqWud4W=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an amazing experience. They got rid of my plaque and really broke it down to me on how to keep up with my oral care. Highly recommend.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3l3EuhGWp251ARxf5rIw9BfcBz5mAFBekt-9V0snoL-Au5GrmLRZr2bh7fhdJxoEx811wZNM7CNq7aILN7EyqPAHoUm38oKp0JWF569AcU7i8dJYLmCtxutGJsz9oDWhCzirPJI-MpJFo=k-no"],"When":"2026-3-5"},{"Name":"Kaley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKheEx8e5p3zJFrlIas6Ukc6-dG5V4LALYpgYgJezkFQSppmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was nervous coming in but Dr. Park and Annette made the visit very comfortable! They taught me the right way to floss based on my teeth shape! Now I am feeling more confident 😊 highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"David Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKE7PM5vsD-VczYI64aWJtilpvJ3EwmDn9sVeFYXv26zvlB0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I visited Clearview Dental in Round Rock, TX a few days ago for our semi-annual check-ups and cleaning.  This was our first visit to Clearview. First a tech took thorough x-rays of my teeth for Dr.  Yoon to review. Subsequently hygienist Sierra cleaned my teeth and did a fantastic job. She took her time and first carefully measured my gums and then slowly and methodically cleaned my teeth. Sierra has a very pleasant personality and patiently listened to my concerns and extemporaneous remarks. Dr. Yoon came in and discussed the results of my x-rays, highlighting a couple of areas for us to watch. Dr. Yoon is very conservative and does not perform unnecessary work. He is very focused and calm which inspires confidence in his patients. My wife had a similar positive experience during her cleaning and exam. We highly recommend Clearview Dental and have already scheduled our next cleaning and exam with Dr. Yoon a few months from now.\n\nSincerely,\nDavid and Thanh Smith","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dylan Ceslak","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRdQgGqJranDi-8bGHUOc-R6WZbptlY_zP0khChIhjnjPpYg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Phenomenal dentist experience. Dr. Yoon and his staff were able to get me in and out in an hour during my work lunch break. They were extremely efficient and knowledgeable. Clearview will certainly be my dentist moving forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hanjin Lee","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXgjYzJz8VDQgPhpxejrCARfWUfszp8agAy-1apEwyQrzMD_YG2zg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Clearview Dental since they opened in 2016, and every visit has been fantastic. Dr. Yoon and the team are amazing! They handle everything professionally and with care. When I needed a crown fixed urgently, they took care of it quickly and smoothly (no panic, just perfect care 😄). They also reply super fast to texts, which makes everything so convenient. Friendly, professional, and reliable! I highly recommend Clearview Dental! Big thanks to Dr. Yoon and the whole team for keeping my smile happy and healthy! 😁","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
