istance, scheduling/rescheduling appointments that fit my son's A\u0026M class schedule - much appreciation!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeffrey Ziegelmann","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVgCWiENkYy9mZH2ctkR-sa-N648RVhS20FwSDxpWrQ1gl_G7dq=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"University Dental is amazing. The staff is always friendly and Dr. Spence always mitigates before the most expensive option. Clear communication and friendly faces. Highly recommend them if you are near the BCS area or new!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Mashburn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsCbmrO2X6R6VZUB67Q0ckYAIL31aMEv8-3rbcyOs5gVWaBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first time in and it was amazing from the start! Def. The fastest service I’ve ever experienced. The assistant and dentist (Dr. Kramer) were amazing! Super patient with what I had going on and acted very quickly to resolve it vs. potentially dragging anything out. I def. Have found my new dentist! Thank you guys!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheri Hendrick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVHuf8D8FY4xfQU9bKlknqwS5zgA5WMcchOWoxAKLt7EBJ4HQQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Spence makes feel relaxed and safe. I have severe anxiety/fear of dentist due to a childhood incident and this office goes above and beyond for me! They are all so patient and kind!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheena Petty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUFwcQgWAdeCayKo0cLkkzt9Ew9oY3kjYC9NSt4le9M0fqRoSLqjw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My parents and I have been going to University Dental for years now. Usually I just go every six months for a cleaning, but recently chipped a tooth and Dr. Kramer fit me in the next day. The staff are always so nice and welcoming. If you're looking for a dental home, I highly recommend UD!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Candy Mcguire","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXgOQFFJfQ1rYTZZS4NNeJ7yKtEyE54U2K0kbOjhRpCzTqY748dQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I have seen Dr. Kramr for years. He and his staff are the most professional, efficient, courteous and kind group of people! We love the staff and facility! Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharron Rosedahl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVaKogZwqSnQorGF6zJ0MiRnT_OmgfvhE6XjWXSyBbx84kd7TCM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As usual all the people I encountered at University Dental Associates from the ladies at the front desk to Dr. Spence's hygiene assistant to Dr. Spence himself were all very kind and diligent in their work.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
