 I come to the practice I am greeted with smiles and good wishes. Maribel is always \"en pointe\" with my Financial and Accounting information, all smiles and professionalism.\nVanessa combines care with knowledge, experience and cool efficiency.  Alyssa is \"Janey on the Spot\", able to read my questions and sense my concerns, even before I can articulate them.\nHats off to a cohesive, competent and compassionate group of folks.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carmen Mandato","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmUroevHhuJCzHA24syOmt7nXbDUirDJSBwcTzAM1Ou4RalExBMw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I cannot say enough about Dr Pigneri’s unbelievable care and compassion. From the first visit he was calm, patient, and truly listened. He explained the plan in clear terms, reviewed imaging with me, and never rushed. The treatment itself was meticulous and painless. His professionalism shows in the details and his kindness shows in the way he checks on you, answers every question, and follows up. For anyone with dental anxiety, this is the person you want. Thorough, professional, and genuinely caring. I live states away and will be traveling back for his services as I have tried so many others, and genuinely, no one compares. Im so grateful to have found his office, whose staff and particularly Cindy could not be more warm and helpful.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vincent G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIRwSYmdpDKmumuvQDxMYMNcZzgmdm90iBEzw3P0lVTudGmFg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone was excellent! They got me a walkin appointment and fixed my dental issue in less than 1hour. I look forward to becoming a regular patient. Thanks to Dr. Pigneri, Vanessa \u0026 Maribel!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Hunt","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX_KxZ0-Lsgau_fq4Y832a1nvomuVv3X4KxUsTtodukIFsVyN5a=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love the whole staff they are very friendly and inviting especially the wonderful receptionist Maribel and Dr. Sudarat is amazing dentist and she will make your smile look amazing and Vanessa is one of the best assistant.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffani Simien","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIDQ6mwDUbvlJG7pJLwpMK4GxEhF8DY-zCYPh1OuqlsrT34YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The receptionist who answered the phone was very professional and welcoming. I have crowns that need to be fixed, a few cavities and an extraction. I really hope my experience is a good one. Seeing as I’m terrified of the dentist . Fingers crossed 🤞🏾","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tifany Urias","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8FceUSjoYpkoJzg1NRFRJ6EaITT5FDbjvg5_HaTHsU3V_cA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Pigneri and his staff are the absolute BEST!!! I had a complete crown done in less than 2hours! Once the anesthesia wore off I had no pain at all and was able to eat and drink with no problem! They made the whole process smooth and even provided a blanket and pillow to make sure I was comfortable. I highly recommend this dentist office, they never disappoint!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maximiliano Degwitz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVr0PTQrX7qaGOTXbgCFySCvcczLGFhszep5kgtSfJLz5ZBkHN7iw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Deissy,l, has been cleaning my teeth and gums for years, and I’ve never had a better experience. Yesterday, I chipped my front tooth, but Meribel promptly scheduled an appointment for me first thing today. Dr. Pigneri fixed it flawlessly, making it look as if it never happened. This dental office is the most professional and provides the best service I’ve ever encountered.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Wes Dewey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJkfVx5fqng9OBFEpB84k6NS5VxI60DNRSSRaiP4AkEgu1jww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful new patient visit today! Maribel and Rashida were fantastic, and I was able to get in for the first half of my cleaning the same day. It was a painless procedure, and I'm looking forward to my next visit.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
