gender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"James Hopper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKGdnolrWHxUkprdLkztEBEhx_lVf6Hn4xq_PZq7ry3hT4WDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Somehow, getting three fillings done was an enjoyable experience!?!?  Dr. Shvets came through on his motto of a pain-free experience and I felt no discomfort.  He and his staff were very thorough and were perfectionists with doing a great job.  You could tell that top quality is the priority and I never felt like they were rushing.\nAlso, the staff was extremely friendly, knowledgeable and professional.\nOverall, a much better experience than it was with my previous dentist, I'll be back for sure.\nHighly HIGHLY RECOMMEND!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Donovan Dunn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhJAwDXF_3egm65X72RejC_WUD5i3ACC7_AnCv9rRomLirMXvK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just came here for the first time earlier today and it was a fantastic experience! I haven’t been to the dentist in a while so I was not sure on what to expect, but they are professionals and keep you in good hands! All the staff are super friendly and use the best technology I have ever seen to ensure your teeth are well taken care of! 5/5 stars and I look forward to coming here for all of my dental work!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maricela Valencia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWdr_9gGbWhSp0fj_q_qhMGNF-TdmrUHp95FW4alrXj3jZYGnY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had my first appointment here at Craft of Dentistry today as a new patient and everything went really well! I was excited to try them out after reading great reviews. I was due for my 6th month cleaning and everything they did was efficient and done with care. Everyone I talked to was welcoming and happy to be there. We talked about possibly whitening my teeth as well as getting my wisdom teeth removed soon which I am confident I will be taken good care of for that. They all have lots of experience and know how to treat patients with respect. Definitely will recommend them to anyone looking for a new dentist office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brenda Harte","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJZ2-hz7qM65sPQyXf0lUixRkn7OFSRd3YZh1Wca-mru3kRbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is great!! So friendly from the front of the office to the back. I needed a new dentist as mine, who I loved, retired. I have had many dentists and I’m pretty picky about them and their staff. I was due for dental visit and found these wonderful people online and read the Google reviews. I popped in a few weeks ago to check it out and made the appointment. I had my visit today and this place deserves its 5 star rating. Plus, it’s such an elegant and modern space. I saw Dr. S. (Yaron Shvets) and he is very professional and knowledgeable yet chill. Very kind and considerate and great at explaining. I’m so happy I found Craft of Dentistry!!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2duFT5GyvYdl1xP4zLg7ZTSiJekVpsTO5yrpk6UPWLVsLYq12s2hG9upR6qOL1_qOuB66bSj7mR0VKzBiWml3z3X8XdVlcd5s4Fq4Erlu__HS9_p01ACG6uJEf9iDwUMFI3PZs8GPJQrs=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn20HaykhrlzbCvPpGJlevwo9RhYmZICKS4YrAO7fWehWaf4-a3bZYrmuLaeYBgcP6_tdf3x5KXTtRDuS7ijwBU5G0JTlmBhqlhYHmWWzittYQRftRbDidWAuM3lX93LXTjGF-TAfTYlb0ea=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2mOttV56rqqEbZYnkxnLC3RRSy_labt0h-i0PGi0IQFPwKgZoRo18KbFyrEujxFtYyvuAJhmUF1vrlJmdrOSYDXUNHtaz8rGFULTjnofjbLIc6JJIxB-eFTkEo5p9DVXiCHWyoZfmEJGrz=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3GDHmbnXviyqG1CbHMud-8rWlUQjsZgZxz1cvzd4q14wAZxKwhIYzvTW1PwttH5sZSTLERKa7Hpo22c9Wlv2FhpCq8mpDOELGp2_pbrBC5uMh9CjKlM6FiyMq_FhKLMSsPtXiDGPdtTefn=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2KDK1bsPhZvL9NyXxaqWK4A0y8e4EaV3gX_1O9AtKQcgR_kYjP8CNHbADuZW6Y0IeM1eaZAMDq342jtDWrTuXZbA_rKEO541RVd_OGPFkRfdBxs-BHRQbmCN6trya1lhS71Y3oNODc02BQ=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-22"},{"Name":"Akamu Ainokea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTKtr2hHoSX_X3V1zX_Tm9nnLUXvfcL82VWOO31j7XaE6Qms0s=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down, my favorite dentist office. The staff goes above and beyond to make sure you have a comfortable experience. Everyone I've encountered was very pleasant and kept me informed on the next step or even different viable paths for my dental health. On top that Craft of Dentistry is affordable. I would recommend Craft of Dentistry  to anyone and everyone!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Melissa Wabschall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUW17GY6aiyOQz-GQyRzb-6ULkX7gk8HFwYxN7OhO_DEhc4Yk8SNQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to Craft of Dentistry for a few years now, and it has been wonderful. They fitted me with a night guard that has made all the difference in preventing jaw pain at night. I have enjoyed everyone I've met with in the office. A few of my teeth are super sensitive, and the hygienists have managed to still clean them well without making me jump - that's rare!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"J H","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuVr-PrDwLUQ_VWU7i2UGv3E4faQEfEbaJhH1r7k9oYnuPxQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my first appointment at Craft of Dentistry with Dr. Lyon yesterday and I am so happy I found them! Dr. Lyon is a gem and provided me with great information on preventative care. You can tell the whole team cares about excellence—they even went out of their way to compliment the work of my previous dentist, which was such a nice touch. The atmosphere is professional, the staff is lovely, and the care is top-tier. A 5-star experience from start to finish!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Avalos","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIFWo1ZufJnC_2uhJRI-fzVW6LJLvBKhadklPbQTsQ6dv8UshIAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my fisrt time coming to this place and I had a great experience. I haven't been to a dentist in about 3 years so I was a bit nervous. They have a warm welcoming environment when I first walked in. One of the hygienist came and gave me a tour of the place and walked me to my chair. They made me feel very calm and relaxed. Everything glided through smoothly. Luckily my teeth were in overall good shape. I plan to stick with them and was able to schedule my 6 month check up already. They're amazing!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
