nsurance/financial questions are covered.\n\nThanks for all y’all do!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Teresa Thy Le","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYOTWKGFoPifucPs9qaiKti1idNh_Gs7OO-mB2pEKNoFiJFCa8FA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff is amazing!!! Tiffanie, Valentina and Dr. Jaros were all kind, informative and professional. I loved my experience and felt at ease the entire duration of my visit. They did not make me feel anxious one bit and the process was very transparent and easy-going. I would highly recommend Austin Dental Works for your dental care needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anuj Bellare","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVBF08O3Lrmv6lxryc95tNL4h69AendaH9NtrYKFExHxivcYoUF=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have only been through 3 appointment - an introductory appointment, dental cleaning and cavity filing + crown prep. The experience has been great until now. Everyone here has been super friendly. Dr Jaros is clearly skilled at dentistry, explaining every step of the process. She also often asks how you are doing which is very comforting. Nobody in the world ever said “I look forward to my next dental appointment” but this place comes close to making you feel that way. 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tanya Embers","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocItKPJ4nNafLE0GFEg3A5sVgnB7ghhpKCA_5er2leztIt532g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love Austin Dental Works! The staff is so lovely and kind, and Dr Jaros is a great dentist. Always can trust their recommendations and care. They never try to sell you more than you need and are super easy to schedule with.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Todd McDougall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJVUCq3mTlAT5-fMdHzKuhIsoXbZ43DbfNGjSS0Mun0A2WMfQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Austin Dental Works has been my dentist for over 5 years now. The staff is super friendly and head Dentist is excellent.  They also give free whitening every 6 months!  Romans 10:9","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alicia Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUjDWWr9emtJAQ7xjR6Q_vBX7iIn9J2fO7hBa4MX78t5dCyA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best dentist I’ve had and you never have to wait. They schedule people perfectly so you are in and out. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joni Buschow","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDG-npJ_DwGtusTPY5YovhzYO1CPJ3JFId-9kKk-1XefYOqWM=s120-c-rp-mo-ba6-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Lindsey Jaros' expertly found a dental issue that was unseen by my last dentist. Her expertise to resolve this issue improved my health \u0026 well-being. Her staff is amazing: kind, helpful,\u0026 friendly.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
