int said deposit was non refundable. I felt it was honestly good up until that point, I really liked my hygienist Jax - she was super nice and genuine.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Koby Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLhjM_nAVNRN3mA7TXPl_nZLCw99paYGUfCgPPCPh06SaxHJg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I don’t write much reviews, but wanted to share my experience at breeze! They have been so helpful through out my time here. When I first moved to Austin I was unsure of where to go for Invisalign treatment, and luckily I found my way to Breeze! They have been extremely patient with me, accommodating, non-judgmental, and most importantly trustworthy! I’m done with my Invisalign treatment now, and my teeth have never looked better! Huge thank you to the whole breeze team, I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria Gallardo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLZDPrD9dpklp1fB4119jqmJMl5u2zNOCKyItVYZ29AHQgFHQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Was very pleasant. All staff were very friendly and welcoming. They were very informative about my what I needed done. The doctor was polite and helpful. Thank you for your courtesy.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
