},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Brad Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLzCTX5Lmtcko_UiZLVi-YcxkWCJ2kXSCdCjoq8HQ4qcF56DQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lewis and Taylor did a spectacular job today prepping me for my temporary crown, with my permanent crown arriving in a few weeks. They kept me up to speed through the entire process, making sure I was comfortable and pain free from start to finish. What impressed me the most was their extreme professionalism performed  with the utmost respect accompanied by a gentle spirit and cheerful encouragement. Such a comfort  for a patient who arrives a little nervous. I have been a patient with Barton Oaks Dental for 21 years and I am forever grateful for the care that I have received and the time they have spent to make sure that my dental needs are fully met now and in the years to come. Thank you, Courtney Thomas.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elissa Cantrell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXWQfSbyfYRKR6pi_UoAYjYidnDciNDFUsNgaW_-mO4CKh1lZc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lauren Lewis and Taylor make an outstanding team. From the moment I arrived, I felt comfortable, welcomed, and genuinely cared for. They work seamlessly together, which made the entire experience smooth and reassuring. I was completely at ease during my procedure and felt confident I was in excellent hands. I would highly recommend Dr. Lauren Lewis and Taylor to anyone looking for a professional, compassionate, and highly skilled dental team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"john conway","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJHgTmtwyOMSAWRbe6BMuOOzPUA8FW0kn2hY5a2M1bbYV7JUw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Lewis has done extractions and customized my dentures. She and Taylor have gone out of their way to make sure everything fits well and is comfortable for me. I feel good just stepping inside the office. I’m very grateful I found this practice more than 45 years ago!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Renee Taylor","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWP-MYcjTh3OWTp-NCBp_TIvL9zAz6Ph1fV8GGeiatyvi3GtimwBw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have to admit, I'm not usually a fan of the dentist or writing reviews, but my experience with Dr. Lewis and Taylor completely changed my perspective! This dynamic duo is simply exceptional when it comes to dental care.\n\nI’ve gone through some pretty extensive treatments that I thought would leave my smile hopeless, but Dr. Lewis is nothing short of brilliant—truly a genius in his field. And let me tell you, Taylor’s skills are nothing less than magical!\n\nFrom the moment you step through the door, they have a way of making you feel right at home. They know how to keep the atmosphere light and fun, making laughter a big part of the experience. The dentist's office isn't typically a place to look forward to, but they have me eager to return!\n\nIf you're looking for incredible dental care, look no further. I can't recommend them enough! They’re simply amazing—10 stars and the best in town! You absolutely won’t regret visiting them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cameron Pugh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXmuiZQsYL26-EwHpmQRlAUWdoc9eR1v_mGUsCLBwMHK4M4k5Ae=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Five Stars for the Barton Oaks Dream Team!\nThis place isn’t just the best dentist office in town — it might be the best in the entire state of Texas. (I haven’t been to all of them, but I’m willing to bet my molars on it.)\n\nFrom the moment you walk in, the whole staff is smiling, friendly, and somehow makes you forget you’re at the dentist. Kristi is a plaque-fighting superhero who keeps my teeth sparkling and my smile bright. If there were a gold medal for dental cleanings, she’d have it.\n\nDr. Shiva is awesome. Even though he occasionally drills into my face, I still like him. That’s how good he is. He’s always looking out for his patients and makes sure everything is done with care and precision. I trust him completely and that’s rare, because I don’t even trust my coffee maker to get my order right.\n\nI won’t go anywhere else. Barton Oaks is my dental ride-or-die.\nThanks to the whole squad, y’all are awesome!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tom Graser","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI24vu12rKd4V0QBIrsonGVy3S4s8g62N-0J4KdDoFZLaVWWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Started going to Barton Oaks Dental Group years ago based on a friend’s recommendation after my previous dentist retired, and it was the best recommendation I’ve ever gotten. They are super thorough, so I feel confident I’m getting the best care possible. I just had a filling replaced, and Dr. Lewis, Monica, and Amari coordinated to make the experience smooth and painless.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPIIZn6wVB3R7jzNJilfy-dNAPUrVE_nUYigV-HnzYL0MTGck=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The best experience ever with Taylor, Amari and Dr. Lewis. I have never enjoyed going to the dentist but this was surprising fun. And the follow up filling needed I did not dread coming nor did I even feel the shot for numbing my mouth. Top notch work \u0026 people with delightful personalities.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Elliana Krone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoVdGkEcgdNgNLErTCcv3T_4XZUBcI2xtMpcxag2sNaBnc2dXK=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I just started going to Barton Oaks Dental earlier this summer and have been so well taken care of! I came in with lots of issues with my teeth and have had to make multiple visits since my initial appointment. I'm a college student have a crazy schedule, but Dr. Lewis and my hygienist, Taylor, have done an amazing job, working efficiently and catering to my needs and schedule. It's such a warm and inviting environment, and while I always used to feel so stressed going to the dentist, I feel very safe coming into Barton Oaks. Highly recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
