","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Rigo Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuc3Wl9n2Y6AzrIKqRMNWIP4Wv-4Jv1ecjTaJ6yvHcrgI2htqGSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Devin and the entire staff at Aesthetic Dentistry of Georgetown are wonderful and make going to the dentist genuinely enjoyable. Our entire family loves coming to their office.\nFrom the moment you walk in, the atmosphere is so positive and welcoming. The staff is incredibly friendly, efficient, and always ready with a smile. Dr. Devin is absolutely fantastic—highly skilled, takes the time to explain everything, and has a great, comforting chairside manner.\nThey make you feel like family, not just a patient. If you're looking for an office that provides top-tier dental care while keeping you comfortable and laughing, look no further! My teeth have never been happier, and neither have I! Thanks for making dental visits a breeze!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Katie Kresl","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVmp6qETPmdnQUOIo8FPsggm5qYixZSVBdUJtWaU9ZboJBipK51=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had the best experience with Aesthetic Dentistry! Dr. Mark and his team are the only holistic, airway-informed dental practice I’ve found in the area. They look at the whole person-examining all aspects of your health, offering preventive solutions, making referrals when needed, and supporting long-term wellness. They are an absolute gem, and I’m so grateful to have found them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jordan Ramey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIXdrm1K4AJJWRYz0nKtF6VXlvwY_szEOLmOWJmQIGDmQ7cCg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the BEST dental experience I’ve ever had! Dr. Devin and Amy are absolutely exceptional—their professionalism, kindness, and genuine care made me feel completely at ease. The entire staff is amazing and so talented.\n\nThe office itself is top tier, with large private patient suites that feel more like a spa than a dentist’s office. And being offered a glass of wine while you wait? Such a thoughtful touch that makes the whole experience even more enjoyable.\n\nI can honestly say I’ve never looked forward to going to the dentist until now. Thank you Dr. Devin, Amy, and the whole team for setting a new standard of care! Highly recommend to anyone looking for the best in dental care. 🙌🙏👏💯","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Adrianne Hawkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWo3fEZrPpPzp_FIpqi9AhiwmjmkF6rPshO6w4T0NBQauT3auY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If I lived in Georgetown I would be their patient! I had an emergency on the road and needed a cosmetic dentist. I googled and found Aesthetic Dentistry..I read their reviews and was very pleased. I called and they were able to get me in first thing this morning. Ellen Boyas, RDA, assisted me in all my needs and was amazing. Dr.Chandler Herman DDS was my dentist and was extremely kind and courteous and decisive. As you can tell I am a very please transit passing through! Well done team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"N L","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWzluP9rO8IK7o6Y-7LockWnMLsIlnx31IUyXIb8ZzkEc34P7jj=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We highly recommend Aesthetic Dentistry of Georgetown. Their team provides consistent - gentle yet thorough dental care in a relaxed environment. Thank you to Dr. Duncan and Kristie who have provided extraordinary dental care.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2BcUeBU0IwGP-kEEp-kCyerf9iWAqk86xejZcBdP64CcnGmItobfSMvLUeqZr41RwMFFSYm5SzNmESrB6FgFPdWlDsEkm1znUOALLwOaCLKNST_knOyA9LRn7JuEYyrxlXscLoLnSH4zTN=k-no"],"When":"2025-6-16"},{"Name":"Y. W.","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbrUUm37Pb_jVamyxm5JfqAOWucYwI6pK3DyNsbOuADN3BMX75=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best care! Organized, capable, mindful of the smallest details. I arrived for my appointment. And I always get cold, but not to worry! The blanket was already on my chair! Exceptional! Dr. Mark and his staff are the best choice!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cherie Ford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXpObapuU4REayOdfVStXPRgft4OJFZvIvfy442I_XlbMX-UgY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was there today after cracking a tooth and they not only got me in but saved my molar and did a same day bridge . They were awesome and very  gentle . Dr Devin ROCKS ! I have a new best dental experience !  Thus comes after a failed implant attempt by another dentist on the same side of my mouth. To say I am grateful and happy is an understatement .","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sande Collins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLsODQhlRy513db8RLyj6v3-CHg6EzKuUSV6TC-swye-gTQRw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and Dentist at Aesthetic Dentistry of Georgetown are very nice. Amy is very educated. She showed me areas on the x-ray showing me areas that could be too weak for a crown replacement on my tooth.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
