g”. Of course they are after what he did…When asked how did I get that, the hygienist said it’s “genetics”. While periodontitis does have some genetic links, it most commonly occurs from poor oral hygiene. When I asked the hygienist how my teeth looked she said they looked great and that there wasn’t much plaque/tartar coming off from these cleanings. They gave me a payment plan for each of these “cleanings” which were $500 each. If I had gotten a routine cleaning, my insurance would have covered it, but these deep cleanings were not. This dentist is not concerned about the patients well-being. They are only concerned about money. Their bed-side manner is strange (especially that dentist), they do not get back to you (unless it’s to receive a payment), and they only will help you if you use THEIR PLAN and spend LOADS of money. Save yourself the hassle, and money and don’t ever come here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tori Simone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWeywCSPGzUsu5sWVywQtssZp5CH9OstPVC0JYAWkkle9Zn3tOjOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The most amazing staff! They were all so comforting and sweet the dentist there was superb he got me in and out I was terribly afraid he did exactly what he said he’d do! Highly recommend them they took great care of me!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patricia DeSouza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV-g4I3_k6UYT-4mOxKmsdInF5vzbQZKkmkX6Fes_JMK1Z8nZiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have found some very nice people in this office, they are all very helpful and friendly they make you very comfortable. I was very scared of dentist but after coming here that feelings is gone. I would recommend them 100% for your dental work.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Roxanne Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwPUob4SyPU3ZZZpeRdc866R-ehQIUAIzgpzxnw42mz7pCpQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have past trama with dental experience, I have found my dentist!  Dr. Okafor is amazing. His gentle work and clear explanation calmed me immensely.  Highly recommend Universal Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pamela Etheridge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLOvMLaKtz7tEujZFIrtaw_gAQvbHBbMCw2cpCGvluY7xYaNA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was praying 🙏 and searching to find a dentist in an emergency situation! I had a crown, also lower bridge break off! I was in a lot of pain and had swelling in my face! I reached out to them, Universal Dental on a Saturday after Christmas and they were God sent for me! They called in a much needed antibiotic for infection, and made an appt for the next following Tues., morning! Mariah, the office manager has gone above and beyond to help me!! I have anxiety and she TRULY CARES!! I REALLY APPRECIATE HER, AND AM VERY GRATEFUL! THANK YOU!! Pamela Etheridge 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nina Washington","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUeHJtg5mD9THlytRLqCrRWIaZKwjXpWZWxvdFhreU_-dXuONJz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love, love, love Dr. Okafor! My 9 year old son had a procedure and was very anxious but he made him feel so comfortable. Very thoughtful dentist I would definitely recommend 1000 times!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Dancer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTdNp58WMj3lyQ-5ShfAvLmUgSX2xoDhayjpfisG4miJJGDutINA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Zoe was kind and remembered me from my first consultation. I was surprised to know that she had a smile like mine before her invisilgn journey. This inspired me even more, because her smile is beautiful! She was professional and knowledgeable.  I love it.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
