"Considering going to the dentist is never fun, coming to North Austin dentistry has helped me with my fears of going to the dentist. The girls at the front are so nice and friendly and helpful. Savannah explained everything in detail and was very patient while I asked questions. Christine was very helpful as well. They just give you a nice calm welcoming vibe. The assistants will hold your hand and pat your shoulder or whatever you need to calm you while you're getting that numbing medication. Aliyah was my assistant and and make sure that I was very comfortable. That's the part that scares me the most and it wasn't that bad at all..  Dr Miller is exceptional. He takes his time to talk with you to develop a plan for your future needs as well as listen to all your concerns you have at the moment. He explains everything in detail and sits with you as long as it needs to make sure it all makes sense. I will continue coming back. Oh by the way, the lobby is beautiful, comfortable and I love the kids nook along with the beautiful views from the rooms.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3BGTlSSWM-obYhSO7wJW6_EzjWXKIUiOvxB9iDHzqhlnitGiZk1lIjp_goTTjXmPx-CPmpeVkqjKBVk0EE8H73u5Km7r5oHHw9I65qPGEkQnwGaVP0cpW68eQbMOz1DTK8oOR4RCJumXD-=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn01gwHsJ8ubiMY79w14XVx7pJN1jgu3EKo86U6X3vgMrnkAqR2y616Ss5BQPCPAFOUUjUZwBY6DCd2lA8VWjHAKy5DwItsYFQnzKgqe9KDby0IzWvtfXEQ3i-o7pLaRJXN6TaFAUw1CT4o=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-23"},{"Name":"T. J. Wolfe","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7QhuDboSKFc9Qh-J67SRafzkkXpcGfXrpoIfDrAWkQawn9ro=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The entire office staff and assistants are always friendly and helpful. Dr Small was knowledgeable, caring, and informative about current and follow up treatment. I can’t say enough about Dr Logan, who was the first dentist I had the pleasure of working with. He’s kind, funny and knows his dentistry. I highly recommend North Austin Dentistry. Definitely 5 stars to this Dental Office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bev Ra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUT4-lJy3YLrs9kcqoI6AGhuU5EzPcGmQf7Je0Rt38XCHrCGuBg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to this dentist office for over 5 years now and they are wonderful. I found them when I was in an emergency situation with a broken tooth, and my teeth were a disaster overall. Dr Miller saved that tooth and fixed up a couple of others that were going south. I’m now settled in there with my regular hygienist, Leo, who really seems to care, offers great oral care advice, and is genuinely excited as my teeth have improved and are being well maintained. Their entire staff is very friendly. Thank you, North Austin Dentistry!\nFrom Beverly B.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rotem Grinberg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKrJvReNMqDt5AIXsOk2xGG56qNbQKuqD-OrOI8yzMVYVkm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such an amazing experience at this dental clinic! Everyone was super professional, kind, and welcoming. Leo took care of me — he was absolutely fantastic! So gentle, patient, and made sure I was comfortable the entire time. It’s rare to find someone who combines skill and genuine care like that. Highly recommend this place and especially Leo — 10/10!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aliyah","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLe2F-X_5FKmLJOWwqjqTri11NDlLq7U2xDYx4eSCSqIbKQLA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Most people think of the dentist as just another chore, but North Austin Dentistry truly changes that experience. From the moment you walk in, the team makes everything feel easy and welcoming. This was only my second visit with Kelyn for a cleaning, yet she still remembered me! She’s fast, thorough, and always makes sure I’m comfortable throughout the process. I also had the chance to meet Dr. Smalls today—friendly, skilled, and great at putting patients at ease. I really appreciate how calm the office feels and that I never feel judged for asking questions. Thank you for making dental care something I actually look forward to!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Henry Shepard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhc0dTiKQElix6OOwvLYLsAk8E9vMredNi-wFb1fpK10mKcDE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"North Austin Dentistry offers surperb dental services with friendly staff. I experienced a dental emergency when my in-mouth retainer broke off and Dr. Miller squeezed me in with little hassle to fix it. Since then, I've been attending for my year check ups with Leo, my hygienist who is always friendly and helpful with reminding me to floss regularly. Very good service, I highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
