tments. That level of responsiveness meant so much to us.\n\nThe office is extremely clean, organized, and comfortable, which immediately puts you at ease. They even gave us a courtesy call afterward to check on how we were doing that kind of thoughtful follow-up really shows how much they care about their patients.\n\nDr.Sinan is very calm, professional, and reassuring. He explains everything clearly and makes you feel completely comfortable throughout the visit.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dental office that is caring, responsive, and professional, Dental Experts is definitely the place to go!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary Stacy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWFprhDeC7E51IwXwzt8DU8cV03_kSapZNf36qvBidBYTjkpVu=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I personally can’t say enough about this office from the moment I walked through the door until my appointment was completed the front desk girls are AMAZING GEN and MICHELLE  are so helpful and the doctor himself is amazing so knowledgeable in his in Industry!\nThe assistants are AMAZING Duha, Iman, Tabby and  The hygienist has been AMAZING. I have gotten a deep clean and have no pain.\nSince I’ve been in this office, I have never had any pain. They’re very gentle very sweet and kind. I would recommend five stars to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ernesto Rivas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKgiCg0Ohalovvrhj-Gyqn4f0ykiTxbunMVRC1tovMV7FdZbg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend this clinic every body is very kind and friendly. The Doctor is Amazing He explained everything very clearly and in detail. Please if you’re in need of a dentist visit this place you’ll be amazed by the quality of the service and the professionalism of the Doctor Sinan and the Team 😊.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"E. Julia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocInDb398b1OMAvGgiSeEv1OK55BTzPMerMRzgjd-GWs1Kqhjg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This office was able to take my daughter in on a Saturday for emergency service. This was after a terrifying bicycle accident the night before that resulted in an EMS ride to the ER to determine if her jaw was broken or if her teeth were going to survive. I am so grateful for the service and care they provide my daughter during her dental emergency. They were a blessing to us in that time of need and I can't be more thankful for the impeccable work the Dentist put in, to ensure she recovered well and with her natural front teeth in tact. If I could give 10 stars I would.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Osama Abdelgader","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXtByL9z_uYiC0opJlzFfUBndF2ndKIYpDVVX4AkPcQg-LsoNKe=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been coming to Dental Experts since 2021, when I had my wisdom tooth removed by Dr. Sinan. The experience was so smooth back then that I came back again recently for 5 fillings. Dr. Sinan is excellent at what he does. His work is precise and his hand is very gentle. His assistant Eman and Duha were both very professional and kind throughout the process, which made everything much easier. The front desk ladies are always welcoming and helpful, too. I’ll be back again soon to replace my silver fillings with more natural looking ones. Overall, I couldn’t be happier with the care I’ve received here. Highly recommend!\n\n-Osama Abdelgader","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julius Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3x1Og-zipLCggxR_lu4YgGdXo0cIza62Cgqxw48gjUOwJAd3SXw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Sinan and Mandy always take great care of me when I come in. Everything is always thoroughly explained to me and my comfort is their top priority. I definitely recommend Dental Experts.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Snyder","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWuauf611o6lixhxV5CpPvWb0LoS1KrDkJglO_tZAe0gsQxOBvRvw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My crown fell off at lunch.  I was so impressed with this office!  Most places are closed on a Friday. They got me in right away and took very good care of me (I wasn’t even an established patient…I am now! 😊\nThey are so friendly, organized, and clean. The  ladies answering the phone, the front desk, the dental assistants and the dentists!  Thank you so much. How refreshing!\nI believe I just found my new dental office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ericka Kincheon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK7A0ZVJpH9M5PmRW81qhJ90vRjJWFbkcUlVIlDLW-WMQOB_A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great team , very professional and communicative through my whole dental experience. I had about two procedures done and they were great and on time both times! The doctor and staff took their time to explain everything from start to finish. I would highly recommend this dental office to family and friends :))))","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
