ges":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tish Pietsch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUCv4NJFxZ3yPR4do7P0mdvIkRQjCKqUK_W9yBvXavU2FVAcVjY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience at Canvas Dental has always been top notch. The staff is amazing, and their attention to detail is beyond stellar. The office is state of the art, and they take great care ensuring you have a relaxing visit. I would highly recommend for all of your dental needs!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brendan McKenna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXMoPNNCwOYoHoG91hFah0hN_9AcVUDYxNfZ7vHZdv-OCEaZx3C=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A refreshingly authentic dental experience! Unlike the corporate run-around, Canvas Dental is a private practice that genuinely cares about your well being and your long term patient loyalty. It's a win-win! I really appreciate the work they do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Shay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLuwpDoq0SCccPneCtzzGt-YSx-lhDKduCMOIM3xHQHgnxHlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’d give 10 stars if I could! Canvas Dental is hands down the best dentist I’ve been to in Austin. They have a wonderful team who all take the time to ensure you’re 100% taken care of. As great as the staff is, the results are even better.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Colton Maynard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVkisJcftvs6mYxoKiWw00Fnyx7D6JbtjiJ-XKDHbT2piZvfUnTRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love going here! Very professional, clean, and the staff is always genuine and happy!\nScheduling and communication couldn't be easier!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Laura Becerra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKnvv59IVrO5UQJGU55s6H5J9gK3zvs0GOy0TO32fsqwCUFlw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to Canvas Dental since moving to the Hill Country. They are the most patient, friendly and knowledgeable dental office I have been to. What impressed me the most is that Dr. Arismendi will go through non invasive lengths to take care of your original teeth and find a solution to save them before a crown is needed.\nHim and his team have taken care of my cleaning, cavities I had and also worked on my beautiful Maryland bridge. If you’re looking for a great all around service dental office I strongly recommend Dr. Arismendi and his team.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0AwIJegua6rs_xSrL4WRO8rgHtB4yicV-Ml6CflddEDQRu2i05E4i5uBHW3HhB5_iq31wWglQcS21vlebhmxkQKhf2Sso9JjyQBq5npZr_QJLqN4KLMZaFsrHQpPNra1bAW0N8Qw=k-no"],"When":"2024-11-10"},{"Name":"Jorge Ochoa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3Qu8WAuIMYqrpmZ9kBuACif2JmLP4QpAdb8IgF1mg169NeHc=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Not only are Dr. Arizmendi and his team proficient   in routine dental patient care,  but outstanding when they fitted me with a crown. Of the three I have been fitted with through the years, theirs is the best fit to my bite by far. They’re also very kind and personable.  I highly recommend Canvas Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maggie Lambeth","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-gVQBTnKeE2h2yWlOWeZqQtYNWYdTKXNdJLv286h2b2J_Y_zm=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Friendly staff and professional care. I have confidence in the quality of work being done.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
