-88j07e2ZhXMqJkWw=w224-h298-k-no-pi-0-ya317.76135-ro-0-fo100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"http://www.steinerdental.com/","source":"steinerdental.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"117408396329788923708","name":"Steiner Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/117408396329788923708"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Steiner Ranch","street":"2900 N Quinlan Park Rd","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78732","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Syri Simpkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDo8-eNqMlrfZGggJ6d3NoKCI8ghzqSEFwoEKHmRmNZYExy66-=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Beautiful office! The assistants Ellysa and Ashley were so comforting and supportive. They work beautifully together with Dr. Byrnes, and the whole office staff is very welcoming and warm. I was just visiting with my boyfriend today and I am a registered dental assistant, and this office goes above and beyond. Charlotte the office manager and has a bubbly personality and makes patients and guests feel comfortable and tends to their needs. Will definitely be coming back and may even become a part of this family. Definitely recommend this dental office!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3n1cINEH_VrKEqjAUj7mSJqtoCLqHkw8bxq4PfyOu6rsifSwA7r0AWi6wJczkvBGZmFFm260KezdUX8krCUQmJXsgsanfiwfDgGSnsx2v1DDl84-t1rHEHequJ4DjcaiBg7z5uz7j_QPNY=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-18"},{"Name":"Bryan T Pitney","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHKpwPwzF2zcl6fls-Se6LV_IvWUBxEuvFMv9KqpBVAOf5CMhHKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Fantastic Dental Office! I recently had an appointment here and was thoroughly impressed from start to finish. The facility is a beautiful, modern space that looks brand new—it’s clean, bright, and immediately puts you at ease.\nThe Clinical Team:\nDr. Thompson: She was incredibly professional and took the time to explain everything clearly. I never felt rushed, and her thorough approach gave me total confidence in my treatment plan.\nDental Hygienist Janis: She was Lovely! She was gentle yet very detailed during the cleaning, and she provided some great tips for my at-home routine that I really appreciated.\nThe Atmosphere:\nBeyond the clinical care, the entire staff was extremely helpful and friendly. From the moment I checked in at the front desk to the moment I left, everyone went out of their way to ensure I had a positive experience. It is clear that patient comfort is a top priority for this team.\nVerdict:\nIf you are looking for a dental home that combines a high-tech environment with a warm, welcoming staff, I highly recommend Dr. Thompson and her team. I’ll definitely be returning!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lance McGilvray","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLoWb4NBbcVNT8m59KGtT5lBmWlRXJbRqi0Jl89ikm-1K-vcA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Rosie and Tatiana were great to work with.  The doctors are fantastic.  The procedures and equipment are state of the art.  Everybody is always super friendly.  They have a lot of services and things they can offer to help improve your dental health but I don't think they are ever pushy or misleading.  I always feel like I understand why something might be helpful and it helps me in planning and making decisions about what we could do and what we really need to be prioritizing.  My wife and I switched after being with our much further away practice for years.  We have had nothing but good experiences and the restoration work we have had done has been excellent.  You could pay a bit more or less other places, but I doubt you would receive better care. You can't grow another set of teeth, so you really want to be confident that you are being taken care of. And they are right in the neighborhood which is incredibly convenient. Thanks for another good visit.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Pragni Dave","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXLaKSzNg9Gi_c-g-d_pKvtqg2qt5Lt7oLK8b0jRUUuTtIuQqbH2A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really like this dentists office! The staff is friendly, the technicians are thorough and work efficiently to minimize discomfort, and the dentists are great. Chelsea has been the technician working on my Invisalign treatments and I really appreciate how organized and quick she is! Everyone is always punctual and I appreciate they are respectful of scheduled times. The staff always greets me with a smile. Glad to have established care with this practice","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miranda McElyea","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4MPXULzcWZbFjkVahqpF0RoX7fWBc4jILK8eQUcdw2AAC7mp5=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a wonderful experience with Dr Byrnes and her amazing staff! From the moment I walked in everyone made me feel comfortable and at ease. Dr Byrnes was kind, professional and truly took the time to listen to my concerns.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jyothi Mail","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZewJRsg77-ycHt1EoagK1D3VA7VlFmHBKuWeZZhDKCQ591g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience today at my dental visit. Chelsea did an excellent job with my filling — she was gentle, professional, and made me feel very comfortable throughout the procedure. My daughter is also doing Invisalign (Envisioned) with them, and we’ve had a wonderful experience so far.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sofia Jankovic","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVU7dknkabjbGk5MURXcMfjnnQwsFZRmzwlAVVYBC1shy4mtUs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The service is absolutely amazing, and all of the workers are incredibly friendly! They really know how to turn a horrible experience into something fun and comfortable. My technician, April, was very kind, welcoming, and professional, she made me feel comfortable the entire time. I couldn’t have asked for a better experience and would highly recommend this place to anyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Arriaga","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVYhYtNC55aRfhPXEbY_rUDfVO4Yx0XAK2MKaFHNeFDdhh5jqw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited Steiner Dental, and I am beyond impressed! From the moment I walked in, the team made me feel welcomed, comfortable, and truly cared for. The office is modern, sparkling clean, and exudes a sense of calm that immediately puts you at ease.\n\nDr. Steiner and the staff are not only highly skilled but also incredibly personable, taking the time to explain every procedure and ensure the best possible results. I had both dental and Botox treatments done, and the results exceeded my expectations — natural, precise, and stunning.\n\nWhether you’re looking for routine dental care or cosmetic enhancements, Steiner Dental is the place to go. Professional, friendly, and top-notch care — I can’t recommend them highly enough!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
