 the dentist in my life but since I’ve started to be a Cutbirth’s customer I am feeling comfortable. The Team is very professional, supportive, and friendly, I am very grateful to be followed from them for my dental care. Last week was my birthday and today I came here for periodic visit and they surprise me with a cake to celebrate me.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ZxcWhT4Q3QgED9pz_-yvlEj1szO_vx3vjsR6gUJ_JgcIhUSS_SQ02hsQZtoNuuAS48Os06AOBFriEl13NLl-OJXhNsQuiMYvE9bSX4ulJmSx8KYamEMnKcvvT5IWeGLyWw738POIvcEAO=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-14"},{"Name":"Linda Niederhofer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVys2P4kubvWVGIx2OKW7rvYLfotX9KxofxmhJS4ybcXqu5VjKd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience. Wonderful atmosphere! Everyone is so friendly!\nCasey the hygienist that x-rayed and cleaned my teeth was so gentle. The receptionist offered us water and Robbie brought us coffee in the lobby! Dr. Han was so personable and even remembered that I was planning for a trip from the last visit we had in September 2025 by asking how is was!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"nguyen nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXoBcCjwqiXlkzHLr2LTRgDy-H9-WWAN93rPcZhXhdLGJpC2kyGUA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a fantastic experience at Cutbirth Family Dental in Elgin, Texas. From the moment I walked in, I felt genuinely comfortable and welcomed. The entire facility is spotless, modern, and beautifully designed. Everything feels cohesive and elegant, which immediately put me at ease.\n\nDr. Han was especially wonderful. He was very friendly, generous with his time, and made sure I understood everything throughout my visit. His calm and personable approach truly made the experience even better.\n\nThis is hands down the best dentistry I have ever been to. The staff was professional, attentive, and kind, and it is clear they care deeply about both quality dental care and the overall patient experience. I highly recommend Cutbirth Family Dental to anyone looking for excellent care in a clean, modern, and relaxing environment.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Ormesher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYPWo_r8F26r8FjGhE5YVfW_R0hp6fECcSjpAN13IwWyemFka3=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cutbirth provides great dental care with personalized service.  They take the time to get to know their clients and make each visit special.  For me, Disney music and movies.  For my husband, an A\u0026M football game.\n\nHighly recommend.  You're not just getting a dentist,  you're making life-long friends.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0PBOgLYf1TdBgk6QZEkXcvH7NZ4NrS2_eoew4NrF1Ie7-WyN-zSvVECSBXfmzKzLWuD-IDRCNb7vX5_mDUpG5BZXQnmEdGgQWDkc-b-Na6jISplXn2RvSxz7vgtuHmjIvNdwrtGM2NuXbe=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-9"},{"Name":"Thia Ruiz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKaW3USdqhj7rzhrwUGwnZA9NUQPJzHz4AptukdIeINEwikKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the moment I walked into the office until the time I left, my experience was amazing! The front office staff was incredibly friendly and funny—and they even took time to notice my Colorado shirt and talk about adventures in Colorado. . The X-ray technician was very kind, talkative, and welcoming. The dental hygienist was outstanding, taking the time to explain everything and making sure I was comfortable throughout the visit.\nDr. Han was extremely kind, funny, and excellent at explaining my X-rays and dental concerns. He truly goes above and beyond to make sure you feel cared for and receive the best possible dental treatment.\nThank you to Cutbirth Family Dental for such an amazing appointment and for providing outstanding service as a whole team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Miriam Trujillo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLBumjTKGqfFogPscH6zFK40gnEL52lJrB3mNhP5E9CgHMODQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow ! Absolutely amazing service from everyone. Highly recommend bring your family. I can't imagine taking our family anywhere else. From the moment you walk in, the atmosphere feels welcoming and calm—never that cold, clinical vibe you get at some places. The front desk team greets you by name, remembers our little quirks, and always makes scheduling painless even with our busy lives.\nOur dentist and the entire staff are exceptional with both adults and children. We actually look forward to our visits because the team is so patient, gentle, and fun—they explain everything in kid-friendly ways, use cool tools to show what they're doing. No tears, no fear—just happy, healthy smiles.\nThe care itself is top-notch. Cleanings are thorough but gentle, and when we needed fillings and a little orthodontic guidance, everything was explained clearly with no pressure. They're conservative in their approach—only recommending what's truly necessary—and they take the time to answer every question without rushing you out the door.\nWe've recommended them to friends and family. If you're looking for a family dentist who truly treats you like family, provides excellent care, and makes dental visits something to look forward to (yes, really!), this is the place. Thank you for taking such great care of our smiles—we're grateful every day!\nHighly recommend to anyone in Austin area searching for a trustworthy, caring, family-focused dental practice! 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria Jordan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7HiQdoocY0oAgJDsYW-JTwXYwsKWySHOxw7vdM6GhlwXb_w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We love going to Cutbirth Family Dental. The facility is beautiful and the front staff is so kind and welcoming. This place is truly family friendly, especially with my 2 yr old whom isn’t too keen on going to the dentist. They worked at her pace and brought out special tools to help her feel involved. The tools were a dentist kit for children and a stuffed frog with teeth. My little one got to play dentist then got her teeth checked out. It was a great visit. Flor our dental hygienist was amazing!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0A2n0Jq9WQfe2sftGno19XO3Ro_9WYF5N0DrJJqz6q1T0j9UIORSkyjaPV2n7P7A2lJNax9Xm-PHVnIQdzR_jNu37UAEjeztkYnkbKqVuutBVae6QHOEaxhvvh1wkL53k9XhV0KTam1Pk=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn26s2HIYLoLBe0_MNEOG7qqvzsef214FsEZlQqLXIarClMtK0UU9l2L_FsR-XZ0O93r4zBsugh3eh0FGWU7FnMSw_euLsqF-HQNBnkFRmrmZ44JFKVrr1FGFfmyMIU2Cv0QJqzXuNYP-kbO=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-15"},{"Name":"Ana Swain","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKVDzWKsXaD9Sk2c-U31FEg1dBFV-mRTT0CKlWFAftIMTi0YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super friendly staff and dentist. Small family owned business that actually took  the time to hear me. My hygienist was amazing.  Took her time and listened to my concerns and followed it with recommendations. The dentist was super nice and friendly. My cleaning was not rushed at all. Extremely recommend this small own local dental company.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
