e me aware of what my teeth needed in order to stay healthy and strong. Staff very friendly and made me feel comfortable. Will be coming back to get more service done!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ranjit Malhi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUE8QNclG__oMe0dio4oq3b4p6MsiIE2FgmO6Wt_Yb8_VYorWzI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Heavenly was incredibly helpful and patient throughout my dentist visit. She made the entire process smooth and enjoyable. Her informative nature and accommodating attitude made me feel at ease. The dentist provided a comprehensive explanation of the procedure and gave me ample time to consider my options. The receptionist Laira and Fatima was helpful too!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jewel Petra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9NWiu5upjLjMrErQADBu6R0rtjzeSvhwy_fuFLluacbiW7TS9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience at this office. Dr. Lee and Heavenly were both very kind and took time to explain all of their processes. I went in for my annual checkup and a cleaning. I was also concerned about a chipped tooth. They took time to explain the best options and went over my insurance coverage so there were no surprises. Overall my visit was very comfortable and the staff are very considerate.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ana Carreon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUZ4TioyOYhZARSi7ZALsRgmcAFDZkX5lQ7U-7Oq50wUru7HU8r=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Lee and Uriel were amazing!! Super fast, efficient and did not rush me when I explained my issues. Very friendly and professional staff. Front desk was able to get me in the same day due to my major pain. Will recommend 100% and will be back to finish up my treatment. Billing was very transparent which is a nice change for a dentistry.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vivek Jadeja","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUTwIRHQYYnK12WTScmnEJwObQx7BKPS2ZE2qjnscUS-2MV3uiW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at this clinic! The assistant, Jasmine, did a great job helping with my cleaning! She was super friendly and answered all of my questions to help me understand my treatment plan. Dr. Alex Lee also did a stellar job with my filling and cleaning!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Larkey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLnfjpr76LOzPaup_6-A2qeU0Vrr3RETOopLyd88pfO_Ah4YQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had an amazing experience. Staff was great and helpful. Heavenly mad the X-rays painless and quick and was so helpful. Dr.Lee answered every question I had and provided me with all the info I needed","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joel Torres","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtceJQioCy3Sq9oKi7LvUQ4bqpIJs0K3zoI4W6-CcS0pL1Ng=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jasmine and Dr. Lee were amazing! Came in for an extraction and were very thorough and welcoming. Made me feel safe and they acted with confidence! Best dental experience ever!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
