recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Neon Luong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIhJVmDwRckiLXRo2K_TeZ1zr26Q-dbEH-spv6p9oDAP1-egw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Much thanks to Dr. Tran who handles the dental cleaning process and Amber to walk me through the cost, scheduling and imaging. First time getting my dental appointment here in Texas so I am glad I picked the right office. The experience was pleasant and I felt welcomed there.\n\nAlready scheduled my next appointment. Wl definitely be back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Larry Frey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSSt9Ym99JgcyHzLPH9YCR2LpvBRqG6F_mqFl6r0Eed0G7oQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This is hands down the best dental office in Texas. Everyone is very friendly and take a genuine interest in your care. They take the time to explain in depth the procedure and show you your options. They are very upfront on pricing which I thought is very reasonable. Dr. Pham took as much time as I needed to understand what was being done and why. The office staff is simply the best as was the nursing staff. They made me feel very comfortable and were not in a hurry. This was a great experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Sotelo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7EANziP7x3YW0b-aVmRiwJt3lwj4sCqOYiFPKpgrRk2aZGQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HQ dental is a great dentist office. The staff are always friendly and professional. They aren't a place that tries to upcharge you and they even will cover certain things insurance says they won't cover. I'd highly recommend going here and have even referred a few family and friends to go here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"whoa","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXSnFBCrIPovjRpCconSXdXvi7Lz0G7T98CmZaAU-YOylXysa12=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They are Outstanding! I walked in and immediately the woman up front was very sweet and answered any questions I had. A very welcoming experience to start and when I got to the back the team took good care of me. Efficient and didn’t miss a beat with any concerns I had. I’m not one who’s excited about the dentist but they sure made it easy for me! Thank you HQ","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joan Worton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXADFZyUOSK6huuDcU_kWjTItN3-xx_JHcR6xzLbEoidaav-4zB=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time there and was really impressed by the quality of their service and professionalism. Needed a new dentist that would except my insurance and they filled the bill. If you need a dentist give them a call.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christina Nunez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIkIDbuf5WE8D_NUMEkOQxQZ1oBqwtMIppnYdNF0GaYJ5f3VA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience for the whole family. Very welcoming and courteous throughout the entire visit. Details of my care and that of my family was explained clearly. I appreciated the images and diagnostics to support any suggestions/plan of care. I highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DuWayne Murdock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMSCbZiDMLuhVK5LqCk7Rc2WKF6xVIWohTAQo9mahgmWi6sAY=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nobody actually likes going to the Dentist so the best a place can do is make the experience as quick and painless as possible. Everything at this office runs smooth and seems organized. Ashley? at the front desk gets you in and out quick, Shyann? who is a assistant/hygenist is very knowledgable and efficient, and Dr Tran did both a deep clean and filling (back to back in two days) and both times it was painless and quick. Also, bonus points for showing up on time and actually having your appointment start when scheduled vs showing up on time and then waiting for 20 minutes like a lot of other places...I literally walked in on time both days and went straight to the chair and they started.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Michaels","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXI8GomAxr6vDiYwU9w3EbW7wFPgCtwLLLKp9zbggNBj6Vny3M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I recently visited HQ Dental for the first time and was thoroughly impressed! The team incredibly friendly, making sure to answer all my questions before and after my checkup. I needed a deep cleaning, and they handled it wonderfully. Doctor is not only kind but also exceptionally skilled, making the whole process comfortable and straightforward. It’s great to see a dental practice that genuinely cares without overcharging. Looking forward to being a long-term patient here!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
