Mb5nJ6mT9CqVCdsMy_wDuzdCnTH6ouiw-ZeG_SYHC7sO-97d1a1i-ct0X19Jr1zoAmIHiwBluPE03EgOvRPA2uqPY62xasMf9syJ_NaQxs_Jl1ZCo4A8=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xYLFSSQx7jHKRFgx-taysjNNA3wdhvY0b0CWqIU8nVaXGhLJQEhfDzL53MD1ZHDJqhwWkdf-7cwV5SjrHEVa8fU0fMqw9YN7QSmI_fWoKRfj4ppM-o3FgPdelyOQ6UluR7qi4m099Io8m=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-21"},{"Name":"Eleonor Nicolls","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKC0aSMHVTTkDg2XByyOj1CcXaXz1S7geeqGSoOsUlTNFxQpA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service. Everyone was very helpful and courteous. My teeth were cleaned really well. Dr. Falke was very helpful in telling me what I needed and suggested a plan to work with my teeth. I would recommend this dental office to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eliabel Munoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_9wWIzZU81mz2nuEm7L2sXz8jjV45XAa92pnVJWkRlAq6Jrin=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went in for a routine cleaning and to address a bone spur that had developed since a recent extraction of a molar. As my dental hygienist, Lilly did an excellent job in a warmly personable and informative way. Dr. Falke came in at the end and after looking at my bone spur quickly and efficiently took care of it. My visit also had a very satisfactory conclusion when the office manager assured me that a billing issue had been corrected and that indicated to me that I had been heard. Overall, this visit reminds me that professional experience and expertise coupled with compassion for those of us who dread dental procedures makes me glad that despite my fears this practice is one I can trust. Thanks Dr. Falke and dedicated staff! You're the best.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joyce Tiner","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlJ_wADNFH3hMuNPhvfITVA4UHW-w1zvUfg3y06jxU65n1rw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had gone to another dentist to have implanted dentures put in. For some reason the bottom denture would not stay in my mouth!! Dr. Mark was able to find out what the issue was! He now has a plan to fix this awful problem!! I’m looking forward to having functional teeth!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Beverly Pence","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUa99HjQzHsWJIIC8F9tJmc7S0v8fNitOkjzJGCuvBNMIZs1zZBIw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"When Dr. Falke said they call him Dr. Numb, he wasn't fibbing. First time ever in all my years, I  couldn't feel any discomfort/pain when he pulled a tooth. His staff are awesome and friendly. Thank you also much for making my day painless.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerrys Garage","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrpaih-wdL7YM6VOUOjXUcrX6kHdfLwvWD9huyMjCy_VOnfkKKgA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dont like Dentist and dread going, but I found a Dentist I like now and know I definitely will be going back as it was a positive experience. Also, thanks to Bregan as she was so patient with me.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Reynolds","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUjs3Z7now62SqafMUO9i0VAhOv-88tLSjLG3a3U6wscQZglXrE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every one at this dentist office were friend and nice and they came up with a plan to fit my budget too get my teeth fix and I recommend them to everyone thank you so much. Michael","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Connie Schramm","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLQZzVGslz68mk59HMBNu58DpAZwJuA-Gm4KTxnbfJYcnrrWA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Franklin had his old bridge fall out and we went to Dr. Falke and he worked me in to put my bridge back so I am able to eat.  Dr. Falke is always so very good and caring.  He's been so very good to us for many years.  Thank You very much Dr. Falke and all your wonderful workers for your loving care for us.  Franklin and Connie Schramm","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
