ews":[{"Name":"erin barrera","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWIpNTn39KyhmNfKMAAv-2hT_c3xyV-fhsa5Y7FlRQOz74eLkp16g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This was my first time here as a new patient and was very impressed with the cleaning I recieved! It was a 2 hr long appointment (way longer than expected) but well worth it and well needed. Found out that my last dentist was not doing a good job at all. The hygienist and even the dentist was very thorough, explained everything, pointed out a few things that the other dentist never addressed, and did not rush through anything.\n\nWill definitely be back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer Matura","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJRir7w1b8HAlKbmmaBssrbVB5w49O2W9GsR7FrvtoTyVIAug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everybody hates going to dentists. However, if they went to The Dentists in bastrop they'd have a different opinion! My visit was great! Elizabeth is very knowledgeable and sweet. She explained everything well as she did it. I'd ask for her everytime if possible! Dr. Smith was very knowledgeable as well. She was very nice and very accommodating. I will not dread going to the dentist anymore as long as this is my dental team!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nikita Tristan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXT6IFysNHTiGSdwGihpgOCgrSrLnidgeggoQL4P2I3YsoCqR8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My family and I have been going to The Dentists for the better part of a decade. We recently brought in our 3 year old for his first check up and Melanie was the most incredibly patient person with him. She got him to trust her and made him apart of the experience so that there was no fear involved. He left asking to go back so she could “brush his teeth” the next day. Thank you so much, Ms. Melanie!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Steven Long","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX2IE4RM6ViG0YyDngW4n2LX3maTjdqZZPyLlBv-Qg7EcjQHyY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience. The hygienist was very thorough, gentle, and made me feel comfortable the whole time. Dr. Koppuzha took time to explain everything and didn’t rush the visit. You can tell they both truly care about their patients. Highly recommend if you’re looking for a great dentist in Bastrop.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debra Dubec","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVvPTx4qa-xykKZiw89scKVVhuNcd3QAs8EhLlD3xSQiUCDq64=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent service , when you walk in the door you have extremely welcoming receptions, when you go back to see the doctor  you are greeted with friendly and well informing assistant , attends to your needs, and helps with any and all questions that you have. Meeting the doctor was a great experience he's well attending very informing very understanding he let you know that you're in control and he relieved a lot of anxiety I had. This will be my dentist for the rest of my life.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"The Young-Chacon's","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhVRjatyxmSJCYtiwlDthw3yFhEbMoxkYjaS0KHMMe_d6UoA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"🫶🏽 I had such a wonderful experience at The Dentist. First time there. The waiting area is super cute and the seating is very comfy!! From the moment I walked in, I felt completely at ease. They didn’t try to scold us for not filling out the paperwork in advance (no forms populated on our end). The team was warm and genuinely human—if that makes sense—treating me like a person (family really), not just a number. I laughed more than expected. At the same time, everything about their care was highly professional, thorough, and reassuring. They have great technology (X-rays, 3D images, etc!!! It’s rare to find a place that strikes that perfect balance between compassion and professionalism, but they do it effortlessly. I received a treatment list and my insurance approved prices before I even checked out. I’m so glad I found them and would recommend them to anyone new to Bastrop looking for dental care that truly goes above and beyond. As people of color, my fiancé and I felt perfectly comfortable and welcomed! Love, love, love this place. I would say “can’t wait to go back” but that would mean they’re doing an unnecessary root canal. 😆🤍🦷🪥","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"James Shelton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgKSxJqDrDKxRA2UCxmUy0gAr5zX97SJanBV88CbZf-nA55A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have never had such A great experience at the dentist.  It’s not somewhere people enjoy going at all. It’s usually Dreaded and understandably why.\nThis dental office is very nice and clean and everyone is so friendly and helpful.\n\nDr. Koppuzha Gave me a root canal today and It was less painful than a filling that I’ve gotten in the past at a different office.\nHonestly, there was no pain at all.  I’ve never received a shot that didn’t hurt at least a little bit until now and I’ve never had a dental Procedure that was so smooth and painless .  This is my first time at this office and I’ll never go anywhere else!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kassie Prew","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLY5vat39eH4GrTUjlFakGGsdqO6LLB5HDSpie2ezAkAR0ZMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"10/10 recommend! My hygienist was AMAZING. The entire practice is professional, thorough, and friendly. The office itself is really nice and clean. Loved it!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
