"Rating":5,"Description":"I loved my first visit. My Doctor took the time to show me each of her recommendations with X-rays and pictures. She answered all my questions and gave me clarity - I hadn’t had that in a dentist before. She never tried to oversell, but showed me what we should tackle first. It was a great visit!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Patrick Tokarski","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8Dl_Al4uYBmWwm_t6kKwm-Tw40tWEZVPxHhg_3wAZx8NGKFE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great folks here, efficient and kind. No upselling (you know who you are, upselling dentists) and interested in getting a wholistic picture of your dental health so they can help you work toward achievable goals. Might be a personal preference but having Great British Bake Off on while in the chair is a GREAT distraction!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Veronica Valle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKyxAm8mTgi2vvWaua8snP7f95bjeLuLD47L6aheUxKPf5_Rw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient of Dr. Hsu at Red Bud Dental for a couple of years. Dr. Hsu is professional and caring. He remembers me every time I have an appointment and asks about my well being. He takes the time to explain procedures and answers questions diligently. I feel at ease during my appointments and do not feel pressured to do unnecessary procedures.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"sandra hughes","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvZ3RIJPjU5t6VVLlRYpI_cBlcqWAMkEl25DssdZR53bHF8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have a lot of anxiety when it comes to sitting in a dental chair, but this office truly goes above and beyond to make you feel comfortable. They take their time, explain everything clearly, and always check in before moving on to the next step, which made a huge difference for me. The staff is incredibly friendly, patient, and understanding from the moment you walk in. I’m so grateful for the care they provide and highly recommend them to anyone who struggles with dental anxiety or just wants a team that truly cares.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chris Kay","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI_UfVb3dwjW_jDp-4RVmi4h5eVsuFrhxXzcjFsx9UfSsIJfg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Sharaf and his assistant, Susan, took excellent and professional care of me when I had an unexpected infection in a tooth occuring over a holiday. They both came in on a Sunday just to make sure I had the treatment I needed to get well. I appreciate their compassion and gift of time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Araiza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIQhVz9hGQ6G8VPv_GnZ_iPfYT5hjg9R7u3k0hrjgjlIzUpOQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Best clinic ever! Every one was so nice they walked me trough everything! And they were very patient! Doctor was super nice and kept me comfortable at all times ! Everything was super fast ! Im very thankful i em pain free !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Killy Scheer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUVfdm1uh_fWvKNsXNXuw-DuuM2g_C_wDDa91FFZxGmKim80E2Z2w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed an emergency wisdom tooth extraction over the holiday week — not great timing for many reasons, one of which was that it fell during a lapse in dental insurance. After reading glowing reviews about Dr. Sharaf’s skill, manner and level of service, I sent him an email on a Sunday. He responded immediately and got me into his office on Monday for surgery. The extraction I had been anxious about and putting off (for years!) was handled with ease, care and tremendous (uncanny, really) generosity. Post-op, I’m in minimal pain with next to no swelling. Dr. Sharaf and his team will be my go-to for all dental needs going forward.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Matt Maples","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXlwNNBdaiTAmihdFGAe3iYx33yWM8W2oH9iyy6ydVttqZM0vILgw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They do a nice job here and they get you in quickly. On behalf of the Round Rock Chamber Ambassadors I want to thank Red Bud Dental for being a valuable member of our community! 👏🏻 🦷 🪥","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
