 accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"jasmine king","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUIMuDQbDrNOC9rtGNw8PBYjZJJpH9vOHVvPhwqtINEWswd2eou=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such an amazing experience at this dental office! From the moment I walked in, the front desk staff was welcoming, professional, and kind. The office was clean, organized, and had such a calming atmosphere.\n\nThe dentist was incredibly knowledgeable, gentle, and took the time to explain everything clearly so I felt comfortable and informed. I never felt rushed, and they truly cared about my comfort throughout the entire visit.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dentist who is skilled, trustworthy, and genuinely cares about their patients, I highly recommend this office. I’m so glad I found them and will definitely be returning!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"A N","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW9idQM-0fAEXF9_obAFHg0wD7861AaS8uj-Xm-Sek8Y4G_l65w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I highly recommend Serenity Dental in Round rock!\nI’ve been in Invisalign treatment for about 4 months and have had a wonderful experience from start to finish. I’m already noticing a difference in my smile, which makes me even more excited for my final results.\n\nDr. Hersheal has been excellent throughout the process—very knowledgeable, professional, and attentive. Brooke, the dental assistant, is absolutely amazing and truly goes above and beyond. She makes every visit comfortable and always has a positive attitude that makes you feel at ease. The front desk staff is also fantastic and very helpful when explaining financial plans and answering any questions. Overall, a 5-star experience!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerry Lopez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKACJoM-vh5LJEBbzImuPM2q77GmtdU9zm2JJe0Q48Br7YkjA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I tend to feel nervous about visiting the dentist, but the entire team at Serenity Dental Studio was exceptionally kind and welcoming. Brooke, the dental assistant, was very informative throughout my visit and made sure I understood each step of the process. Dr. Hersheal also did an excellent job explaining the process for my brand new smile, which gave me even more confidence. The staff overall helped me feel comfortable and at ease during my appointment. Brittney also did a great job getting me scheduled for my next visit. Thank you to the Serenity Dental Studio team for such a positive experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cindy Keever","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLx-0RenL2ZzpiGeviXCPovCKvYAjyUXwFu0LLbOD0qV6uF-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Super impressed. I absolutely hate dental visits however after my 1st visit I will be bringing the entire family to Serenity Dental Studio moving forward. All the front staff was super sweet and inviting. Brooke was awesome especially for anyone with dental anxiety. Dr Hersheal was equally great, He explained everything thoroughly and took his time. Office was clean and appointment was made in a timely manner. Highly recommend Dr. Hersheal and his team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yash","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTuC5fVBpWVF_HSVzG1-t6CxXp6Q_0K4vlRxuNn6mOsrRTGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a great experience at Serenity Dental Studio. The front desk team was welcoming, the office was spotless and calming, and the visit was very organized from start to finish. Dr. Hersheal Aggarwal explained everything clearly, answered my questions, and made sure I was comfortable the whole time.\n\nI really appreciated the transparency around the treatment plan and costs. Highly recommend if you’re looking for a friendly, professional dentist in Round Rock.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucas Huffman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiRyRFF-pDM5qbzzuB6k-LZq1Y-anCj9yNNIN26JaJ24xGR7U=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Hersheal Aggarwal very clearly cares about his practice and his patients. The facility was immaculate and offered amenities like a Keurig, a refrigerator with refreshments, and snacks (ironic for a dentists office). When I arrived I was promptly checked in and taken to the room shortly after. Everyone was warm and friendly, from the front desk all the way to Dr. Hersheal himself. He very clearly explained everything that was going on and concisely laid out next steps and best practices moving forward. This was the best dentist visit I have experienced and will 100% be coming to him for many years.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shanthi Desilva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUxVvzia5ZS3_1HFFcRjV26rGfWZi_k_mIoBMGggQqr3Ml39V0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My first experience at Serenity dental studio  was nothing but amazing.  I  was excited to enter a serene environment with staff so welcoming..   Dr Hersheal so kind , compassionate and attentive, definitely relieved my anxiety despite of  having  years of suffering with my dental issues. I highly recommend   Him to anybody looking  for a professional dentist in Round rock area.. Thank you  for your dedicated service..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Meredith Makela","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIKjdE8t2H6CInxSAd6kBMpAo6MxjBPshLiQvqT8rMk7YEht2Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"After not going to the dentist for years, I was hesitant to go anywhere. I chose Serenity Dental Studio because they were open on Saturday. From the time I walked in to the time I left I felt comfortable. Everything was explained in detail, everyone was super nice and the way they show you what’s going on instead of just telling you is next level. I’m really glad I chose to come to Serenity and for once in my life, I can say I’m excited for my dental journey.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
