ffice is clean and updated as well. Dr. Mendez and the entire staff were AMAZING!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"M B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKr6_nzPDPQj3CaC0eWFxj7g9A4FK-jnNOoNmLow7yYzGO29g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff and doctor are AMAZING! I bring my whole family here and we always have a great visit. The staff remember whats going on with my kids and I feel like more than just a patient. I will never go anywhere else.\n\n10/10 Recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"wynnie denny","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfGYJPUZMa3U7u3WKH-DrA_FxFdcYDiDLdKnHX2yXYyfQbYbKhug=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":3,"Description":"I had to get 3 cavities, a crown, and a cleaning. Lots of work and a variety.\n\nThe communication from the doctors and hygienists was abysmal. They did not tell me what to expect during any of the work. No instructions on caring for a temporary crown. No communication about the process, the actual work it entails, or about follow up. Chat gpt had to answer all my questions.\n\nI'm editing my review because after the work was done my bite changed slightly and was causing discomfort,  even after I left a 1 star review they were professional and honored their warranty,  and allowed me to go to their Georgetown location which was a better fit for me. I paid zero dollars for the hour long appointment which was very thorough.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Corbin Family","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLVbP3RAMANJJXT8MJ5Yw5GzDJC7garTtjPLs8v0vwMY7vwfA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was a pleasant experience then I had my check up. All employees are friendly and professional. Randy did well cleaning my teeth, I scheduled again with him. Great job and keep it up","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zoe Guerin :p","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVMNRO_FqXk0A-30mhOdTni10LZDgvRx7tGz2