26pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":[{"link":"https://mapledentaltx.com/appointments/","source":"mapledentaltx.com"},{"link":"https://booking.one.getdeardoc.com/?location_id=a0305ca9-64b9-4a7d-882b-d8a2038d4d47","source":"getdeardoc.com"}],"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"104901122245463772905","name":"Maple Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104901122245463772905"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"275 SE Inner Loop Suite 105","city":"Georgetown","postal_code":"78626","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jeanie Whatley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWD8gfj1iGx7DAXHQutO3LY56WKbTDlSxsz9SrJGWfTJuq3L9Xy=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've never been to a dentist office like this in my four decades thus far. Sure, the interior looks standard, but that's not why it's so different, so special even.\nLiving in Georgetown, I was so excited to have a non franchise practice so close to where I live. I literally watched the practice get built and officially open their doors. I walked in, and they did not disappoint.\n\nThis perfectly sized healing hub is run by TWO of the most absolutely incredible women I will ever meet. They set a high bar with genuine warmth, kindness, compassion, knowledge, confidence, patience, competency, efficiency. Their communication to the patients,  and just as important, to each other. They're thoughtful, your level of comfort is always monitored, your understanding of what's going on, and answering your questions with honesty and with clarity without that feeling other dentists give of rushing and not listening.\nThey are both extremely thorough and helpful.\nThese two women are inspiring to watch. The teamwork is unmatched and builds patient confidence.\n\nCome on over and see what two women can do that MANY fully staffed big clinics can't and couldn't do. Its beautiful really.\nThey are in constant communication with one another. On the same team. Helping each other. Respectfully speaking to one another. Like two seasoned bartenders during St. Patrick's Day where no one is Irish. Irish can hold their liquor 😉\n\nFrom front desk responsibilities to physician assistance to patient associate to xray tech, to hygienist, and never shows that she doesn't actually love doing it.\nTHAT'S a real gift, a welcomed change of pace, and something I do not take for granted. Plus, it's fun to see and hear in action. Well oiled machine 🤘\nThe doctor is in a class of her own. So sharp, kind, humble, astute, shows genuine care and concern for your well-being beyond your dental health. Makes sure your comfort is maintained throughout. She does the most loving extras steps just to make you feel better.\nShe's extremely knowledgeable, skilled, confident, thorough, attentive, and patient.\nShe's a dreamboat. They both are.\nOR, the Dental Goddess Dentya or the Dental Goddess Peridontia 😉😁\n\nThey both go out of their way to be of any help possible in every area possible. And never, ever, make you feel like a burden.\n\nI find them both inspiring as individuals, darn proud and grateful to be under their care. Welcome to Georgetown. I'm glad you're here 🫶\n\nBook 'em now. Thank me later.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ozair Tariq","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXuqvkS-_BzZB-TxvU9N90u3vmK53U4hsA9oUED88xd_d0FQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff at Maple Dental are amazing and very accommodating. I had 3 cavities removed today and it was chilly in the office for my liking. So they even brought be a blanket to wear during the procedure. No other place is like this place. 5 stars all the way.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Lynn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUQRSlVjla2Mov2bqg4llkLGNjw7h33Rt9wvYAKOYDydhqHD-WzRQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I went to Dr. Kumar for a cleaning and whitening before my wedding, and I couldn’t be happier with the experience. She and her assistant, Stephanie, are both so friendly, knowledgeable, and genuinely caring. They take the time to listen, explain everything clearly, and make sure you’re comfortable every step of the way.\nAfter working in the dental field for 12 years, I know a great dentist when I see one, and I’m thrilled to have found my new dental home here. Dr. Kumar not only got me wedding-ready in a short time, but also helped create a plan for achieving the smile I’ve always wanted. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Daisy De La Cruz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXXiq9UiMM1ILyMS8nvmnMQ9PSErOpcx2VqpxNjDvF2ZSsjsY3Awg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you haven’t been to a dentist in a while, this is the place you want to be! The staff is just so wonderful and Dr. Kumar is thorough, patient and non judgmental. Looking forward to my next cleaning! (Who says that) lol","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"D Mugica","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIH3zQTIrRIS-jYEaA4ohTi24PbQNYUzwX0aiBob7OffdIWGQ0=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"​\"Maple Dental is hands-down the best experience I’ve had. After visiting three different dentists in the last six months, I only wish I had come here first. The entire team attended to me from start to finish, and their prices are very reasonable. The office is incredibly clean, and the staff is both knowledgeable and friendly. Most importantly, they made sure I was comfortable throughout the entire visit. The doctor clearly knows exactly what she is doing. I’ve already recommended them to my parents—thank you, Maple Dental, for the awesome service!\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samuel Brannon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXTJ2KWFqJ1QQ9MwjEt1-ANB56KxCANpBhm0tJvfcEBv2ZmJYkURw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The dentist who operates this office is top notch. At first I was reluctant because during a checkup she identified more issues than I thought I could possibly have. So I went to get a second opinion. But she was right on and her prices were much lower than the local competition.\n\nThe Doctor is fast and thorough. She is professional and believes in gentle dentistry. The ambient music, the cool air, and good anesthesia made my visit go so smoothly! And I had a lot of work to do.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"tia beam","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIArcc2RGpV6rX7h98tMKxYI0kx4WJAgOJpYK5eBN0R-y1JhQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From the start the Kelsey at the front desk offered amazing customer service. She was friendly, knowledgeable and efficient. The assistant who took x-rays was thorough and very personable. Dr. Kumar was amazing with being detailed in explaining what the process was for a new patient exam, did a thorough exam and cleaning SAME DAY. no sales pitch, no up selling and by far the most professional, positive experience I’ve had in Georgetown. I highly recommend to everyone this is the place to go. Her team was amazing!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Stern","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX91gjiay1dlIxPzQFJg5pHTMfaIe1z5nwaRwjSiBneOpu0r8hF=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Kumar ans Stephanie are great. They are kind and patient. They have done a great job on my teeth. I also bring my toddler here too and they take time to help her feel comfortable.  Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
