d super friendly. The atmosphere is really nice and they strive to make sure you’re comfortable. 10/10 would definitely recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brianna Wapples","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU6y-gZBNpLINXXn5-yLclpJx5CkyHTgucCgtRtT7ea_FK7CbMG=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient at dental domain for several years, they are professional, respond quickly and are very accommodating, Dr white managed my Invisalign treatment as well as a performed a gingivectomy and composite veneer to perfect my smile and now does she does my maintenance dental work. Very happy with treatment here !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gilbert Avila","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUMPnjHoZgLOsf-IVHg4MPVfHzoGS3MM8-pkNdDwHUZoF0Or7dP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience and very professional.  Dr. White was very informative and staff was exceptional.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Mhwfv8DZ-wPPWeL-xifgct13cA3ytq94cfZiQNY3ZaNJZnyUUM2CwYA1HecW4niA6o7bAGkpI7zDYlFIUi3_Xg_8HBnCU4VQITt2PP1zmE0WRqKdCVlrhHt9HpDx-kJNvMaz80D9gLWhE=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0W_xzzTJz1pF1c9qRdBjNXcTwIdmbHPSX8eYwqg1IvmEnAy80Rx-_0oM12kTcRG5kf1LgRDTfANM8x3lvs7YWztEbpA8G3YtUylhvYyKyYZrp2IPKUfxgyed56aDsDeexWbbEWzwYbDpAW=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-27"},{"Name":"Adrian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeo0GMFhTI7ubFxtQRqJlw3fvTFZEgue0o1QUKtHStWyH3270O3w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Quick and friendly service! I like the rooms and all the options they provide while the work is done including TV, headphones, and or weighed blanket! I think I even saw a poster of having a dog come on Wednesday to help patients calm down.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaytlin McCaffrey","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUX6wKQsC_cXYrDkcCFic0LXPpWHqrEKqwcugopG-wC8xJZhIE=s120-