ll taken care of through out my visit. They were able to get me on a solid plan to keep my teeth cavity free.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Val A","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJS5jH3TT-UV7z0G6Ls-8bEjkU_rMnM8-YKlGxnO93xwOqe3Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been a patient at Greenbelt Dental for about 20 yrs. The standard of care is excellent+. I've never been disappointed; the entire staff always goes above and beyond, to not only treat you for the current visit, but also to advise you on steps to take to maintain your dental health for the long term. I feel welcome, well-cared for, and appreciated as a patient here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lauren Levi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ7KiuhMBhmucDsRk8T0Q6_rBTg9T4Gr0Qj8fv5bYcCDo1kPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Genuinely kind and knowledgeable dentist and staff. My old “regular” dentist didn’t know enough to protect himself or me when removing amalgams and I ended up in the hospital with liver damage. Don’t take that risk. Dr. Naranjo, as a biologic dentist, has the training and knowledge to keep you safe and take great care of your teeth. He goes the extra mile. Lucky to have found him.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Trish McAllister","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKJgvkyyA_im7En8ylTFvQqQGpWraJMoAjdRX6hgqNuswJPaA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone at Greenbelt Dental Is exceptional. Cynthia always takes such great care to make sure I don’t feel pain, Dr. Naranjo is so talented and calm, and the administrative team are incredibly kind and caring. They are fabulous!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charlotte Keith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3h0uG2nS84fEWGMFtP0jeo2pXwTn80t-23Bm4P3EAW1Y1PPvu=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Naranjo caught critical issues with my teeth that my prior dentist didn’t mention, so things kept getting worse. I’m grateful someone referred me to Dr. Naranjo just in the nick of time. He's done great work giving me crowns and is very patient and creates a relaxing environment. I've always had painless experiences with him too. I'll definitely use them for cleaning my teeth with dental hygienist Cindy too, who's very skilled, sweet, knowledgeable and fun; my teeth have never felt so smooth! Also the staff are very friendly and it's always a pleasure going there, because I know I'll be taken care of in every department. I highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carlyle Scott","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ_scjO6da0GeFjLzAK7LjfSitgqklyTOLWDCXwmsvnqU54Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Highly recc Dr. Naranjo and the team at Greenbelt! Have seen them for a range of services from semi-annual cleanings to fillings and everything is always seamless and without any issues. The whole team is professional and great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Caroline","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkX-LVh6-ktrYVSNalQciJ7Aweo7yaGzo8Pue1xweLDQjlvFYn=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Every single person in this dental office is so kind and patient.   I completely trust Dr. Naranjo with my dental health.  I look forward to having  a longstanding relationship with Greenbelt Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carolyn Doolittle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJvMP_iYeH_gBJ57TycmfSlfnKjEyecPr9LkHriVskWR0k8wgvL=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going to Greenbelt Dental Health for many years and appreciate that they offer holistic dental care.  I have always received excellent care and very short wait times.  The office staff is always friendly and welcoming and the office is clean and modern.  Dr. Naranjo is friendly, knowledgeable, and makes sure procedures are understood before proceeding.  My Dental Hygienist, Cynthia, always makes me feel comfortable and takes extra care with my sensitive teeth.  I highly recommend this practice.  They truly care about their patients.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
