:"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"James Hedge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJhLmyCEq6HoTKg0QH6FYY07PZOI2SCl3SM8_CMLb3nEqwtvw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was scheduled for a \"deep cleaning\" and having four composite fillings.  Never in my 87 years have I been more satisfied with the work of the hygienist.  She is friendly, easy to talk to, and does a superb job.  Additionally, I found the work of the dentist and her assistant to be outstanding.  I can now see and understand why my wife recommended we switch to this dental faccility.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jonathan Loesch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV_U0IxJwi0bgTCfHvC8c3yXw-CIDP5LRh3GBaWJv0rdv_MNUnb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went for deep (root planing) cleaning today and the experience was amazing! Tiphaney explained the procedure so well, was very pleasant, professional, thorough, and encouraging! The dentists, and entire staff, are top notch!\nHighly recommend!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Linda","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVZwxKsrFvCmiuekkENyI-iwLmIIIybsO3HTZb5lm6XU1HFbzy_UQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful teeth cleaning experience.  A great dental hygienist who really thought with me about teeth sensitivity and helped me forge a plan to reduce the likelihood of my teeth becoming more sensitive (they are ok now, but I want to make sure they remain that way).  A great experience and I am down to see her again in 6 months.  All good.  A great place to go!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kristi vaughn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWC1wxkMs0Q25q4On1cQdf967IIe4UP-gkeAwWckJqwaKrni7k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been needing extensive dental work done for quite some time and just continued to put it off until the day came that I couldn’t any longer. My daughter referred me to Smile Hause Dental in Georgetown, Tx several months ago and it is the best thing that could have happened to me. Everyone there is very kind and gracious. They are more than accommodating and willing to go the extra mile to make sure you are happy and well taken care of.  I will be a patient of Dr. “C’s” as long as she will have me.\nI would recommend this dental practice to anyone 110%!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Darla Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZtN1cFZCrUME1waz84KvLiA8Up5J5rppQMbQ-dp8vbAqrbA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I 100% recommend this office for your dental needs. The office is very clean, the girls at the front desk are very friendly and efficient. The dental hygienist that cleans my teeth is very thorough and explains what and why she is doing certain things.  I feel very comfortable going to this office and feel like they are honest and caring.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ivan Mazoch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKi_k2cPorc5PeZTviaehxR_maPp9GjNaR3SEBDT471-CrYsA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Smile Haus Georgetown was an awesome experience and strongly recommended to use.  Moved to Georgetown 5 years ago and never established a dentist locally.  My filling fell out about a week ago and was still lodged halfway out the tooth.  Made a call to Smile Hause Georgetown after being strongly recommended by my daughter and could not ask for a better dentist office from the admin staff, nurses, and Dentists the experience was outstanding.  Dr. Chenausky diagnosed my issue placed a temporary filling and scheduled the procedure two later to fill the tooth permanently.  She was fantastic and I strongly recommend her.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Chuck Chovan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLSI9N2E7ASC25aUhDHu2J9cZynEzcoRWklFXV2FE3ChOfh6g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"At first, I was a little concerned with the transition from Horizon Dental to Smile Haus. I really liked my former dentist, but I am pleased with Dr. Johnson. He is very personable and professional. Tiffany has been my dental hygienist for several years. She is always pleasant and very thorough in examining and cleaning my teeth. She lets me know if there are any things that may need addressed and she takes the time to answer any questions that I may have. The front desk staff is also pleasant and welcoming.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Quynh Nguyen","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ29fXfNBQM_qiqUHQyq0pgbNz2emcCAedql7mDGS6NJoBhtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I moved to Georgetown about 2 years ago and found this place. They have been amazing, staff was helpful, friendly and always do a great job in cleaning. The office always make sure that you're ready for your appointment, so they would call you if needed to ensure your info like insurance, details are up to date before the appointment.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
