amily, I call family because does how you feel as family.❤️ Everyone there are so sweet and kind.Laura  millions of thanks for taking good care of my mother.🙏 Dr Samani is the best if you ever need to do trasplans please go to Cloud Drntal they take great care of you. You come out of there with a lot of love towards them. I would give them thousands of stars millions but  here is only five. May God bless all this team they are the best.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1dyZelaXWYrGrWq2bvNRYcg7WRwZDUYnVlL7pPOlQJVjR6qdDiBZHgfhvhQI7m6hjWEL9-CvUuF0TeyWVUH8WfSpvOIjoH0N800i6peGI4lq3E-Q3rgc3fmcq0vnxKp-ugAdb3=k-no"],"When":"2023-7-28"},{"Name":"Haitham Faroun","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKLbmvmz157WXrybD_WUJqa2v9GyXklcRVimtd_VCPO_tzx1w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly \u0026 warm atmosphere, Dr Samani showed an outstanding knowledge and professionalism regarding my wife’s case, explained in detail the whole procedure.\nThe staff from reception to assistants were very pleasant and professional. Thank you Cloud Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"christina luong","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIA5848x6wGkemTTDUvB68ECBMNYl5BV9BKI7lGGsFrqNINKw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Cloud Dental exponentially surpassed my expectations. The team went above and beyond making me feel welcome and at ease during my appointment. Dr.Hamza was super informative and super efficient in his service. What a talent. We had 4 crowns placed and 2 fills completed. I have full confidence in him and his staff even after just one appointment. I experienced absolutely no pain or discomfort. The various equipment utilized in office was most updated technology I have seen any dentist I have encountered.  I left after my appointment so satisfied and hope everyone gives them a try to experience the amazing encounter I had.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Orlando Villarrea