s well! It’s like I step into a ski slope vacation (with a dental appointment 🤣) every time! Great atmosphere, great staff and amazing service!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn25INVAqZGeedElxnNevs6Ogen_s0c7X8sIyTtPfD6A3mspBeHY-PSc8MgX72lCG36J1a2pxPaspqzQARmn6A304PsMI9DK8K1HjGSnoZePprTUKRZzikJXBlFO2WCjijnN6xK1F2NmhCY=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-9"},{"Name":"Beyond HVAC","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXhZWMo7mT7tmx0hnhVFw-PGGGO1zbLJPgJasL6TQlvO6AfMjd0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very friendly, professional, and quick service. No waiting at this office. My appointment was at 7 am and by 7:05 I was being seen. Very thorough examination. Gave me everything I needed and nothing that I didnt.  I chose RR dentistry based on the reviews and they did not disappoint. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a good dentist office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheyenne Deverna","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIwTDWQ0yDdXtptWsTBWdioBnpEhX7HFCXFZJTA5QCz5QupvA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such a great experience with Dr. Roach and his team! Dr. Roach was very informative and did a thorough check to address the tooth pain I was having. His dental assistant was friendly and made me feel completely comfortable throughout the visit. The entire front staff was so welcoming—they introduced themselves, greeted me with a handshake, and created such a positive first impression.\n\nI usually have anxiety about going to the dentist, but they truly made me feel at home. They explained everything before doing any procedure, which helped ease my nerves. Dr. Roach also provided a clear plan of action moving forward. My family and I will definitely be switching over to his practice and making this our regular dental office. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dawn Cramer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVA-6WIibsqPjFQDCOQt7