tal experience I have ever had. I live about 40 minutes away and I will drive this way forever if that means I get better care! They are so thoughtful and put your comfort first. They are great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kathryn Hanson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXEPv0gK4IYYTrgPEBXdpps0sLpVWsZVUj7Xq1Ag6P5o7z1Ojf9Bg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great time at the dentist today, which hasn't ever happened before. It was my first time and I was very pleased with everyone and the facility! Thanks everyone for making a chore into a nice experience! I am glad I chose 4405 Dental. :)","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
