le parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jamil Sabbagh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXykwNqug3Uh0oJNtMPbO63M_zB4e2PQ7fv-YNyv_U9_x6uWKv7=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience today thanks to Jerry, the dental hygienist. She was incredibly kind, personable, and easy to talk to, which made the whole appointment feel relaxed instead of rushed or uncomfortable.\n\nWhat really stood out was how clearly she explained things—especially flossing. She took the time to show me how I could do better and why it mattered, without ever making me feel judged. It felt educational and supportive, not preachy. Her warmth and conversation made the cleaning fly by, and it was obvious she genuinely cares about her patients.\n\nAs always, Dr. Stone was also fantastic—professional, thorough, and approachable. Though I didn’t see him this time, he still said “Hi” as he saw me just to check in and ask how I was doing. This extra effort made the overall experience feel thoughtful and well-run. You can tell there’s a great team culture here.\n\nHighly recommend this office if you’re looking for care that’s both high-quality and genuinely human.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Raj Khhatri","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLqCMojxCxH7_Zf2t2iWLwOtYEEj4fh-MmBR1QfXdiPoPp8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a really great experience at Swiis Dental. From the moment I walked in, the staff was welcoming and professional, which instantly made me feel comfortable.\n\nA special shoutout to Jerry, who did my tooth cleaning—she was incredibly kind, gentle, and made sure I was comfortable the entire time. She took great care of me and explained everything clearly, which I really appreciated.\n\nOverall, my experience was very positive, from the front desk to the dental care itself. The staff was friendly, attentive, and made the visit stress-free. I would definitely recommend Swish Dental to anyone looking for quality dental care with a caring team!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DR. JONA LEICHER","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVrWMes7ghyJxkk1tBpQtQwov7asOYJik1umWfyrHNKWVPOcpyP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As a fellow healthcare provider who deeply values compassion and empathy in patient care, I rarely—if ever—leave reviews for healthcare providers. In my experience, it truly takes one to know one, and I have yet to encounter a provider who cares for me with the same level of genuine dedication and heart that I strive to give my own patients. That changed when I met Dr. Stone.\n\nAfter relocating to Houston—a full      3-hour drive each way from his practice—I made the deliberate choice to remain under his care. The 6-hour round trip for a single appointment is, without question, worth every minute. Dr. Stone’s profound compassion, attentive listening, and unwavering commitment to his patients’ well-being stand out in a way that is rare and deeply meaningful in our field.\n\nFor the first time in my career, I feel compelled to write a review because Dr. Stone has earned it. He treats every patient with the kind of empathy and respect that I aspire to every day in my own practice. I have absolutely no intention of ever changing dentists.\n\nThank you, Dr. Stone, for your exceptional care of my dental health and for ensuring that I maintain a confident, healthy smile that genuinely reflects my inner self. Thank you for being the kind of provider who truly makes a difference. Thank you, thank you, thank you!🙏🏼","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn11cdqT9c7lcdDUfHyPdl1ZdM79keZCC9enHa70vd8MrRAdtYcNWmGYQifI7QBE48dGjTRyCgdI_kka1rHwIJmXJCbtM1CoFCVyFS6AKYSVi5axjsAEglp3BZDhvbEfBFTGglqQtwn3IbGI=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2daRstd82shw3hX3dWvzu8m_6TbDvKKZu2Lfvw-6atzXoBXhXofGTTSskTfXJS0cDGh8cmW-e4Tf1YSGGSHkpEYPllqCTGF6-CN7lzFHlPYiglj5P8S_VI2CWT33sD9mnvNITDgVhL4wQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2PiFoztbJ3ODsdP5eHgKgmhyZCnBPHvisGuiU-DIw9CCRCYspu_wKhk3fiIYV2OQm-tL6HXPEywE0CZZX9tQdiCG_tYISiF7Dek71CL0J7veiE0sQI15vWhDYHnY9ozgayH_t1voX93Y_L=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn36O58yeuTVF1y5XAnt_PbexQXEsC7wq92GBGHu-m4l41BcmfdK0k7Vw-QYvsNeBvSDI89LZ_tUiby-mD61YhL_NcFYZ3thQv7QwOS2O95SIWudhOT904qLPxScA08v0jnVm7CCIkpQOFGl=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3O4L71ojZ_yStIDmWEbZGMveCuwhI7j1HyBL0023gHo_-cMXie0xmYDTfOXKiA4-aNC5O9l7SJ1UoBQS_O_Em-MIcQ5W_FunDY-ThTnKgK3uGLgenL0UkLX3VNJwnIyYfcehvLlE1MlWib=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-15"},{"Name":"Curtis Daugherty","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJmNvP4ibXr2u49022ZA1LDKuwv06JegSBYXMzCG9PhmO_I=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The Oral Surgeon Team was incredible! They made me feel calm and relaxed. They explained everything in detail and answered all my questions and concerns. They all did a great job on my procedure from start to finish.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Carpenter","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWXr1KcuMCnGwtm4-j6ayG2_j-0EfXOv5oRqCeAsED-nC1itQo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Having spent a small fortune in my life I choose dentists carefully. Started with a cleaning but it was clear to this skeptical eye this staff knew what they were doing. They moved with the confidence of a championship team. As a senior I knew I needed expert care going forward snd I can relax knowing Dr Beard and his team are worth every penny. The journey will be long but I’m in good hands. I got lucky choosing them first.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nathan Brooks","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJw3ZN5pKw4V1s7UWIg6XFZGZGRSdQXGNWYu-DsIt3OIRMaSA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had to find a new dentist and ended up trying Swish Dental. Getting an appointment was easy, they took my insurance and prices seems reasonable. All of the staff is very friendly and took it easy on me during the cleaning because I have sensitive teeth. Office is also very clean!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2GW-LCZQq_A0--GRj3ts93bWUAISwMwwTN47F8FEJDzi-R2Y4xQks3xRiiXj_LzGlaQvzJwybX3lL0efx7v9ZoIzBKTwE7eOAH0cJXd5enMIEZZj157BRcnhlfxXCEzYibXxSphj_qgGXY=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1Ca95ZuuJ4DRnfe09hUdpTnoRVtwnEcMkjL5yiKvHAopuv267IiHJAIPfD_yeRpnDvXRwBXgWzVjgf669y2c0EDHHCK3Z3TaanfGzjrDhlZ0ktXENeF8pCX72wXiL4EgVD_FllQVuu9ZQ=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1-UwxyTH02kbyGOgLL56RYyvkEn8EKvE2zd_vAbIz2LpFzJPct-P6dDIjTscbKvG54hF7pB-6kxDrl_WadblwgdwVvmHfGirYmDMky9ZnIynjrtEoOrcqvXhl2Albid7eVCdy-kwkxwPqX=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn30MyY70opuK5mz9rEwfd-rV5FCkgmOoMhTuyX-duHbpS6dfq-VceBrtLtaOiudOWQueBuE8BOiC9PbAQr9c0Otx_YQKDoP3X71JRK6lXZ-yPegmhbE9z6SsmPRm9OtvL1xa8zdRVmOtyM=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-10"},{"Name":"Isis Coreen Smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIpC2G6eS1HmrSKcAfs_elNVTrJAvg3fhsUqzUVMUyPRdHh6A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My friends/work colleagues recommended this location to me, after I was on the prowl for a new dentist…..I was recommended Dr Stone~\n\nUpon entrance to exit, you as a patient will be treated as if you are one of their very own relatives. I didn’t catch the front desk woman’s name, but she was very friendly, personable and helpful. From there, I was greeted by my hygenist, Heather. She was funny, sweet, but most importantly gentle \u0026 thorough \u0026 did a wonderful job cleaning my teeth. As for Dr Stone, he too was thorough, informative, kind, and knowledgeable. I appreciated the conservative approach in regards to watching possible problem areas (ex: a molar tooth may need a future crown in the future, and giving me pros and cons of Invisalign, retainers, night guards, etc etc… essentially not feeling forced or feeling pressure to any treatment but allowing me to make the best decision with all the info laid in front of me).\n\nAnyways, I think I found my new home for my dental plans \u0026 treatments, so I wanted to take this time to share my experience! Thanks! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michelle Matos Imbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWBj4bGChWFhaaaBeavMmb67-vxEVJcsrAOcjpK-JfSHhDvBK7d=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"Swish has been an amazing place to meet all of my dental concerns for the past 3 years up until my most recent appointment.\n\nSadly I was serviced by a person who didn’t even introduce themselves when we started, told me I had gum disease (when no one up until now had given me that diagnosis) and also scared me saying that if I don’t floss, the germs can hurt my baby (not the best way to start a cleaning appointment with a pregnant patient).\n\nI feel like I haven’t been properly informed about my condition (if I in fact have one) and it’s made me reconsider continuing with Swish. Before this experience, I always received great customer and professional services at both the Domain and Pflugerville locations. I hope the team takes my comment into consideration, not just for myself, but for other current and future patients, and that this isn’t just another review that will be forgotten.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
