ow, hand \u0026 foot massage, friendly and patient professionals who take their time with you— it’s the VIP vibe and you deserve it. Highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"whitney nalle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWap5d_ho37Vwhz0FEfnCeq_em4Cb8boWiTGmEOLqnTOQRc-FLD=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hands down the best experience I've had at a dentist. I have pretty severe dental anxiety, and the team and Austin Dental Spa really understand how to make you relaxed and comfortable. Shout out to Cara for taking good care of me 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Genevieve Pierce","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU7TEIzL47dStS2rYnTJJOoBnEdvuUAqVkxmlztLEcWwrfUGqSd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am so happy to have found Austin Dental Spa! I've been looking for a dental \"home\" most of my adult life in Austin, and I believe this is it.\nI'd been at another practice 8 years or so, and while they were fine at first, the quality was declining, and my final visit I was given a litany of treatments I needed that just didn't \"feel\" right. When I pushed back just a little, I was dismissed.\nSo I finally went about finding another dentist. I'm a very anxious patient, and Austin Dental Spa came up as a wonderful place for nervous patients. My first visit Martha and Dr. T really listened and walked through all the options for helping with anxiety. NO ONE HAS EVER DONE THIS FOR ME. On top of that an exam (based on the previous dentist exam/x-rays), found none of the issues I was going to get pilled, drilled, and billed for. Today at my cleaning with Bianca, I was treated with care, patience, and not made to feel stupid because I had anxiety.\nNot only will I be coming back (happily! to a dentist!!), but I'm bringing my entire family to Austin Dental Spa.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"KIRAZ CANDAN","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsjKzdblbWHspjDGdIV008h0Fi2K5ZMXEl6Pd5r_pFaxutgA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very grateful that I met Dr Crista, she is amazing, I totally trust her because she’s thinking my teeth health not like others to see as a money business for patients, I ‘ll definitely keep seeing her☺️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Maria Marta Carlin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXM_7vmdQN7CstkJPCLoGAtdkyYcWYd_4aP-AyZdVoXll8rt1k=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My son got his wisdom teeth removed here and everything went well. They were efficient in removing the teeth and helped prepare us for the recovery. My son had no problems after the surgery and I would recommend choosing this place if you’re in need of getting your wisdom teeth removed.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
