_MNb0yMige-dxi9eDsERUNKipxC5PDZVsZ3EeP=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"NEVER ever go to this Dentist Office. Complete waste of time. When making the appointment I asked specifically did they, in fact, accept my insurance. I was assured Yes. I was there to address two teeth that were giving me serious grief. WERE they interested in what I wanted?  NO. They like many current money hungry dentist only wanted to give me a full teeth replacement. Worse, when I left the office, they assured me they would get in touch with me after checking w the insurance company. Did they contact me?  NO. Not one call back but Yes they billed my insurance for what I don't know. Terrible Place. Do yourself a favor and go elsewhere!!!\n\nReply to Owner's Reply:\n\nNo sir, there is only one Georgetown 3D Dental on Hwy 29 in Georgetown which is where I went. Your reponse only demonstrates your office's incompetence. Look again and refund my money.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Giovanni M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWN1xshyyGDTYXWYz7QmPIdBATLJXmrnwvy5JMfRJSOUV9i9n2wQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very positive experience, as positive as dentist visits get. Jordan was very gentle and overall a great experience having my teeth cleaned. Glad I found a dentist I'm not going to hate coming to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Curtis Morris","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJTHFoqnnYS9-VwWtvcssDmM1bFeQY6y_6HNTmaKlNYwrgIiQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have been great with me and all the procedures for my implants. Heather always goes above and beyond to check on me. They have fixed everything that aspen dental messed up. Thank you Dr Ho and staff for a great experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Joyce James","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2e-E7-kl5y8K_Fadj6u-EFgLNvKntTFADLn23gt4u464_Fg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff are amazing from the time you walk in the door to the medical team. 3D Dental provided me a 360 degree different experience than another provider who promised permanent teeth in a day.\nThe doctors are so professional, caring, and honest. I loved everything about my experience.\nIt’s still a work in progress but it’s a wonderful start!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Arthur Jordan","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXehELvMmV-2NE9j1SEqYuq9DCXHTmJ2TKplB6bkD3oKuzohWhS0A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"​\"I cannot recommend Dr. Roland and Heather at 3D Dental enough. I came in two weeks ago for an emergency root canal and two crowns, and they got me in immediately to take care of the pain. The temporary crowns they placed were perfect and stayed secure the whole time. I went back today for my permanents, and the process was just as smooth. As someone who genuinely hates dental work, they made me feel comfortable and kept everything as pain-free as possible. I also really appreciated that they were honest—they didn't try to upsell me on extra work I didn't need. If you need dental work, go see these two!\"","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ryan Connors","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKId2elQaToPZHRouXq6SC7qViD2-LNsUfiEmd2r4xpqu4nBaE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I've been going here for years- excellent staff. Always polite and professional.\n\nToday I got a cleaning- Brittany was excellent. Very kind and welcoming.\n\nHighly recommend for folks looking for Dental services.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
