-/ALV-UjVnPC-gwU64ie_ziyACqh86maDRVKgHXt_SUkepWffrE3gSCmvp=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Nervous doesn’t even begin to explain the emotions I was feeling day of extraction but I had the best experience possible with Resource Care in Clyde. The staff were very friendly, attentive, and caring. The Doctor himself made me feel like I was an existing pt. He even called me a couple of hours later to just make sure all was well. Very thorough and professional care! So grateful for this group of people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mary","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6zp7LAb5wLGkvSwSFq1px2ps5EIySwzC6oaddWQQT2pwoCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff was ontop of scheduling for the day, I was called to fill a spot left open by a cancelation. I was seen a week earlier than my appointment. After the xrays Dr came in and was very personable which enabled us to have a relaxed conversation about my tooth future. The explanation of my options, nutrition, medical conditions and referrals made a very good conciliation.  The staff made my referral appointment and I was out the door in under an hour. I love having a local Dr.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah Mercer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKYN4sm6mggmdPj2XkHBy7_XEx4j7edpIIiDtUNAIVG4gF4kA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The most gentle and thorough cleaning I have ever had. They scheduled me in to replace a cancellation. I got my cleaning 2 months before my scheduled cleaning. Everyone is very kind and caring.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Debbie Kill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDSVNZslwKDhk_3R4jc-ZqJozom3HHd5fLln5weSGj1T94QQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"I was scheduled for an extraction which went very well. Except that he asked me which tooth a couple of times. I asked him if he could see me record of my exam. But he’s so gentle and painless. I also had a filling scheduled for that same appointment but he didn’t know anything about so I will have to go back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"janice Leyva","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI1rX5R5nRG8PQ1WaatjAufXMbl34BUt9kFy9L-lTNknzW4xw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Most compassionate, thorough and quality care I have ever received.  Even personally calls back to see how you are doing.  Great bedside and is very knowledgeable and gives you a personal caring experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Shelton","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLJQMq0G_aKAEaoAevq3rUMffZJOZA7XEpIt56IdHZ-PfFtLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was totally happy with my experience at Resource Care, Albany Texas.  The staff was excellent. Dr.Cavazos was knowledgeable and professional.  I highly recommend this facility.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
