e":"Round Rock Dentists (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114968290221116281411"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Oakmont Centre","street":"325 University Blvd","city":"Round Rock","postal_code":"78665","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"service_options","name":"Service options","options":[{"name":"Onsite services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":false}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Courtney Thomas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUbXjuFIV_2taD79GlIAn0Cd3vNCrzMGCARg6i6HjZCutlIDt93=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Theresa took my X-rays in the beginning. She was very sweet and made the x-ray portion move quickly. Dr. Megans was great. He completed my exam very quickly and painlessly. He offered advice to prevent any future issues and let me know which floss options were the best. Denise then helped me with the floss, polish, and fluoride and was very kind and helped make then end of my appointment just as painless. I would highly recommend this office for any dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandy LeCesne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLFJFjU-jHVO4FVVrHmE6DSXZy_WryurDs_SyRv2aIy6XQPaQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I have to say every experience at this office has been disappointing.  I continued to get my 6 month checkup there due to convenience.  Every appointment they have tried to get me to spend money out of pocket… I just would decline and get my regular cleaning and check up.  EXAMPLE: Telling me I need to remove old silver fillings that give me no issues.\nI went for my 6 month checkup  yesterday and they refused to give me a regular cleaning due to they said I needed a deep cleaning because of bacteria.  However,  I have had no issues in the past or present, no pain, no bleeding of the gums, no bad taste.  I am very diligent in brushing and flossing.  My bottom front teeth did have the regular build up, this has always been the same in all my 6 month appointments.  They refused to clean these teeth as well unless I agreed to the out of pocket deep cleaning expenses.  I ended up walking out and calling later for my records and X-rays.  I will not return!\nPlease be sure to get a second opinion if they are trying to bully you with additional dental services.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sylvia Castanon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIw1A48NEO6OOhXVpz4BlaK7zYIzeewDaSfpoUynJgVGiKtsw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I brought my dad here a couple of months ago, but this was my first appointment. I’ve always found the front desk staff to be pleasant and professional but had no experience with the rest of the staff.\nFor my visit, Theresah, the DA, was patient, kind, and professional. Dr. Farrar was very reassuring and easy to talk to. And Chrissy from the front was friendly, thorough and clear in communications about plans and costs. Thank you for making the dentist visit an easier experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tiffany Justice","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUWn8Q_3nyd5NJlopTQRSmU99_by6deek9L98hMtDyfDNygDUcMKQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Melissa and dr farrar are amazing!! They made me at ease with my experience  going back to the dentist after so long of not going because of a bad experience at my last dentist. They were kind, attentive and listened to my concerns and helped calm my mind. I recommend them to everyone. Best place to go! I will continue to go back","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Clarisa Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUiBUJ1kaNjmYYg-obEkIpJY_2qfFl2adexQuSzq8mpL8XKn7M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience at this dentist as a new patient! Alexia in the front desk was so friendly and helpful with scheduling and insurance, which made everything stress-free. The hygienist was gentle, and the dentist took time to explain everything clearly. The office is clean and comfortable, and I left feeling really well cared for. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jorge Rios","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKMxhQ3-ibHT96PhJ9CIlU-WAx0446AJIuUNIg9tJvwvYt6nQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Giovanna was very friendly and professional. Dr. Megens is extremely attentive and has excellent bedside manners. I’ve been coming here for years, ever since my children were small. It’s a great place in a great location with friendly staff all around. They always do their best to work with my busy schedule. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Demery","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJrpKZ65ToZ7fRAqZyinM6wXwnbS7IDL2Xqzk3-KMD6uF9z3A=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This office is VERY accommodating! They were able to get us in for an emergency visit the same day. They also worked with our budget to find affordable options and even offered a payment plan. From the front staff to the Dental Assistant to the Dr; EVERYONE was pleasant to work with. Our dentist for years!! Give them a try!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn22Z83yk35SqAbPVUgCVAJVP2RxOfB9hl7JNldaln1LI4E1-vUvtwGyu6OT4qGWaf1xXE9cIFObgdYIh86ekuXPWU53UvwpYr54Huq8rYfWusAdVfiGlkxXMiKMhWcHdkHzHTMj6jL6Ipue=k-no"],"When":"2025-8-29"},{"Name":"Erika Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVFilrtj9l4wAR_lE-fsPoonmx1J_8v3TjjuDc3HYIHoiFJ5qN36w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience during my recent treatment, and I want to give a special shout-out to Denise. She was incredibly kind and made sure I was comfortable the entire time. Her professional yet friendly attitude really helped ease my dental anxiety. Thank you, Denise!\"","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
