:"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"CANDICE OVERSTREET","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLDBxzXh0RIGtGwhku5uLxf3So3yjEgyzoyjjVFMGJYfLaA078=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"New office manager is rude!!!!!! I have been a patient here for over five years!! I asked about my insurance and was told doctor out of network!!!!! No one have ever shared that with me!!! This office manager  got me dismissed without me evening speaking with Dr Lai!!!!! I'm in the middle of my ortho treatments my insurance has paid all my claims??!? Clarissa got upset necks I asked a question about billing and coins!!!!! Please don't waste your time office staff turnover will run up your blood pressure!!!! Taking my smile and my insurance and money elsewhere!!!!! Do not go here!!!!!!!!!! Over six years what a waste of my time!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"theresa smith","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJk7BCv541ZE0NqaLmvHgwSWAFN0D9QgH9fEb9Lk68vOmAXMQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I didn’t  enjoy going to the dentist but going to Edge Dental is different. I floss like my hygienist told me and since then my cleanings have been so much better. Everyone is friendly and caring. Best dentist and highly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Mairim van Domselaar","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtsZlx8POwsQgNuyn3EPlLvCrpFYG1q5TkY1LY_NXljyO1cGwENw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I needed an emergency appointment and they were able to accommodate me even though it was a Friday. Very friendly staff. Needed a referral for an endodontist and they gave me a name and they were able to set an appointment immediately for the next day! Surprising since it was for Saturday. Couldn't be happier. 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jim Godell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW-Sx7-RiisylKiOL25hBHXZRi0XXtJtuCmCPT3RG-FvNjB4Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I found the people at Edge Dental to be friendly, helpful, and very professional. I am having crown work done. I have found it to be painless and professionally done. I am very happy with my experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Walsh","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUYeXlNX3l09088639VsOjnbBx21sZYVpzTtD0MjQSUh3AglUat=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am very pleased with how well Edge Dental communicated with me before and after an appointment I made for a patient that I am responsible for that can not make decisions for themselves.  Edge Dental sent me the appropriate forms in advance for past history information and authorization to communicate with me for future care.\n\nImmediately after the examination they presented me with a detailed \"Active Treatment Plan\" that prioritized each procedure needed along with an explanation of what was required and the cost with the insurance plan I had for this individual.  They have been flexible on scheduling dates for the work needed for the patient.\n\nP.S.  They were recommended to me by other clients of Edge Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"RJ Lewis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI8e9Xk83cpedPhoypL1XhjGnkewTLKjhyJmBd7WupVsqtpFg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m a 74 y.o. retired dentist of 42 years, I have been looking for a dentist in the Houston area since my dentist of 40 years in Huntsville is retiring. I visited 3 other offices and was underwhelmed with either the staff or dentist. My experience with Dr. Lai was very similar to my retiring dentist. The intake process was very smooth and comprehensive. They verified my insurance within a day. The initial diagnostic process included a panograph and full mouth X-rays. The hygienist did a periodontal (gum) evaluation, which most offices don’t do initially. Dr. Lai was very affable and I didn’t feel like he was trying to sell me on  treatment that was not appropriate for my age. I had 2 complex implants done by a local oral surgeon in January that needed the final restorations (abutments and crowns.) They had my treatment plan ready within 30 minutes and Dr. Lai was able to do the scans for the implant crowns. Norma, his hygienist, cleaned my teeth during the same visit and discussed the condition of my gums. She was very thorough but gentle. I should have this phase of my treatment completed by the end of the month. What would have ordinarily taken 3 appointments took 1. The front desk and assistants were very thorough and efficient. I gave Dr. Lai and is staff 5 stars and  being a dentist myself, I am probably going to be a practitioners worst critic. I am going to refer my wife, which I obviously would not do unless I had full faith and confidence in the practitioner and his staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sharita Henley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVKVyTIEcrNUjMf87-UlKFvcgtobxPS-Q7NOkKN-qQz-uBoHu4Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I referred my sister she made an appointment Justin and the hygienist was very knowledgeable \u0026 gave honest feedback I called just to see if my insurance was accepted when I found out they open late I got in same day 6:30pm I Had tartar build up on bottom teeth and whew the hygienist CLEANED my entire mouth so good she was very knowledgeable even with me being the last patient she took her time with me and answered All my questions! Thank you to All the staff from the scheduling to the end! (Me today on the trail at 5:30am with a Big smile)","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2NBZ58H70xFMcIbJ_Op6w5hwbEskCZXYjRJNckUmFCwkFrWQRl6BsBrTAwQIRjUZNPs2oMgXx_VviEViraCG7WaBJ8tgQ-yI0E48Ndy2SoBV8jWrD6AP2WNRloqLrgZHaZMXY1Wj4qQak=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-25"},{"Name":"S George","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjViRJ3yLTbo5iQjowTmBsA339wglneqAlzD5gODe1II5LB1hGHb=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love all the staff. Each of them treat me with a smile, and provides great service. Love to go to Edge Dental.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
