s was smooth and successful.\nThe final result is perfect; the healing dentures are comfortable and look amazing. If you are considering Aspen Dental, especially for dentures, we highly recommend this location. The people and the doctor here are truly awesome!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John O","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLs5Y-Xh8cJvJgDVZfDuAsMNmr2wEuD6AUFCVQ7gLl-exO1IA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow!! What a great day at the dentist! Yes it was the best experience for a dental appointment. First of all Amanda the hygienist was super cool and funny she made my visit nice and pleasant. Thank you. Dr K. He came in and Presented my new partials and they fit perfect. I was like how did you do this? He said it’s magic. Hahahahaha. Anyways best dental office I’ve been to. Highly recommended","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Candice Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJFU7YwawFhu0i6ev9wfIxIitB6gXjYEm35vYE4FyRkTyU9mQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"A huge shout out to Ashley, Alisha, Amanda, and Dr K, who took such good care of me when I broke my tooth. I have terrible anxiety, but they were all so kind, compassionate, and caring that I was comfortable the whole time. I have found my forever dental home, for sure.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
