Tkk60ihtuQVjSaxyDlsx8yeCN8-auu5FBalkTMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had nothing but great experiences at Lakewood Dental Trails. The hygienists are truly wonderful - Zoe and Lindsey have both been amazing. They’re gentle, thorough, and always make the appointment feel comfortable and stress-free. You can tell they really care about their patients.\n\nDr. Kern has also always been a fantastic dentist - knowledgeable, kind, and easy to trust. She takes the time to explain things clearly and never makes you feel rushed.\n\nOverall, this office has an excellent team and a welcoming atmosphere. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Ashley Berthiaume","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKBivOgsMOFt2cZJeJJfZey24QfxkHdMb4HR3lRiiyn1zUX=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a great experience at LDT! I have minor dentist anxiety as I am newly into going to the dentist truthfully. Zoe was my hygienist and was so pleasant. She listened to my history and was so kind. She told me everything she was going to do before starting which I liked. The facility was clean and my appointment time was honored with no wait time. I have found my new dentist office, very pleased!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rosie Rosatti","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZyfeaHtr1e0RorFjZMHte5tEmmxi-Ke548EGCh-RMFYSBzQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Lindsey, from Texas, is amazing! She definitely reviews her patient’s charts prior to their appointment. She makes you feel like she just saw you yesterday, that’s how well she is prepared. Her bedside manner is second to none. She listens to her patients and effectively communicates their concerns to the dentist. Lindsey is a gem and Lakewood Dental Trails, and its patients are lucky to have her!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"MATTHEW WARGO","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVu8gogSKAcRL4iIZVG_G8O0jHNO8FOThubXL