 his wisdom teeth extracted by Dr Roberts and everything went very well and recovery was amazing. Lupita did a great job setting up the appointment and communicating. Thank you","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bayard Friedman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLG6i_t4k_mAs9kFyyafuxrAmvx-80SxVPig8h8N8eE-uO5Cw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really hate dentists.  Usually.  This group was awesome.  Addressed real issues, felt like they cared to make it as comfortable as possible, clean, technologically up to date.  Very courteous and clear.  Definitely my new dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"rachel reid","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWfY7r029yuIjgEHN0l9wntzVKkXWuywbs6pdjmVv6WMjwG5Ph0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Warsop is the best dentist! She is very nice and puts you at ease. Landry gives a great cleaning. The whole team an Highland Park Dental is superb! 10/10 recommend!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lucy Hasselbrink","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJqMYSRLvXDdzpySgVnkwJWdP38XQbSS5JEbQP9RnzHOTiULw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience! Very thorough and everyone was so nice! Best dentist experience I’ve ever had!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Trecia Sylvester","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLbcCs2g_AFwjGpfWNVeaOuNk7-vqDQAydCGWnMMFpfxerS-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"HP Dental services are Top-notch. My hygienist takes excellent care of me. Dr. Jones \u0026 his entire team truly cares for their patients. It actually doesn’t feel like I’m going to the dentist. It is such a relaxing  atmosphere with friendly and well informative staff. I enjoy going to HP Dental and I highly recommend👌","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Christopher Derderian","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKNTDTk683H2mS1HVaanZnbmHHU2nxEQw7kYVwbGZ_gedtyAA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been going to highland park dental for over ten years. Dr Jones has done extensive work on my teeth including root canals and I could not be happier with my results. Landry is my dental hygienist and she is outstanding. She is meticulous and an absolute professional. The staff are always friendly and scheduling is easy. Could not recommend more.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
