:"Windsor Hills","street":"1015 E Braker Ln #2","city":"Austin","postal_code":"78753","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Craig Matlock","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVWzgMS9Vr0v_OVwY2SpS0e_FWa65kAyxr--3K8FUwHhU1WC1E=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came here for a one off as I chipped my tooth trying to fix a key ring…yes I’m aware that was stupid, but that’s beside the point. I came here for what I deemed an emergency and they got me right the same day. That brief transaction made me a fan of this place and I’ve been a client since then. The whole staff is always a1 and they treat you with so much organic kindness. Just got my braces done today (shoutout to Jennifer and Doc Sheinbein) and I couldn’t be any happier. Y’all got me for life!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Johnny King","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_YX1z352aEAS4VN8ewlGcwvUY9P7x8GUsYYrHD1hEzgBY0kX8Qw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Jennifer has an amazing caring approach to her job. Best cleaning I can remember having in decades. Dentist was non nonsense, detailed, and also non invasive. I give 5 stars as I cannot remember the last time I had such a pain free experience. They really care and kept asking how I was doing throughout. You can tell everyone here likes their job and are proficient.\nJennifer is superb for the cleaning ask for her!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Juliana K","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUI-lJ9k1h-pCYpSFVZg7xtiCJ3qMuhiznqaLGOlTlxu5V-AHE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"They have been my dentist for 12 years. During that time they've only recommended one filling, and the assistant held my hand while they did it. When they weren't accepting my new insurance, they very generously honored it and didn't charge me. They always run on time and have been cleaning my teeth by hand all this time because the cavitron thing made my teeth too sensitive. I can't think of a single complaint I've had with them in all this time.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kristina Reed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIVY1aM1xATucjwjWdpfMk10YcT7TTKRx92CVSev2LFtwKkDA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful doctor. I trust her ! Im very scared when it comes to work on my teeth, but she will put you at ease.  Also each and everyone of the assistants and ladies at the front are are very very nice and make you feel comfortable !\n\nAgain a hard tooth with a super long root was able to be pulled by my wonderful dentist ! I don’t know how her and her staff make me feel so at ease even with a fear of the dentist . This place is great , they make you feel welcome and want you to make yourself at home. I’ll never go anywhere else. Very professional staff at the front as well as kind and friendly attitudes!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2QfQES_bLSzeYGp5FtSDdtyqQY7AcGtw1FpGIHfHOqPiO1AXO5P1uDwmGA-COsW4g_l3K_f7jIBnAM1mo6uaqahZ5RZxXJFA-I_8BmC-HLXveqLITcc7Rbqgo7BiQLDdgAuUAv=k-no"],"When":"2019-2-22"},{"Name":"Grumpysleeper","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWVTFSdeLJQ0oezaIuE7EddjYOJ4ZL7ZML_AhCkJJtfOcV3rxw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'm so glad I found this dentist! I went in for a routine cleaning and exam but was nervous to get anything done since I'm 37 weeks pregnant. They made sure not to use anything that was unsafe for me or baby! I felt completely at ease and knew I was in good hands. My teeth feel so clean and I'm glad I went in.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jamie Vasquez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXq_pX5M9m8r_I3GJY1K8DqZqpZGpIORm48G4bv6Wb6bnr2yhWf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Most amazing and patient DA I have ever had. Nohemi was so sweet and comforting when I told her how nervous and embarrassed I was. The Dr took her time and explained everything to expect and how to plan my procedures. I cried in the chair and they waited and talked me through it. I have never been so comfortable and felt truly listened to at a dental office. This is the only dentist myself, my husband and our Four children will go to. Thank you so much everyone!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"miki","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVjyfOJppc-Xlk5PSNlzmNHfYg0e3-cwv2mIMljBexoWP0okpTZCQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Zayed is AMAZING. She’s funny, patient, and very thorough. She explained what all my X-rays meant, was gentle in the exam/cleaning, and made me feel safe. The wait time in the office was minimal. The staff were all kind and accommodating. I highly recommend this dentist and office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabe Link","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTUw4bFR9E4oyjDXAlrqDTxVvZiHzT8V-pSYKyVTe5FU2yjo_eVA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba5-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We've been coming here before our kids had teeth and they've always been so kind and friendly. Dr. Sheinbein has always so gentle that the kids actually look forward to going to the dentist. All the staff is awesome. Thanks!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2GviOjeiCtWMHNZ0Lf394VnHq0SigXNx3AMdXjzNhdKJnRqIab7fguxizi_SChomaIYwhdkm5M6RJBjtI0IIIfvGpCtLbFR_0VjDzhTkNCxZ9oOTfxInYq2Pz2qvg0twPRe6oJ2w=k-no"],"When":"2021-9-8"}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
{"input_id":"980960e8-b2b9-417f-aacf-84dfb09ec85e","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/place/University+Dental/data=!4m7!3m6!1s0x8644d15c79478ae3:0x4334f013273d9a84!8m2!3d30.560491!4d-97.690316!16s%2Fg%2F1tcvv7k8!19sChIJ44pHeVzRRIYRhJo9JxPwNEM?authuser=0\u0026hl=en\u0026rclk=1","cid":"4842759464383519364","title":"University Dental","categories":["Dental clinic","Cosmetic dentist","Emergency dental service"],"category":"Dental clinic","address":"200 University Blvd #340, Round Rock, TX 78665","open_hours":{"Friday":["Closed"],"Monday":["8 AM–5 PM"],"Saturday":["Closed"],"Sunday":["Closed"],"Thursday":["7 AM–3 PM"],"Tuesday":["8 AM–5 PM"],"Wednesday":["7 AM–3 PM"]},"popular_times":{},"web_site":"http://www.keeproundrocksmiling.com/","phone":"(512) 904-0672","plus_code":"H865+5V Round Rock, Texas","review_count":126,"review_rating":4.9,"reviews_per_rating":{"1":3,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":122},"latitude":30.560491,"longtitude":-97.690316,"status":"","description":"","reviews_link":"","thumbnail":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGkrLxFreb3P3hhhyY3X4r07T8tjMoc11VBM6obEnyC5fKfue_OPAs-VqZkM8-XZTGKQphsGnHq2LtVbtw8aBoydGaklxNNvmp8Q3VvDQZC1UE9leDPl-HhCrho4RXhyBii6DaHug=w426-h240-k-no","timezone":"America/Chicago","price_range":"","data_id":"0x8644d15c79478ae3:0x4334f013273d9a84","place_id":"ChIJ44pHeVzRRIYRhJo9JxPwNEM","images":[{"title":"All","image":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/gps-cs-s/APNQkAGkrLxFreb3P3hhhyY3X4r07T8tjMoc11VBM6obEnyC5fKfue_OPAs-VqZkM8-XZTGKQphsGnHq2LtVbtw8aBoydGaklxNNvmp8Q3VvDQZC1UE9leDPl-HhCrho4RXhyBii6DaHug=w529-h298-k-no"},{"title":"Street View \u0026 360°","image":"https://streetviewpixels-pa.googleapis.com/v1/thumbnail?panoid=XpMYQh-jilzKiEc_IbTuIg\u0026cb_client=maps_sv.tactile.gps\u0026w=224\u0026h=298\u0026yaw=40.393234\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"111798268838959995512","name":"University Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111798268838959995512"},"complete_address":{"borough":"Chandler Road Retail","street":"200 University Blvd #340","city":"Round Rock","postal_code":"78665","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Cosmetic dentistry","enabled":true},{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Sheila Jones","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU_fYLTySesyW_rMfytqHz3xAVgycpVgO1tfwGUL1yXg9BXLc9E=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Come here if you want dentists who truly care, take time to explain everything in a way you can understand, and make every visit a pleasant experience. They always make sure I’m comfortable and at ease (I have a very low pain tolerance), and they consistently make me feel like my experience genuinely matters. From start to finish, the whole team is kind, patient, and professional. I've had many dentists throughout the years and have NEVER been treated this way. Dr. Naik and Dr. Angela Niknam are rare gems!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"DD's House","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWCjJAMfNaHkd4DyDVZbJQiv755KR9EglHl-D08eLOoXfKfaM0c=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve been going to University Dental for over 10 years, and they are absolutely the best! The whole team is friendly, straightforward, and honest. They always take the time to listen to what I want and make me feel comfortable. I couldn’t imagine going anywhere else.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"SkyeArte (Skye)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUqpaRO56bsbdZlT9xucILF6VzUTFWjRsOPUX0XNFXVRQBFbhaA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My parents, myself, and now my spouse have been getting work done here for as long as I can remember. This practice puts you and your comfort first, not their bottom line. I was genuinely shocked seeing how people were being treated elsewhere due to how amazing the staff here has been to me on every visit. I highly, *highly* recommend this office to anyone looking for a long-term dentist. For the procedures they cannot do, they have equally amazing practices they refer to.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Don Zuckerman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8rRsguW6I4FdFoUJXRsNWe0pkLNszKYBfQUx4A4ykTRrG-6Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Have a long dental history with lots of ups and downs, psychologically hate going to Dentist.  Dr Nikam's friendliness, warm demeanor and honest approach to things made my visit great.  My first visit was thorough, with a full discussion of my history and a detailed professional exam that included me in as a participant.   Even with work to be done was a very relaxed experience.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"ABHIKALP M","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLgaHNizNC5GNNbwsoby3aL9nUZiI_Y5LOKkWeSev43xlbDPeds=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very pleased with our visit.  The entire staff is very patient and hospitable. Dr. Angela is extremely polite and helpful. She is very knowledgeable and straightforward. We felt we were getting a genuine advice on every step. They made us feel very comfortable. Highly recommend for those looking for great care and attitude. Thank you University Dental team !","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tina Auer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvacLyTdpYIDd61hF0QKw3ImN55QzFi7sPp-dBg0bAfpbQMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Everyone, from the receptionist to the hygienists and dentists themselves, is incredibly friendly and professional. They take the time to explain everything clearly and answer any questions you might have. Both dentists are knowledgeable, gentle, and truly care about your dental health. Dr. Niknam is amazing!! She discovered an issue that many other dentists had missed. For that I am truly grateful! I highly recommend this dental practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sarah Garza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrmt5hy483LUxdj5ZzO-BA_opddeOthr4v_4YXx8Mn0hCajtQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I'll start by sharing that I've hated going to the dentist my whole life; I've been known to cry at teeth cleanings. I told all of this to the team when I first came to University Dental and they went above and beyond to make me feel comfortable. I thought maybe I received special treatment that first time but I've been going consistently for a few years now and every visit has been just as good. The entire staff just seems happy with what they do every day. I would highly recommend University Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sabine McCalla","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU4hAqWG_QnEly9Bz-Oab_34aGUZs4ncS4KR0zf9Th83PAQid2N=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"University Dental is fantastic. My dental hygienist, Shermance, is upbeat and fun and makes a \"not so fun\" experience much less daunting. The dentist himself is friendly and makes you feel comfortable. I was afraid of going to the dentist most of my life - not anymore, thanks to the friendly and empathetic staff. And one thing I appreciate as a professional: Their time management. I barely have to wait.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
