C mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jayme Miller","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWRGgAiTtvHYSSHdM3YTJI9UKwn0vcoDI-LXEYycIIJe3QeBHk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I feel it best to take time out to praise when praise is deserved.   I went in and was greeted warmly.  The atmosphere was welcoming and the staff were pleasant. One of the staff members, her name was Megan, phenomenal. She treated me like she knew me, which was very calming. She was very informative, attentive, and so, so kind.  I came here because of the open availability, but I’m now staying here and making this my family dentist office because of Megan.  Those who go above and beyond really make all the difference.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julie Gillentine","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW4wCek96VdPt8a2ZnR5utgtCH0uPa9k-NmdVSrCEHsXM_2pxdk=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I did a new patient exam and was highly impressed with how thorough they were. The wait time was minimal. Everyone was knowledgeable and happily answered my million questions. The office manager was able to utilize both of my insurances to get me an unbelievable cost for treatment. The entire office was very clean. I highly recommend this dental office to everyone.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Car B","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-Mulc8lINUu5Ae66S__xOytnkpK85RbXwQF5IjT6nAjinGg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a comfortable experience there on two recent visits.  First the location on major business street is easily visible and accessible.  Plenty of parking.\nSarah at reception desk was always pleasant and helpful when scheduling and needing to reschedule due to bad weather.  Kele was very pleasant when taking x rays.  Met dentist and hygienist also that initial visit.  Surprised how efficient the office was.  No long waiting towards end of the day.  Really appreciate that appointment was at no charge to assess and review my issues.  I was provided with a detailed outline of expenses which felt overwhelming but as I requested, the treatment coordinator unbundled so was easier to understand. After obtaining insurance, scheduled periodontal cleaning.\nUpon arrival, was easily able to make my payment on my phone privately in the lobby.  Waiting room was not crowded, quiet, comfortable, noticeably clean and neat even late afternoon.\nMet hygienist, Jordan.  I really appreciate that she made her office atmosphere comfortable.  No bright overhead fluorescents, soft music and a TV was on.  I was fearing the procedure would be painful, but she explained what to expect and talked through what she was doing when performing the procedure.  She was extremely attentive, gentle and very pleasant which put my fears at ease.  After, she scheduled next appointment, clearly provided precise after care instructions, special toothpaste and rinse for home care.  She did not rush even with another person waiting.\nI met with the treatment coordinator who was available and again patiently reviewed future treatment details plus provided printout that I could take home.\nOverall, I made comfortable, felt staff was extremely pleasant, professional and office is very well organized.\nI highly recommend this office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nutterz06ss","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKUw41bEnuLCCm86in48P5bHEIj0CeSDte6vwigqAWg_vNITQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely amazing staff. Was greeted when I walked in the door by sara who was extremely nice and polite. After doing some paper work, the assistant Megan and Amanda helped me through the process of getting my tooth the same day! The Dr was very thorough and telling everything that needed to be done during and after the extraction. Wonderful staff thank you all who helped Sara,Lexy,Megan,Amanda and Dr Sindhi!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shelby Aguerro","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLy47QSSDNIHNn8DZDe-0o2tK9RfVi8HjpatYFe2i9upjirr-w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had major dentist anxiety since I can remember and apparently I passed it onto my daughter. So we  both very nervous when it comes to going to the dentist. The front desk girl has some superpowers and became friends with my kid and that made the whole experience way better than I could have expected! My daughter said that “Sarah was really nice and funny.”  10/10!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon Vincent","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzhjA6W4G1ogEHmX7fsulH_BAy73tpB9LefjXdR2u2YziXug=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a pleasant experience. Went in with a broken tooth and they were able to pull it out the same day. The staff is friendly snd the doctor was amazing! Will definitely go back for dental needs.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Zachary Winchell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3iGZJngdDoedVS_5RQ5ysErMWuzMFxB4uykvqw1n2P3H4I4MH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My experience here was phenomenal. They made sure I was aware of every step of the process and made sure I was comfortable. If I had any questions or concerns they didn't hesitate to help me. I definitely found my new dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"William Strawbridge","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkQLVh55vjmpy2DCtEoaooCyf--WkgIamrMr4YZvMJzuzoxg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I guess I have to be the one to give a bad review. I had to have a tooth pull, pretty much had a bunch of stuff done that I didn’t want. I understand the X-Rays needed to be done. Then I was treated in an uncomfortable position that the denist made me fell uncomfortable in result my blood pressure was very high and was not able to pull the tooth. So I’m left paying a $2400 bill I have to pay and I still have tooth that needs to be taken care of.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
