f from work to be here for my appointments. I am losing money. The entire system here is broken. I have already pre-paid $1200 for my dental work that they can't seem to finish.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1sBQmjjERyen4EOu2SjCb3x1m1I76kQm3KVr1CcOaDlPdZzfIYJjQ8ivJdAyabkUXedS-nZP9TKGy3tmxc1CV5v3Ks05_pdwvEYWOhCyOi9a-9azCFrdTAGdw6yBwTEgwT5Qy3Tw=k-no"],"When":"2022-3-4"},{"Name":"Teresa Trevino","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkzBb7FmLB5mwkM98fQqhXmPjqsz2MnfHod16amY7--7vBDePUOw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":4,"Description":"We have been with Brident for a couple of years now. Great experience with them, friendly staff and great doctors. My only complaint is how often they change our appointment time after we have already set it. If you know the Dr doesn't do certain treatments after a certain time of the day, why call and confirm the appointment I called to make if you're just going to change it on me anyway. I set.y appointments at the time I do because it works for my schedule and my daughters. If I had any pick of the day, I wouldn't mind but I work 10hr days plus run a business.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lily Guerrero","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVLR2FvuO5nQD8F2PvMDSr2AwGT2f4LnANfaTtuWEXM1BCE_xk7Sg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"DO NOT GO HERE. Terribly unorganized and unprofessional. I’m currently waiting for service for my 9:30 appointment. Plus, do you want to use the products that they leave on the floor for bugs to live in?","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0Tm4nYAIHNWLjP_prM_25cZbBuYPO1wWK5JmdODYXSx5P9enwYIUqfZn-sRrFzSVZAgg_jHBIanQzBWf19k7Dk5gUPoIR353zsy7hicIoIsXpN7rMFw8WHbI9ytSv0zGi3NFz-=k-no"],"When":"2023-9-16"},{"Name":"Brittany Sterling","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9QOGo9E1oUmLHlYKazCiWFZp9N6j04l8XxeTwKT_hv6WMRpwbsg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very professional doctor R she had the staff check my Blood Pressure which I’ve never had done at a dental office before and I have had a lot of work done dental wise. This show’s accountability And care for patients. For her to get my blood pressure taken tells me that she is very advanced in her practice and truly cares about her patients overall Heath. I am a nursing student so that speaks volumes from a medical standpoint. The establishment was very clean and welcoming and Dental Receptionist Ms.Agata Greeted me with warmth and understanding. The staff explained everything they were performing and treated me like family. I will be back to see them soon as I was satisfied with my treatment. They got me in and out promptly with excellent service and clear explanation about my treatment plan. I got there at 2:30pm and left at 3:09pm Well done!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"kayla randømz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULBVN8T4kpEgtssBYYSaAgEygpKXsOThrtIhIQYt_5sbDS-UwW=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"This place really sucks and dont recommend, I wish I could give them 0 stars. They give appointments at 9am but don't open until 40 minutes later and like to take their sweet time, but God forbid you're 5 minutes late to an appointment or they will make you resquedule. Not only do they not care about your time but the staff is also very unprofessional. One time I came in for a cleaning but the only thing they did was just check my teeth out and after that the dentist wouldn't even tell me what was going on, she kept me waiting in the chair for 20 minutes straight talking to staff. If I can describe this place in one word it would be horrible, I hope I never have to set foot in there again.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Anna Almquist","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK6inBdx-z1xTkRToRtxZW61p3-hHgf5zkv9IojPe13CiExHg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":2,"Description":"I only give 2 stars and not 1 because the doctor was nice. However, the staff was incredibly slow. I waited over an hour for my apt and it legit took another hour. AFTER I had my hour long appointment after waiting an hour for it, I was informed they don’t guarantee same day cleanings. I have never in my life not had a cleaning scheduled after an exam. I thought I was getting a cleaning, since it’s not “guaranteed”, I didn’t even get one. This place is a scam, avoid it.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
