nabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"jerome k","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIZQ1nQt5XW94ax2IUq5BJjLUH02UpdPK79BQEee9pGJT9U7w=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a sudden dental emergency and was honestly pretty anxious walking in—but Michaela and Dr. Thornton turned the entire experience around. Michaela was warm, reassuring, and incredibly efficient getting me settled and ready so quickly. Dr. Thornton was calm, professional, and clearly very skilled. What could have been a stressful day, was instead a smooth experience! Their team is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Michael Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWNpmkP4aN3NIZ0PonCSzLC-PsgczCveJSR0K3Ddbon5xNNcDTiWw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Customer Service At Thornton Dental!!! They were able to schedule me the same day I called. Their office is set up very Elegantly and Everyone was Extremely Nice \u0026 Professional! I will Definitely Be Back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1oSVKijDUcj3KN7VwpuTPJyuxdBBnsfvAVdG6ZWj4OV8kN2BftV9aw6S3_BzKH8utvqGRCH8z-V3hUMREHkn3V5xABN49yCCp1IVKWTxosELCKMl-PeghiVCYwTkWeA5wfYraYwwHRAPNg=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1SxSu4MH5NQerXEQEcy7kaucrWDepcXb0boGastddavm-9-6zUzkqE9s0R25yoThNVU9NQWdc4P7jg2jccz9__5ZILLpxoOPUb3YXso-L3KNFbEggdrpWm3AmijDD9SnccMJU3vUxU837e=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-5"},{"Name":"Toni Foreman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWoE1NgWkBguE101AF5boFa85kQD-XExwmwOmPOjkgwe_KeLkN1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was the first visit with Dr Thornton so of course I was nervous.\nThe office is extremely inviting and geared towards our comfort (they even have chairs with massage for waiting)! I was skeptical regarding the consultation as I’ve never experienced this where I’m from but it gives a good opportunity to get to know each other and what the expectations are.\nThe teeth cleaning was fabulous and the care is just well, beyond my expectations. It’s nice to have found a dentist I can trust. I hope I’m able to give reviews throughout my experience going forward.\nSo far I’m giving her and the whole team a 10!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kylan Gurnell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUNImKKhe2sAKXJJ74DhOiLF5AaFYw8yH5NfkgqFkcxBdo28f8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve had a bad track record with dentists my entire life, which led me to avoid them for a long time. It is hard to find a dentist you can trust and be honest with. The moment I came to Thornton Dental, I felt like more than just a patient. Michaela  was the first person to help me, and I immediately felt safe and like I could tell her everything. She was very attentive and understanding, while being super helpful when it came to figuring out how I was going to pay for the procedure. On the day of my tooth extraction, Dr. Thornton and her assistant made sure I was calm, comfortable, and completely numb before doing anything. They were constantly checking on me, asking if I felt any pain, and explaining all that they were doing. I walked in nervous for the surgery and by the time we were almost done, I was falling asleep in the chair! I’m very grateful for how little pain I felt during and after the surgery, but I’m most grateful for the entire staff’s compassion, empathy, and dedication to making me feel like more than just another patient. Without a doubt the best I’ve ever been to, it’s such a relief to not have to dread coming to the dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carrie Harrod","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9DYxAwSP6tOJy1SYJlCH6oVytAEQVOtMs8w-inY92Kgsk-Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing Dentist!! My son needed four fillings and was extremely nervous about it. Dr. Rahimi- Thornton and her entire team were incredibly kind and went above and beyond to make him feel as comfortable as possible. I would highly recommend Thornton Dental to anyone looking for a compassionate, gentle dentist.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OQqtKj03vo2M1LDNlL_BuxqBttpbDarM5JvFgBktsxt3URupjR1RS2ULcicFEXVjNCmRuxp9xkwZPPZSnoeyrE_p_rQ7sgHeAaJtGSDM0Fk--tJu4EMgTQkLluDAHfhj-HZqrHi6V9hx6=k-no"],"When":"2025-7-18"},{"Name":"Caitlyn Guy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLpudXZFn46-ktMpI6wCya27ZyAzZe3nP7rErT8ieWiNbOABA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’ve always had a lot of anxiety when it comes to dental work, so I was really nervous about trying a new dentist. But let me tell you—this team is absolutely amazing! They made the entire process smooth, comfortable, and stress-free. Everyone was so understanding about my fears and took the time to help me create a plan to get my dental work done in a timely way. If I could give them 10 stars, I absolutely would. Highly, highly recommend! 🤍","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dr. Becca Sansom","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVzA6Pvsy85P70B7QC7oQ9ay5h-JtgMQJNXnTOYIV5WKb3tTVAt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I am a relatively new patient at Thornton Dental, and was referred by a good friend. I’ve been impressed with the professionalism of the staff, the modern X-rays and treatments, and the personal attention from Dr. Thornton. She takes time to explain everything and make sure you are comfortable and understand. It’s also a nice bonus to have a little spa treatment while getting a cleaning—eye masks or paraffin hand treatment. Takes the sting out of visiting the dentist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Hostage Hirsch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhcSmJQHe0WwO5qXw1vZMk1EL99_GZyw2vKFufTNil7AKSpE7S=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Absolutely love Thornton Dental! Coming from someone who’s always had a strong dislike for dentists because of bad experiences in the past,they are the complete opposite and a bright spot in the dental industry!\nI went to them with an emergency, they saw me as soon as they opened,even when they weren’t seeing patients! Got me a prescription to chill out my tooth, put a game plan together on how to treat it and a couple of days later, got me all fixed up! Dr.Thornton, Dana, and Michaela were all awesome and I will see nobody but them moving forward!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
