s always pleased! Great job!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amber Mobley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLY9oC9yewK5OI0aM-J081tJxjE9NR94cSwLPQZ7b-VfoV_FA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff is amazing and friendly. It was my 4 year olds first time in this office and he was very nervous. The hygienist and Dentist are both wonderful with children and made him feel super comfortable. I can’t thank enough for such a smooth visit today. My whole family can now go one place for our dental visits.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Karen Herrley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVwjDLsQdSHKbLmTS_QqVDcbCUhRjFKAySbV_xkLeHeoa1N4ZhlDw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been a patient of Dr. Sivley for 14 years.  I am never disappointed with the care I receive here. The staff is friendly and helpful. The hygienist are very thorough and knowledgeable. Dr. Sivley is genuinely concerned about his patients and quick to fix problem teeth. The eight veneers he placed on my front teeth 13 years ago are still beautiful and I've never had any issue with them. I highly recommend Big Country Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Letty Hernandez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKkTZXSMlsHDx6pUtWe2sxBbIx6uLjSMmSVdP0QZXKEdKx2yQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First time patient, my fiance told me about them and I decided to try them out. Never felt judged and left with a good plan on what steps to take into getting me on the right track where I want to be with my dental health. Definitely worth going to! From the receptionist, to the hygienist and to the doctor, they were all amazing and friendly!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marsha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLaH9HcMz7fMSKVmR49b0BxLOmAmVni8Olip8ADcE5FLAtmLw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience with Dr. Silvay and the hygienis