 visit to this clinic and I'd say it was a great and memorable experience. The clinic itself was clean and welcoming. All the staff were very friendly and thorough, special mention to Jessica, Dr Adam and ofcourse Moose who made the experience extraordinary.  Olivia brought home a birthday balloon, a lollipop and a happy experience ☺️Thank you all again.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0xnoMGhEA05bv4McraGM0hHuIrn5oxRlQ-vHx_r_je1jvDRFG4Zx0Wav0mBydBonB8s6LmZEez_SVu4aMEQpSV1Sb9zIh8XgHeJeoenu2UXVbYjO4ponLCoPESRJd-hC9nCv7-KIqUPI8T=k-no"],"When":"2025-12-2"},{"Name":"Sheridan Gleason","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocImwUh7WUa6Da2uM7B1D8ZjbXUJDuDUUy-4r38f12ApDLB9xg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"If you’re searching for a place that genuinely cares, especially for neurodivergent children, this is it. We brought our special needs son here after a less than great experience elsewhere, and we’re so glad we did. Watching our anxious, fearful kiddo completely turn around laughing, telling jokes, and actually looking forward to his orthodontist visits has been incredible. We’re so grateful to the sweet friends who recommended this place to us after their own positive experience. Truly thankful to be patients here!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1e-r_nXiRDKymVPfgHmCEAbTp6G6YUI5imYqxkoNhtbG3dRUQBgSsPQkzFsT8lLZVyyB0ZUx3f6NCSRtkx1IqxJD16TP3yU-Rc_w-FRpLGUut0R5rS2bV0-dc0XAzUgzfkvtdmFsjSpWBx=k-no"],"When":"2025-9-25"},{"Name":"Sabrina Guzman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXPukql4WoJKgEg3YX6uAfjPx4ogmZZdTbHP8OqqrUDXojD-qu8=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff was exceptionally kind and professional. They treated my tooth promptly and relieved the pain I had been experiencing. I truly appreciate the quality of care and attention provided. Thank you very much for your excellent service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jnkoa33","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXYmCNjrT2SU82brrSDUCCbpvFPdOKHIdQ7jBQwM0lDe-2ZTg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Excellent care. Friendly and competent front desk staff and office manager. Very good dental hygienist. State of the art technology. They always get back to you in a timely manner. Dr. Lacie is thorough and knowledgeable. I am very pleased.\nKeep in mind that some insurances WILL NOT PAY for some of the technology used at this clinic and the clinic has no way of knowing what your dental insurance plan will cover. If your insurance company is being cheap, then you will likely receive a bill 90 days down the road which can be a significant cost.\nMy wife and I enrolled in comprehensive dental plans which are unique to our individual dental needs. We chose this route as I no longer have dental insurance.\nIf you will be going for regular cleanings, ask about and strongly consider enrolling in one of their inclusive comprehensive dental care options INSTEAD OF USING YOUR DENTAL INSURANCE PLAN.\nAgain, the clinic doesn't overcharge the patient. If you get a large bill a few months after your visit for testing or imaging that was performed, this clinic has done nothing wrong. You are receiving excellent dental care. The reason for the bill is because your insurance company is BEING CHEAP AND STUBBORN.\nThank you Dr. Dennis and staff.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kaci Queen-Phillips","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU3E9XDeJFS9yf0NFo06hA2784Xc4Fd-g5bbtQ3Q27Su405b64=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My 2.5yr old daughter was terrified, but Moose (the precious pup they have in the office), the balloon, the sugar free sucker, and sunglasses she got to take home def eased her mind about the dentist. She even asked if we could go back as we were leaving 🤣\n\nThe entire staff is so kind and helpful, and I can’t say enough great things about the atmosphere/overall comfort. Thank you Jessica and Dr Adam for taking care of my daughter, and for making her first dental experience a fun one!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amber Swisher","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXdS0Hxqd4ApgWisK9PTyuYHHti0mQMExDlVHaAf3vjn4nccfs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"First off I have never been to a dentist office that was so thorough. It was welcoming from the moment I walked in and the entire staff were so friendly. Lacie explained everything in detail about what she found and my plan of treatment, and she  was so nice. The best of all was moose snuggles!! If you need a dentist, this office is great!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jackie O'Bosky","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWTatioOV2rKutLj_vUytrmuD_uUQE-YHc6dHyPcE0gNV3V5TdP=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My visit with Laci and her whole dental office was wonderful! I am so happy to have found our new dentist here in Abilene! The visit was relaxing and so comfortable. Laci really takes the time to listen to your concerns and provides the best treatment. Ask for her pup Moose if you want all your dental anxieties to fade away. She sat on my lap the whole time! Very impressed and will be back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0kYj1JkG5uPzDWvRqIHUr16hxlo1i1-R-IkQc-IIQuPiVkbohdum9kc9T-DKkZeGPtlRlsKQHiXdRCmjrfs2YEBkKcdJ5I3wQCWvc5sLL6XgY53VbKiH1wlm4z4kgqs0mPXrhe=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-22"},{"Name":"Karen Munoz","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJN3EocuvIw-ery6sUNydyLjxoohPGL_rmi7A-zqROj3OTxew=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I so enjoy visiting Dr Dennis and her staff!  They are all so friendly and professional!  Their state of the art exams and services make this a wonderful and educational experience!  Would recommend anyone and everyone to come visit Dr Dennis! You won’t regret it!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
