ared to go to back to the dentist, especially one I hadn’t visited before. But Dr. Kim and his team were so gentle, friendly, nonjudgmental, patient, and informative! I’ve never met a friendlier dentist office. I don’t get anxiety before my appointments anymore. And because they educated me so much, my teeth are in a much healthier state than ever before. I highly recommend Dr. Kim’s office!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dr. Ben Zoghi","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL9CpaRSeU--nPerYY0n7R5geoOsxfd0WiTU5ZGYvWlFCAsUQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kim is very professional, mindful and kind. My experience has been delightful, and fun. You are in good hands, not a traditional dentist  experience.\nOffice manager, Mandy, is the best part of this clinic, fun and super sportive. ❤️👍❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lizzy L (Liz The Tech)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWkhdfc7Z9V44tnO7nyZ6pwKDI1hJT1AmSSAdkPht2vghL0j0Oy0Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Kim and receptionist Mandy were absolutely amazing! Dr. Kim was gentle, professional, and made me feel completely at ease. Mandy was so warm and welcoming. She made the whole experience even better. Outstanding service from start to finish. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jon Kelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVt37Pty4dpPTvGVIasMqDAWpt3tTcfsaKyRON3fEra94kLmpI=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love Dr. Kim and his staff. They make visiting the dentist a pleasant experience. Highly recommended","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Audrey Connelly","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXaEETudBgqst1EWzX0Q-QtjeVDL97AQiIB0kO7WHtyo6ypNMY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Mandy and Dr. Kim are seriously the best I’ve never felt so comfortable at the dentist, they know exactly what there doing and are just so great!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
