ll,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"100990067672567325276","name":"Sulphur Springs Dental (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/100990067672567325276"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"300 Central Texas Expy","city":"Lampasas","postal_code":"76550","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"offerings","name":"Offerings","options":[{"name":"Emergency services","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Kristal Alderson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVeysxQfg2FjnpXM4QRzo1dkMCbOeH-sQi2VtGMkU9YHlUlXw8z5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Crystal and her team are exceptional. They make you feel comfortable, cared for, and truly heard, while making sure you’re thoroughly taken care of every step of the way. They go above and beyond in all that they do. Truly a blessing. There’s not much humanity left in this world, but I promise you’ll find it here.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Brandon DuBose","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKlrTp0iI67a6SOICiOvu18reidk5L04EUF1Fci_izJ8b1-jA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is absolutely amazing! From the start it was perfect. Called this morning told Miranda that I had a bad toothache due to a tooth breaking. Miranda was very fast at getting me in there. I told her how nervous I was and she assured me everything was going to be perfect!\n\nI got called back and the nerves starting going crazy! Crystals assistant came in asked me what happen and got all the trays and all that good stuff. Crystal came in and was super amazing with a great personality that really lightened the nerves! She explained to me literally everything steo by step so I wasnt surprised by anything! Even had a few jokes going during procedure! She is the absolute GOAT of dentists. I cant give these ladies enough credit from start to finish! Those 3 ladies are nothing shy of badasses!!!! Dr. Crystal and her assistant have got the teamwork down to an art!\n\nThank yall for being perfect!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shellie Oakley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIj1mNTEbBv8Qpf-hTmHnGBP0v4-eHdHPKrGKq0xVZa8wkLSg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I can't express enough gratitude about the dentist and staff at Sulfur Springs Dental. I have always been scared to see a dentist. I had my first procedure done on 5/7/25. Doctor Crystal Eschbach is amazing!!! She is very gentle and listens to my concerns. To SMILE confidently is PRICELESS! I'm ready for my next appointment. Thank you so much Sulfur Springs Dental!! ❤️❤️❤️❤️❤️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"paul gyroman","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7VrclYDWwv6NNCrV781Wclx82ZRiQA30J6XbrZZIssQ3fmVE=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So chip a tooth friday evening memorial day weekend and it exposed a nerve. The pain was a level 10 and would not let up.  I was surprised to get a call Monday and say they could get me in first thing Tuesday morning.  Despite being in a lot of pain from another injury to my hands they did a great job on the extraction. Now I will have to say this girl must have spent time on a ranch removing fence post as the motion she used to extract my tooth was one in the same...lol It could have went differently if she had spent time in a rock quarry and the alternative was drill and blast!. All fun aside they did a superb job and highly recommend.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lily Staley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIdElTiBEJfB-Ds8ZYOhKMzpLtuv0cl8jFhnhESJzGFG7bBkg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"This place is amazing! They go above and beyond for all your needs! I've been going here for years, both Dr Elder and Dr Eschbach are AMAZING! love this place! I will continue to travel to them no matter how far I move!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eve Tatum","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJAgjeCjaA1kUQPgf2Y1OGX_KtTVsh6ApYK8Hr4nwgLe5kjmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Love my dental crew at Sulfur Springs dental clinic!\nI’ve been a patient for many moons and I get the same service with a kind greeting and smiles! The crew makes you feel like family!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aime Ibarra","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV8Skl1uYWeGabut5wUbGLO4cqT8COC1cOjiwrEm_5vX7TdMZXNbQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I’m so thankful Dr. Crystal Elder Eschbach was able to see me in my emergency situation, my husband and I were traveling from San Antonio to Lampasas for a bible study we host monthly, when I felt pieces of my tooth breaking, it was my wisdom tooth 😔 My husband and I were going to turn back around and cancel bible study, with it being a Friday, we didn’t think anybody would be able to squeeze us in, but we decided to call Sulphur Creek Dental, and they were able to check me in  🙌🏽 I was give antibiotic, ibuprofen and a referral to a Dr. in SA- which by the way was also great, Dr Crystal Elder Eschbach,  Miranda and Kayla were just amazing and took the utmost care of me.  We were able to have our  Friendsgiving and Bible Study the next day 😊","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jim and Mary Alcorn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLj3STvyb_tQ9ZOz5bRjDZKo_f-_9voNc3Mk5oAuvq5WAIDEA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I broke a tooth and they worked me in as a new patient. it was repaired and I was in and out in less than an hour.  I have some dentist anxiety but they made sure I was comfortable and as calm as possible.  Very pleased!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
