is incredibly sweet and provides very helpful tips for maintaining my dental health. We love this practice and will continue coming here for the whole family. I highly recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Catherine Gomez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXf51_GqjGSL5FRBFnbw14e3Zk1qpZuppytRTlFK8ejC8chKY883A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful staff!! Very attentive and caring dentist and dental assistant!! ( Dr.S \u0026 Sabrina) They worked with my schedule and pulled out a tooth that needed to be pulled instead of making me come back for another appointment! I highly recommend Achieve Dental!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"whitney cochran","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5_aBqDKyfUZt_O45eUeEZ8FiStq8anE8YzP2MlcmRORKRaA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Took my 3 year old granddaughter in for routine checkup the staff was absolutely amazing!!! We went from a little one refusing to let them near her mouth to getting x rays dentist checking her teeth to sealant applied. their kindness and patience was definitely appreciated!!! She ended up loving going to the dentis!!!! if i could give more than 5 stars i would def recommend!!!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Destini Murrill","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUommDaMAzOiNJbu8mSCiBPDedSU6ZDrq5P5cHPo0aA0rDjhMA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The environment was welcoming Glenn and employees were nice. I am a black woman. I did not feel any discrimination or otherwise. The doctor Shweta took care of me got it done quickly and informed me of my treatment plan and walk me through it step-by-step so far I’m loving it and will be returning. My Asst. Sabrina was awesome","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Navy Boone","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJWZOhtpP6hTWUcHT8jhvVaZaKuZXcT9Roq_MqJcnOxybsT4A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I love achieve dental!! I have been coming here for years with my husband and children. We always have a great experience with the quality of work that gets done, and the staff is always very welcoming making sure my family and I are comfortable and helping us out with the kids when we need it!! By far the best dental office in West Texas!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jennifer De la garza","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLEm-0hlHZ1X3P3XWHEjm9Skfv35TiFeHP5WsfxB_2p3gCd=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experiences. They got me in fast, very clean, profession and kind. As someone that hates the dentist, my experiences have been good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Frank Ortega","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVth0cEPcJnrg1Ar-DjKayutxIOmKuFRJVa5NtxoPkbywlNz0Yo=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was very please with the care I received, and almost called b.s. when they told me the final cost for my dental work.  Not even in the ballpark as to what I was expecting to have to pay for a set of dentures.  I'll up date after I get them put in and they fit right...I hope.   They insured me they would have them fit properly and work out pain.   So far so good.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Shanna Lambert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIniXif9YfEsdO18ujuowGoMsdyx81FIiQ-Z80FH7BfyyVhzw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Sabrina and Dr S was super laid back and reassuring and helped me get thru the apprehension of the visit and the lack of self esteem and embarrassment of needing dental work done. Made me feel at ease through the whole process and they actually cared and spoke to me with care and hospitality and wanted to help me.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
