n I was greeted by friendly staff and taken back in a timely manner. Dr. Soben was friendly, professional and concerned for my problem and gave me all available options. Once my new partial was ready I came in, and it was adjusted to fit comfortably. As I knew would be, I still needed an adjustment a few days later, called and was able to come in that day; Dr.Soben made the adjustments, and sent me on my way, happy with my partial. The office and staff is also well organized. I am SO glad I have become their new patient. I’m in very capable dental care. I highly recommend Dr.Soben","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
