 in my truck when we where leaving but my son fell and had to ask for help all came to help including the dentist we couldn’t not pick him up called non emergency and Firefighters came to help and everyone stayed with us till the end offered us water and a pillow for my sons head I know it doesn’t seem like much but to me it was A lot and Thank All The Staff That Day","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Terry Kim","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIN8l2pcV6xNMEzkN3yy8_g3pw44IseKPNC5YSzKvysdG-OmQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"5 Stars but wish I can give 6.  Great staff especially Registered Dental Hygienist (RDH) Jenny!  Great attention to details, knowledgeable \u0026 kept me comfortable the entire time making my first appointment a superb experience.  Second appointment with Dr. Grant.  Superb \u0026 efficient dentist; barely felt anything \u0026 no sensitivity after treatment.  Fun to talk to \u0026 hangout with for a bit afterwards.  I look forward to coming back!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jasmine Acosta","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ79tHrUDwBJJSvd15lgSgajj2RjsC6EpC9_yqwWJ_kmvE3Aw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Definitely recommend for all of your dental needs, my hygienist was the sweetest and explained everything I was needing thoroughly. I just moved to Abilene in June and was needing to get in and they made it happen for me super fast. Front desk and staff were also very sweet!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leah Nicholson","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJfpRCpdhJ4yei-jpjNjFZRZ50wLNNeR3t-cjhWyustnIoKUg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Grant and his staff are amazing!!  Lolly is always so professional and kind.  It always feels like you’re part of the family when you go there.  I highly recommend them!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dianna Zugai","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJDRr4_c