credible technique of Dr. Fandel! If you or someone you know has apprehension about going to the dentist: go here! You'll be well taken care of! Honestly though, ask yourself why you're still here on Google instead of calling for an appointment!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rae Ann BIble","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJsEqJygZNCYauzrjV6R7ma-iltTyc6lafJkWXs2_MVr5Z3Hg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dental appointment was great.  Dr. Fandel was very gentle getting my treatment completed...even called to check on me.  My cleaning went well also. I would highly recommend Concho Valley Family Dental.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacob Kari","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ6rML_4JQsfOEdUYl-TG0TgzXbi-UVEzitCD3hzIHKdy7Yyw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr Fandal and staff were amazing! They got me same am as a walk in, filled out paperwork and got right back! Dental hygienist both visits were so reassuring and helpful!  They walked me thru step for step the procedure and tremendously reduced my anxiety about my procedure I had to get done! Highly recommended!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rachel Ballard","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIzEMXx_22FdSvYE7E9uTAJPJYC48UmaXgoB84Hp9w0vr3a=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We just had the BEST experience with Dr. Fandel! My son is almost 14 and has never been able to have a cavity filled due to such fear. Dr. Fandel took the time to listen to his fears and then talk him through them! He was able to get the entire process done, and his cavity fixed, and walked away with a smile on his face rather than tears in his eyes. I’ve truly never had a better experience with a dentist than I have with Dr. Fandel and his team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cheyanne Horn","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHKmnSJS8rgXtNpdFulFyoQbodN06ZHtklYViZGZSEMF-mqA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Fandel was amazing with me! I have POTS syndrome and almost passed out and they were super nice and helped me with oxygen and set me up with blood pressure and heart rate things to monitor everything. I have no pain today after getting 2 teeth extracted yesterday! Amazing people!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jessica Rodriguez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWJisS9jJ-vN13oJvzZeWhYui8hCzJ9TIYXT5f2DXH-NkQ7f4_1NQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I couldn’t be more satisfied 😊 The first time I went to a dentist I had the worst experience . This time around I trusted Dr. Fandel and his staff,  I had 2 extractions done I didn’t know what to expect. I was a little scared and nervous but glad to say everything turned out okay 👍 he definitely made sure I was ok as far as the Procedure I didn’t feel a thing. He then gives me a call later that day to see if I have any questions or concerns and to see if everything is still ok . 😊 everything went smoothly didn’t experience any pain or swelling? Unless it kicks in later but it’s been a whole day and I feel fine . Thank you Dr. Fandel 🤗","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Abigail Carroll","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUmOyD-6wDWyv47wyKqylCq3jhDhhVb-4TlKj5fIoqltDTFjGSw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to the dentist for the first time in forever and felt so safe, the staff was super nice and made me feel comfortable. Definitely recommend them!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gloria Ruiz Garcia","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIsIS48BoF3OPQ8H6VKjKrUML5ZSjXdCuFIJL0BOukB1GjDSA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Went to get a loose tooth extracted but was informed that since I was experiencing minor pain, I needed antibiotics for a week otherwise if I didn’t take antibiotics first, the pain after the extraction would be severe.\nSo, I was thankful I went to this dentist.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
