hmabaANSmwlZEDyogRpyuiqFIociBAbUerkw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My dentist Doctor Safari and I are matching shoes.👟👟😀😀\nExcellent customer service⭐️⭐️100 point.\nI love how Dentist and dental hyenist personnel were able to take care of my crown #5 on 13 February. I am grateful, they worked as team. Thank you ❤️🥰","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3A4_GouQBRLsUiL9JB_90PRqskKd6h5Enn4wVVhmrbpc5o3HtU7rTYSKDNMRpWLui5qQW4bcCS8T0zQAH_2oSzc3bOY4ZyEOsybagAnrrK3Ln0ZaDJA3hYlkmBKGLLLt7fFjpUBTxV1Vu0=k-no"],"When":"2026-2-13"},{"Name":"Chris Parillon","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKvS7CIzns4CtMCHVBX_PRI2zaKixjfhuDAtUYksFzOsPujxw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Staff was friendly, courteous, patient and took time to listen to my concerns, answer my questions and explaining procedure and recommended treatment. They even informed on payment plan. Michelle was excellent in performing my periodontal treatment. Great job. Thank you.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Marlene 670","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUXrA_RSrSfhokSVh_bKePw6wpAI4BdEshUDeBOLMDW_qLPm615=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"The staff are kind, supportive, and understanding. They are patient and listens attentively to patients concerns and needs. I leave the clinic satisfied and look forward to returning for their great service.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Deanna Broady","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXd_SZOz_4OUU7Tv2EBKDJbW6whvLLFwJLzd2F1k1jNy81hkJKhmg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I like using Coast Dental for my dental needs.\nFrom my last appointment: Michelle was great \u0026 very personable.\nSafari \u0026 Irene were friendly \u0026 quick. I'll continue to come here for my appointments.  I've been coming for a while now \u0026 everyone has been nice \u0026 I've never had a bad experience. Highly recommend to anyone looking for a dentist.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Nicole Davis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI7tP04K7c2sUeAZkmu-5jq55HLn-oNcENvVFm6r3l4G90WgQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"If I could give a negative star I would ! This place is horrible they canceled my appointment twice, after I take off work two separate times for this one appointment! They are very rude and unprofessional! I took off for my appointment today only to be canceled when way earlier in the day claiming to be because of the weather… mind you this was a 2pm appointment it wasn’t snowing today only a little rain …..","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Alysia Williams","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVs0ZJVxg8kbm98qiItmMSx2ozPkOi6IFpN3NTxAu8TNvhJVYasoA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Today, I had my first cleaning with Mercedes. I cannot recommend her enough!!! I am a person who has anxiety before getting into the chair. I know all the tricks to settle my nerves, the best I can: wear earbuds with a carefully planned playlist, wear a comfy hoodie, so you can lay back and snuggle into something for comfort, and so on. It just so happens that today's cleaning was going to be an invasive one, to the point that it is scheduled as half of your teeth one visit and the other half the next visit. It's too much to do all at once. Needless to say, anxiety was high! I go in and meet Mercedes, and to my pleasant surprise, she was just the most joyful precious human! I brief her a little bit on why I am such a baby...lol. She made me feel so comfortable and at ease.  You guys, the sort of cleaning I had to have done today required her to go deep below my gums on each tooth. When I booked my appointment initially, I kept hearing words like....invasive, deep cleaning, root planing.....scary words! However, I didn't feel any of that! Every time she would reach for something, I would think: okay here it comes, this is it, here we go! And then nothing!!! No pain!!! So she starts to talk to me, and I have to pause my playlist to hear her. I realize she is telling me what a good job I have done. I'm processing her words and I'm beginning to catch on that we are all done!!! What?!?! She didn't speed through, as this appointment was over an hour. But she navigated it in such a way that I didn't feel anything. She is a very talented, skilled, precious person!!! If you are looking for a hygienist, please make an appointment with her!!! I will be back myself, in a few weeks!! And I don't have any anxiety over it. She gave me a gift today by removing that. I'm so grateful!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Rodney Befit Alfred","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUkk1OExdkFOFlCyj8zCTVMKCiE9NpVqj6s5o6XUrULDb4rkHGt=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Very professional staff! Michelle the dental hygienist was amazing! I normally hate the dentist but she made me feel comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Latrayvia Bell","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUg92d8KpHNT4r-EBFYkDbowX3x7FSmN_NWh0xOKn-sWFV_kWs=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Awesome Awesome Awesome work !! Nancy \u0026 a gentleman (I didn’t get his name) and Michelle all made sure I had a comfortable yet effective experience! Highly recommended ! Great team! Even front desk staffing was friendly and professional ! clean lobby, etc. Just amazing all around. Thank you all !!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
