true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Taylor Parker","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU5z3VbxurQs3bSmlJ8M-YzyE5R00zh9kjrhRNR7W4idxWrpwsV=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Garza, Anthony and Aracelis were all amazing! I am very grateful to have found this office. It's bright, clean, smells great, a little chilly (but they have and offer blankets!); I feel very comfortable and confident in their care. They explained well and everyone took the time to ask me if I had any questions, and listened without an ounce of irritation or rush even though they were busy! Happy to have found the dental office I'll be sticking with!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Bekah Melenric","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX7UN0nsnwBo3bvb39Cra5lLsvmF4lmDUEFybqRwaT_s3w1ogOz=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a wonderful experience for my first time going! Dr. Madison was amazing and informative. Felt very comfortable and they felt like they really cared about their patients. Aracelis was also wonderful and very helpful through the process.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron Ferrer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLHyI8Ko0frd57lyj_d-38kdtbfQmgXx7XV48EG1XksKvZY6oYH=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Great experience with Dr Madison, Aracelis and Silvia. They were kind, down to earth, and really took the time to hear us, my wife and I, as new patients. I did a deep cleaning and it was painless, also a filling. I would come back!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1w15BbrbTCMgc1qUNgaKruCtUsiVu45LUWLajvyWsQ-zA-iZVryYVW63XHsYZ-Pw9AF0omCWI5QqXW_mV0WZRtNcWv5Y35R1za91Zg-d4ygCRTIg3RNYqtvg