ges":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Aaron “Sparky” Gilbert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVVh5dQOeJ2Qjmb0MXL5riKPMkc5mRkUpHkY3RFIAgo0TkJqOE=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Hi, I’m Aaron and I have a serious sweet tooth. I can’t blame anyone but myself (and probably my Grandpa). Pearland Dentists next to HEB identified an issue, did not jump to radical expensive fixes, and when the time was right, made the correct calls. What a time we live in! I had a root canal and received a PERMANENT crown all in the span of 2 hours! This was my first root canal and I was understandably anxious. Sure, it wasn’t exactly a Maui sunset but, it was nothing to be afraid of either.  I could not be happier with Doctor Madison, Doctor Dennis, Yuri, Lorena, hygienist Shadie, Jenifer and the rest of the team! Thank you for putting me back together! I owe you all a Snickers bar…. Well, maybe a nice celery stick.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
