e had such a wonderful experience here. My daughter has significant anxiety about dental visits, and after her appointment she asked if she could return for all of her care. The team was truly fantastic.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Leigh Balios","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocILnLZvkie1VBqr3-HVPnR_iZbURDdeUmdm7pGA7Z5moCG4KQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I finally have a tooth that isn’t shocking me every time I bite down!!! I feel amazing!! I can’t thank all of you enough for helping me with my teeth!! I highly recommend Dr. Sargent!! The office folks, the assistants, and Dr. Sargent will help you make the best decision for your dental health!!  Thank you so much!!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Dora Guajardo","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLTPhNAw3y6fSius4GITyl-v6hx3qaIHlLL7OEAHA7_Oq6WJI8M=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing team Dr. Baker and the assistant that helped her were two very knowledgeable, well trained, and connected people working together to make me feel safe, better, comfortable, and made sure it was done correctly. Dr.Baker made me forget I was scared \u0026 nervous. My root canal procedure was excellent/perfect as of 12/5/2025 NM time 3:50PM. I’m grateful and thankful for these two ladies. God bless🙏♥️","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"John Brimberry","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBX7ymqs5YQAyTCrui3Ey8bI6Xn0c8lVP-XrZrsNPZNx1tUyyf=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My visit was very good. The front desk was friendly and inviting and I was promptly brought back for x-rays and evaluation. It was determined I needed a root canal. Dr Baker was fantastic. Very polite but down to business and was able to save my crown during the root canal. She was meticulous and efficient and 4 days later, I had no pain from the entire procedure.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Yvonne Lunsford","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3