 It’s rare to find a medical office where every single person you interact with is so kind and skilled. I cannot recommend them highly enough!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julep","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUHIqx0D0dyJ0cyBXIkNa7p5DQDX07wGngeQOcFOczbhs4naP78rg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Such caring and professional staff. They were able to fit me in for an emergency, waited for us to travel the hour + to their office, and gave me first class treatment while I was there. They understood the amount of pain I was experiencing and made sure to walk me through all the various steps for my treatment. They made me feel comfortable during my procedure, ensuring I was both adequately taken care of as well as informed. I cant recommend them enough, and I’ll direct anyone asking their way. Dr McIntosh was my doctor, and seemed more than knowledgable about my issue. My healing time since has been stress-free, but more importantly, pain-free. Abilene is extremely fortunate to have their practice.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Studd Daddii","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUF-1l5uShhuyJz-7KpMfdih_XnC7aVLxkwr8Qz7EIFzEFZ6ZVK5Q=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Came in on December 2nd To get a root canal done to my mouth when I tell you, the doctor was very nice. The employees was nice. Very professional The doctor make sure he took his time. He was very polite. I love his service hands down. I will be back for more work if needed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Fr. Philip LeMasters","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULwRbv1hUzzYDzmC8dNWPxHpHSnJJ9YKaBanmHIghzSSeF2rWr8Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. McIntosh and his team did a superior job with an urgent root canal through a crown earlier this week.  I was in pain and they fit me in immediately.  Everyone in the office was friendly, courteous, and professional throughout every dimension of my experience with them as a first-time patient.  I could not have been more pleased and give them my highest recommendation.  If I ever need such dental work again, I will call them immediately.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Kelsi Schaefer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKzOrQfjTkestPSSMb6G7I5rMf5jxRCC2IO_dCci-KyUT_qOg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had a completely pain-free root canal retreatment. I went in extremely nervous as I usually have trouble getting numbed at the dentist, but I felt nothing at all throughout the treatment. They called to check on me the next day which was very nice. My only “complaint” is that I was really nervous before treatment began and ended up requiring nitrous to calm my nerves, and I felt like I was annoying to them by using the extra time it took to get that set up and that made me feel a little embarrassed.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Sheri Johns","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUBDklg-dWrAY2qEq-pSfQj5vIj-NPjZEL6TjPfFuSxkPgl6Qga=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Due to certain circumstances, I needed to be seen very quickly.  Dr. McIntosh and his staff worked me in within 1 day.  The staff was so kind and put me at ease right away.  The procedure went much better than I expected, so I would definately recommend this office to anyone needing their expertise.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tonya Holland","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLa2zDzk8ZWmEwn2WTwqCyLrVF9qFxyNDSObcEBHO5p-VyURw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It was probably  the best experience at a dentist i have ever had! They were super nice and very informative on what was going to happen. Through out the whole process i was very comfortable.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jacinda Hawkins","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXY8WteEk_fDdCvi_jiOB9a0ygqM4p4Mjf4OKKhtM44I2cARlA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I was referred by my dentist for a root canal. The whole experience was quick and easy. Dr.  was informative and let me know what was happening every step of the way and the office called to check on me the day after. Great experience if you have to get a root canal!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
