name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Rebekah C","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK5BhB_PHgQDJvzB7AX2RabFztEfAK1ycrO9j7MJKqHS9v1DQ=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Hernandez and Renewal Dental Arts offer a holistic standard of dental care that far exceeds expectations.\n\nI went through extensive research to find a dental office that does not use fluoride in their services. I chose this office because they look out for your health beyond the surface. Amber shared great details about product ingredients, opening up a whole new world I wasn’t aware of. Had I not known this, I would have made a costly mistake elsewhere. She called me back at just the right time, and I’m so appreciative. I was happy to wait longer to see Dr. Hernandez because dental work lasts a lifetime and truly impacts your health—I wasn’t looking for a quick, surface-level fix.\n\nA lot of times we aren’t aware of these small details, but Dr. Hernandez has you covered. The research he does to keep your health front and center is so reassuring. The attention he gives—even down to using paper cups instead of plastic and choosing high-quality mouthwash over commercial brands—is the kind of mindfulness that sets this office apart. It’s all in the details.\n\nDr. Hernandez’s work and care created a clean slate with the best-quality products.\nThank you to Dr. Hernandez and the amazing Renewal Dental Arts team for your help.\nHighly recommended.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"dolores cordova","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHmbxJSbGnxBmc_6nlvho4aN0sIVG1654e_pYcdbk12Q3QIIt1=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"So happy i was able to have Dr Linnemann take care of my chip tooth..I had gotten another opinion from another facility and wanted to do a crown and charge me a pretty penny..what a big difference when you have a Dentist who can do a great job and make you smile again..SO GRATEFUL FOR DR LINNEMAN!!! I will continue my care with him ❤️","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0jtQlam4w8PFO4AzLvzSuvybeWK_lM2du30snMi8c99PYHV8kbNtPNrDD5jooKC5OuUgJZ2FhtOKR7v6U9W424B7_9pxN8fPHs131PAXHQd3NxhzzRJ-DA_cM2M93cglmc7iM=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn04fuQdkODOe4LZh3_gSQ8xunSdew5oH04hSwIP_5uBASVXuNLRCOB0FGcbPFXEQZNwouTshQBKS49WV4S1drfigkdd5EABCyzx9knpSa-qDP_C302rWR-sTWd9p8_NzTaBtcEBwQ=k-no"],"When":"2024-5-8"},{"Name":"Izzy Padgett","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXRSJ2GPAeLJmIyCcGpQshFkN5WuLKeWogjkoIYfilbA3SRXn862Q=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We won the dentist lottery! I absolutely love this office, all the people in it \u0026 the values they hold. They legitimately make you feel like family. My twin toddlers are not only excited to brush their teeth every day, they LOVE visiting the dentist! This is a huge Mom win. We love their holistic approach and flouride-free care. They also take care of me and are actively helping heal dental anxiety. It's well worth the 48 minute drive for us.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn0ijILlPjPL9wUQQ0-KUzFZ36q8mNKtT64V18epjDmUgx3WF-SiJOqo2gMBD00ZtoN6_zMR9bbt9SHickhr4iGMuaGsk-nnThEh8L4Sui4ax3lUR_hRD2BABd6rXT96YgAXOKIg=k-no"],"When":"2025-5-3"},{"Name":"tracy Bobacy","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIq3MSqhDW7IItoROwqEEgweWYjKS7Wq59omRWK4r7IFD8_KA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"Dental hygienist was sick when I went in. Husband is immunocompromised. Dangerous practice to allow someone who is so close and in your face to work when sick!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Cls Me (Swingline)","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKTiMNgQfgsxF24FspHxDsBMKvP8SwnRjt_GOCt_z2MidjEAA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My wife and I have always been impressed with S.A. Cosmetic Dentistry. Even though they have changed their name and two new dentists are replacing Dr Linnemann,  they are committed to carry on the same service that allowed my wife to overcome her fear of dentists. They are also adding more services to better provide for the needs of their clients. The original staff are still their and they too are enthused with the changes being made and also have high confidence in the new dentists.\n\nI highly recommend them and will continue to use them","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jerome Gainer","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXDUSU9aDXcLQIfukalRu2rzxysM-ke9kZnqHsRmxW5e_m3Sz4b=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really appreciate Dr Linnemann and his staff. I have been going there for about 10 years now. I first found them when I was new to the area and looking for a dentist for my wife and I. At the time, my wife had a serious fear of dentists and refused to go. She was literally in tears she was so fearful as I dragged her to her first appointment. However, the caring and understanding staff and Dr Linnemann quickly put her at ease and gave her a comfort level to where now going is no big deal. That immediate won me over, but I have also had nothing but great personal experiences with them over the years. My own dental habits have improved as a result of feedback from them and unlike most folks, I don't hate going to the dentist. I highly recommend Dr Linnemann. You can trust him and his staff to take good care of you and your loved ones.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Vicky Carmona","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7ZyV6LmI3LiHAIvnV35FMOs2x5bIdu4dFuQs_goLBmuU3leGd=s120-c-rp-mo-ba4-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Karen was amazing!  I was afraid of trying someone new because Dr. Linneman retired, but she did not disappoint.   She took care of three fillings and made a sissy like me feel comfortable with the least amount of pain as possible.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Eric Ramirez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLfVnM4fdRreJxFsw8e_pg2v4ARg93KXOEMBLgw7uClWMNTnw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I do not like going to the dentist, I never had but I do have to say is that they try and make you feel as comfortable as possible. From the front office staff very attentive and they return your calls immediately, and friendly. For being my first time Dr. Linnemann made me feel comfortable and has an excellent bed side manner that is comforting. He not only listens to you but also makes sure you feel comfortable. He explains everything thoroughly and provides you with options and makes sure you have an understanding of the type of treatment you are receiving, or will receive for future appointments. His assistant was also very friendly and had a great sense of humor, not sure if it's to make you feel better or if that is her personality but she was just as great. I would highly recommend this place, all the staff seems very friendly and like good people.","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
