d of the visit.\n\nSix months later, I received a call asking if I was ready to schedule a follow-up appointment, which I declined. Sometime after that, I noticed an unfamiliar charge on my credit card. After reviewing my bank statement, I discovered that this office had charged my card as if I had come in for a six-month follow-up appointment—which never happened.\n\nI do not understand how my credit card information was accessed or used, especially since I was not present and did not authorize any charge. I am now dealing with a credit card dispute, though I was able to get my money refunded.\n\nThis experience was extremely concerning. I recommend others be cautious when dealing with this office and closely monitor their billing and statements.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Angelica Hall","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIgD0RxgWDWseJUSh1wNtawM8CAThH-Shu47e-xW05cDefeyg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had a wonderful experience! The dentist, hygienist and staff are friendly,  caring, professional, and take the time to explain everything clearly. They are so gentle and kind, which makes every visit comfortable and stress-free. Lovely office and never a wait.  I highly recommend Dr Lori Logan’s office.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Santos Tamez","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLwZQ-8IDOfOtQqdndEsGUQA1fvQILvWw_p6ocoMcTG7O7TCA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I finally found a Dental group my wife mentioned to me. It’s been a while since my other Dentist left the practice they were at. I now go see Dr Lori Logan at Lori Logan DDS.  They have a wonderful and professional staff. I felt at home with them. Their hygienist who helped me was very friendly and explained everything she planned to do for me. Overall, I’m happy I went to go see them and happy to say they’ve gained my trust.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"jimi rezin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV34DkbOuzHntuwR7kseF5PoM49GxxXNfeii8ux7-ehmAOrzRRH=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"I scheduled an appointment as a new patient a month in advance. I showed up today , early , only to find out that there is no record in their system. I showed them my confirmation email yet all I was told is we can schedule next week. No one said they'll look into the clear issue with the system.... No nothing. Apologies are great but I wasted a day off and my time. You would think there would some sort of credit or anything to help me feel good about wasting my morning.  I'm scheduled next week. We'll see.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Charla Reed","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK4m-UNFW5vmWgGdi-n1s5weeGTpwYq9dfZVDOjRNknfy08ZQ=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As much as I don’t like going to the dentist. I ALWAYS have a great experience. The staff is amazing.   Highly recommend Lori Logan!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
