ency services","enabled":true},{"name":"Pediatric care","enabled":true},{"name":"Sedation dentistry","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Gender-neutral restroom","enabled":true},{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"crowd","name":"Crowd","options":[{"name":"LGBTQ+ friendly","enabled":true},{"name":"Transgender safespace","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Checks","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true},{"name":"Payment plans","enabled":true},{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":false}]},{"id":"parking","name":"Parking","options":[{"name":"Free parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"On-site parking","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"Jacquelyn Koch","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIvPj60PMvl70kSuXqf9-mWHRfJalVTDV8UplqYMS2nF_C2=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wow! Wow! Wow! From booking the appointment to walking out afterwards EVERYONE was friendly, knowledgeable and thorough. I loved that all of the equipment and techniques are all new, state of the art and the most current technology available.\nI’m also incredibly grateful for the time and patience they took to make all 3 of my kiddos feel calm and at ease throughout their visits as well.\n\nI can not recommend this practice enough! If you’re looking for a dental practice- look no further! Hamblin is the best there is.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2gObomfanhBP1mOBZcUr9dILT8dsnWCsQsBpgfoAqIs_F5OoJV0bqPOS0zzsrRmIwEXZhHLH6gQ_3HwmOApOaqvdA3QFzmlsDU952TAWWiQm79u5FxpCUGGHI5sRirgRPthbJbZD_-hFXW=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-19"},{"Name":"Jayy Cartagena","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVEvS-ZT6mjYiulO5riOw0jaiHxLthyufah6EECsj5K6LrzJcOS=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I came in today for a general exam and cleaning. The front staff was very welcoming. Vanessa, the hygienist- was very thorough on explaining the entire process. They were able to examine my plaque under a microscope and give me information on the good/bad bacteria in live time. I met with Dr Hamblin who was extremely welcoming and informative. I ended up going with the superprophy cleaning and the results were night and day as far as removing my staining and build up. The atmosphere of the office is nice and clean as well. I would recommend this to ANYONE with dental needs. I was a self pay patient, and it was still very affordable. I have no issue making HFD my general dentistry home.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn2gFXhbpybmweOOxt6_7pXaVG8TEFINwrzIJffLCr3JHahYud-y1qhERdc8GKNvQ2UmX30N0KHpREZsOa5SPEzLn-_7yPaG7LcJdT79niGdIGoafwBOelQaqJWlHarpLxRSuT5gO7INZoY_=k-no"],"When":"2025-11-10"},{"Name":"Sarah Lazaridis","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV9um4J5xmOVSDAwsHhtkN8xoqci4l2JA-jzMnWvRFV4QmiObY9=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had such an amazing experience at this dental office that I felt compelled to share. From the moment I walked in, the atmosphere was welcoming, calm, and professional. The office itself is beautiful and very thoughtfully designed, which immediately put me at ease.\n\nMy hygienist, Vanessa, was truly exceptional. She was warm, personable, and incredibly attentive throughout the entire visit. She took the time to explain every step of the process, reviewed all of my options thoroughly, and made sure I was comfortable the entire time. I never felt rushed — she made me feel like I was her only patient that day. Her energy is so positive and genuine, and it’s clear she truly cares about her patients and the quality of her work.\n\nI also really appreciated how she educated me on my dental health and helped me create a plan that made sense for me. The entire team was kind, professional, and attentive, and even the small touches — like the goodie bag + gift at the end — made the experience feel special.\n\nIf you’re looking for a dental office that combines professionalism, excellent care, and a genuinely welcoming environment, I highly recommend this place. Vanessa and the team are outstanding, and I’m actually looking forward to coming back.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Stephanie Payne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWZ0o_p56e44xXJU0B_r5SAHMX3iSnrfH6IW3S5P-SGuyKw4rCSUg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I loved how clean and modern this place is (granted, it’s fairly new). I especially love the big screens which allows you to see what the dentist sees.\nEverything from the initial entry, to the final goodbye was a level of professionalism and excellence that I will definitely keep coming back for.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn1CDSg8XKF8WSYTVkiZ4NnJRj8aJqCZhR8W8Iuosut0gpz-KgBi7Nud3cSJFpd7JEWx-xLYs7_4-HgKz7JUFohU92RMrvWhGp_8i8Vexjzb0FnoXGnD6gIH-cXtZNXjyKcy_JEY5I8ObIbt=k-no"],"When":"2026-1-27"},{"Name":"Amy Auguste","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU8iZ3-zpslHRH86OP4dKeHxg9MuX5xpvBsFCeE-VD3PNDM-8ypqg=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Had my visit today and it was a great experience. Met with Dr. Hamblin and his assistant Megan. They had the best customer service and were very informative on dental needs and future needs. Staff is very welcoming. I have definitely found my dentist. Thank you Hamblin family.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"The Houston Geisha","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVuNyoLfI_2s3S9CKTdMPAs1pUp9voCUbeVOUhJZ1NsGLwEYNY=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Wonderful experience at Hamblin, I was a new patient who needed an emergency filling done and they helped me today! I'm also looking at doing dentures in a year or so, was very happy to talk with them about that and get the info I needed. They put my mind at ease and made me feel trust in them for the future. Office is clean and very nice, staff is wonderful- very friendly and professional! Helped my dental anxiety melt away! I love that Dr. Hamblin was so understanding of my concerns, I felt heard and seen! Overall probably the best experience I've ever had at a dentist (and I've been to many!). I think we've found The One! :)","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Gabbie Saldana","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUhhVRUPvcaNTEHDlVazjAeLIfacozrTgKrLrIkaIviPADv0i0=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I had an appointment last week at Hamblin Dentistry, and as someone who has had previous bad experiences at the dentist, I was honestly pleasantly surprised. From start to finish, everyone made me feel comfortable and taken care of. My hygienist, Vanessa, did an amazing job explaining each step of the process, which really helped ease my nerves. Dr. Farrell was also great and took the time to explain everything clearly. I’m very grateful for this office and will definitely be coming back. Highly recommend!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Lesly Vargas","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUrPl0yxJW1YqjcjpVocmOY4o9w9CTCqQuGrFnE5nnvft6AlCDg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Amazing experience! The staff was welcoming, professional, and made me feel comfortable the entire time. The dentist explained everything clearly and the results exceeded my expectations—my smile looks so natural and beautiful. Highly recommend if you’re looking for quality cosmetic dentistry! ✨","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
