-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Without a doubt one of the BEST dentists in San Angelo. Recently referred my mother to them. After several unsatisfactory attempts in finding a dentist, Twin Mountain checked ALL the boxes. Friendly , knowledgeable staff. Very sanitary and inviting atmosphere. Amazing Dr. who is very detailed and thorough with all his patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Samantha Wrinkle","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXHKM1RywM3PyeAfa62jmrPlspL2evIxXb1eqIKwPY_NbMjMPg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"My whole family has been going here for years and we have never had anything but wonderful experiences! Even our toddler loves coming to the dentist here! Everyone is very friendly and knowledgeable and appointments are always super easy to book.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Megan Ashley","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKbTepQV5eqiGSMWkAg6xmGUmQZOQFYTU8S5gdfILL9EzRCMw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":1,"Description":"The lady that takes payments is the only reason for my 1 star. She tried to reschedule me two days before my procedure for no reason and was rude when I said that wouldn’t work for me. She said “well that’s not going to work for us” then was not helpful in answering mine and my husband’s questions about payments after the appointment. Thankfully another woman jumped in to help during both of these interactions. She deserves a raise! But that other lady needs a new career not dealing with people","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Julia McCormick","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocI2BEWm6fIhuqKidY2D3RIvg6-xPw0eJue0tHwJ4uJz5jL1Hw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I dread going to the dentist office and I have complete anxiety triggers... but this office experience was completely amazing. Julie had the best patience and was so informative throughout the whole process.. she was extremely kind and I'm so pleased. The main dentist was very nice along with the receptionist. She gave a breakdown of procedure and payment info, and was very sweet as well. I highly recommend this place!!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
