d with dentist visits as most people do. However my appointment with Dr. Paris was easy going and pain free. Dr. Paris is the most knowledgeable dentist I have ever been to and its very clear that him and his staff truly care about their patients.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Janardan Amin","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJtew1UDbRdZ_qsBcJocnlyl1VUkW2ge8KbdIFdt-IT_jki-A=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I have been seeing Dr. Paris now over 4 years. He is a man of integrity and honesty, treats patients with humble care. Very passionate person. Very knowledgeable and skillful surgeon. Where would you ever find a dentist that would tell you implants are not for you when all other dentists I visited said its a \"piece of cake\" for every issue I had. Dr. Paris MAKES time for his patients, studies the issues in detail and explains everything in layman terms.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"S “Suz” G","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjU56qXRM_piOeOcTRFZMwMB7jmC50IUzugLk8bWroE_vWFirsVO=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Paris spent more time with me explaining dental health than any other dentist I've ever used.  I now understand in layman's terms what certain numbers indicate concerning my oral health and how to improve those readings.  Also, Carrie and team are so friendly and caring.  My husband and I both chose Dr. Paris, and I highly recommend without reservation Dr. Paris and team.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Tracey Paul","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVO6nq50VD8G5MDAfgtlbhIxUIwW2m3PrI5OPgLBmUF72GWE75e_g=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"From a person that has dealt with dental iffice fear and anxiety ... After my initial consultation... I can honestly can say my prayers have been answered. Dr. Paris is not only empathetic, he is encouraging and his thoroughness in explaining his treatment plan is motivating. There is no doubt I am in good hands under his care. Oh, the office team is just icing on the cake!","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
