yaw=78.55784\u0026pitch=0\u0026thumbfov=100"}],"reservations":null,"order_online":null,"menu":{"link":"","source":""},"owner":{"id":"115694620958156960565","name":"Robinson Orthodontics: Dr. Paul R. Robinson, DMD (Owner)","link":"https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/115694620958156960565"},"complete_address":{"borough":"","street":"617 Ball St","city":"Grapevine","postal_code":"76051","state":"Texas","country":"US"},"about":[{"id":"accessibility","name":"Accessibility","options":[{"name":"Wheelchair accessible entrance","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible parking lot","enabled":true},{"name":"Wheelchair accessible restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"amenities","name":"Amenities","options":[{"name":"Restroom","enabled":true}]},{"id":"planning","name":"Planning","options":[{"name":"Appointment required","enabled":true},{"name":"Appointments recommended","enabled":true}]},{"id":"payments","name":"Payments","options":[{"name":"Credit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"Debit cards","enabled":true},{"name":"NFC mobile payments","enabled":true}]}],"user_reviews":[{"Name":"William Atto","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLXT_GfvniCACtWkxghAH1VyO8LIjIDCEwzCYEtXuuS6PGwPA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Choosing Dr Robinson for my children’s orthodontic care is the best decision I could have made. Two of my children were in his care and both had wonderful experiences with him and his staff. It was a seamless process from start to finish. Both needed substantial help and everything was explained with patience. One of the things I’ve appreciated most about Dr Robinson is that, from the very first, he spoke directly to my children. I love that. They’re the patients after all, and he made such a positive impression on both of them and on me. I can’t imagine taking my kids to another orthodontist. And a word about the extent of the procedure for one of my kids who really needed a lot of work on her palette, etc. It worked exactly as he said it would. I can’t recommend him highly enough in terms of his expertise.  And his staff - well Jeanna is up front - friendly, engaging, and efficient- she’s puts a great face on the business, so kind to everyone- puts each patient at ease I’m sure, especially the kids. And all the additional support staff: wonderful, friendly folks. I cannot recommend Dr Robinson and his team highly enough.","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn28DSAEYvUoKPUCSzIfqdfMfuu5nSa06zD99Z6JiODQGHF9psVen3NAS120me-L15oVN8WrC7w3qYbLAUd2apRE2ClwEd_wWoeP29KPGlBoj6_HmRosMoc5cSTClI4kXOyoUvZ1=k-no"],"When":"2024-5-29"},{"Name":"Cameron Vitalec","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLyMkgFsfB9-ReUuFD8_btI83Fjrajfa0JQVy2aRskOcd5SIA=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"It's been a very long time since I've been here. Dr Robinson helped my teeth 14 years ago and they still look absolutely amazing. I don't know if he will remember me with how I look now, but I could never thank him enough for this how my teeth and smile look now. Would never recommend anywhere else for somewhere unless it was here.\n\nI was prompted to post this review because my girl was talking about needing an orthodontist and seeing a dentist and I wouldn't recommend anyone else besides you. And I didn't have a phone back then to do this, but now I do and was reminded of this place when her and I were talking about braces","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn20TBq85923JCJ99QoWZdpSWgkvrR06lcfnUIM0SWbn7LrJawKpGC24NBs8TnX6EiOm0abl9hQXaGAQUDsyAkFBTnjb4LqtlL4Oj4LylZWgV5lpcQT_DZSwxHgjgwX5UzhNL2gP3BlJQvDK=k-no"],"When":"2025-10-13"},{"Name":"Scott Wheeler","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocLmKvG8ALvlC6phqBpNXHkkZLKpfdfOWjCeMBEyaLVOlMQmzg=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"We were on vacation and my daughter forgot her ortho bands. Dr. Robinson provided her with the exact bands she needed without hesitation, even though we were not his patient. Awesome people here","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Jeffrey Hubert","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocL6hNteOvqnuEyP36bVI5WNTcWTyzKyBdzlb0mhgarrlEvZFw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Robinson is great and the entire staff is fabulous and accommodating. Kid endorsed, my 10-year old literally springs out of bed for her appointments.","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Carolyn Ann Walgren","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjULxKbbve1IdfjlMzBBaDSzBdTB7zjnBd-EjnnbH3RxaewKBB4=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Both daughters have been treated by Dr. Robinson and staff, and I couldn't recommend anyone more! When the girls were young and starting their orthodontic treatment, I wanted an office that was calm, friendly, had the same staff every day, reasonable plans and pricing, and excellent treatment.  We got all of this and more at Robinson!  From the minute you walk in the office, you're greeted by Jeana's bright smile, the smell of baked cookies (what a treat!), and a family atmosphere who knows every patient and parent.  My youngest just got her braces off and has been a patient there for 10 years.  When I looked at the molds/impressions from then, from the middle of her treatment, and now--wow--I really saw the depth of the work they did.  And after so many years, there, I'm truly going to miss seeing them every few weeks.  They're like family, and I really appreciate and recommend them to anyone!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn19HR-QHcPettWhL5e2Fd5YLFvrCfaSQCx-J67RJoY9z48TOzxSkaEdR8RR6LSHxO5zkZFYqGc8u7WvXEqEKNF5-k-nFspmnmRc849RuyLjWuXwUEZxyTg_ng_Jf9pHcAEKksaC=k-no"],"When":"2017-7-12"},{"Name":"Robyn Brandenburg","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocK-rzQlFa1iQ_xLymXW6-8HT2WAuQuKEkWponkQ4yW29oZCyA=s120-c-rp-mo-ba3-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"I really did my homework before selecting an orthodontist for our little girl and we are so very thankful I did. It seemed the only practice that I didn’t hear anything negative about was Robinson Orthodontics and now I see that’s for good reason. We went there for a consultation and fell in love with all of the staff. I swear, you just get that warm, comforting feeling of being at home when you’re in their office. While we positively adore their entire team, I have to say that Miss Jeanna and Miss Shelby are the sweetest rays of sunshine and somehow manage to make a dentist visit something my daughter and I both looked forward to. They are quite possibly the most delightful group of ladies you’ll ever meet. It’s amazing to see how they each take a sincere interest in each of their patients lives.\n\nMy daughter just got off her first set braces. (We also needed a pallet expander.) Somehow they got her a flawless smile in a shorter time than we ever expected! Her teeth are absolutely beautiful and she is beaming with pride. These guys did a phenomenal job with her pearly whites!!\n\nWe LOVE Robinson Orthodontics and will be back for our next round for our daughter and our little boy when his time comes. There is most certainly no one better!! I can promise if you select them to handle orthodontics for your family, there is no way you’ll be disappointed!","Images":["https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3OQOZeIAeOpxvN_opJpytF_jNwE2ZJBlBmj0346HrXbcilEAbrU-fx8i-zj9tklaAMSKuXK7eHTaUDUzbYMH-bYSYlHkki3gsT2fvf5be9h0n8dKI-gBjlNXEXAFRHUe7bjjsG=k-no","https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/grass-cs/ANxoTn3searFn7iq0yRE0ETc_6_rZY6cY1pUXjsimo2iueyRJQZlcEKdS_GaX5LFDT9HSIAP_X40oy1vAmhNXMI1V2zpcdtpMPkych1iRQErQXVmmQRBiX8Qq0cUOrZUFba3_RrtspI9=k-no"],"When":"2024-3-6"},{"Name":"Brenda Ring","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIuJ6OioDBLhGfYnZfsEOUetRBXAHjV4K0cT6N4sh3JrCBNJw=s120-c-rp-mo-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"Dr. Robinson and his staff are wonderful and do excellent work! Jeanna is always extremely helpful \u0026 personable any time I call to schedule or reschedule an appointment and makes me feel like they truly care. My son recently got his braces off resulting in beautiful teeth. I would strongly recommend if you're looking for a great orthodontist!","Images":null,"When":""},{"Name":"Amanda Jayne","ProfilePicture":"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ1pLooNIeJVEBAq7BfjXectc88ii6V0NcWnLwtcF4nDE7Csw=s120-c-rp-mo-ba2-br100","Rating":5,"Description":"As an adult who needed braces for a second time in their life, Dr. Robinson and team made the entire process easy and worth every moment. I felt like a new person after completing treatment and the entire process was wonderful.\n\nDr. Robinson knows what he’s doing, is knowledgeable in the world of ortho and his entire staff treats you with kindness and a smiling face. I don’t want braces again, but I will miss the bi monthly appointments and I recommend this office to anyone!\n\nPS- wear your retainer ;)","Images":null,"When":""}],"user_reviews_extended":null,"emails":null}
